527 
528  TotalStaticEfficiency = new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
529  TotalTotalEfficiency = new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
530  KineticEnergyLoss= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
531  TotalPressureLoss= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
532  MassFlowIn= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
533  MassFlowOut= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
534  FlowAngleIn= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
535  FlowAngleOut= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
536  EulerianWork= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
537  TotalEnthalpyIn= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
538  PressureRatio= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
539  PressureOut= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
540  EnthalpyOut= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
541  MachIn= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
542  MachOut= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
543  NormalMachIn= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
544  NormalMachOut= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
545  VelocityOutIs= new su2double[nMarkerTurboPerf];
546 
547  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarkerTurboPerf; iMarker++){
548  TotalStaticEfficiency[iMarker]= 0.0;
549  TotalTotalEfficiency[iMarker]= 0.0;
550  KineticEnergyLoss[iMarker]= 0.0;
551  TotalPressureLoss[iMarker]= 0.0;
552  MassFlowIn[iMarker]= 0.0;
553  MassFlowOut[iMarker]= 0.0;
554  FlowAngleIn[iMarker]= 0.0;
555  FlowAngleOut[iMarker]= 0.0;
556  EulerianWork[iMarker]= 0.0;
557  TotalEnthalpyIn[iMarker]= 0.0;
558  PressureRatio[iMarker]= 0.0;
559  PressureOut[iMarker]= 0.0;
560  EnthalpyOut[iMarker]= 0.0;
561  MachIn[iMarker]= 0.0;
562  MachOut[iMarker]= 0.0;
563  NormalMachIn[iMarker]= 0.0;
564  NormalMachOut[iMarker]= 0.0;
565  VelocityOutIs[iMarker]= 0.0;
566  }
567 
568 
569  /*--- Initialize the cauchy critera array for fixed CL mode ---*/
570 
571  if (config->GetFixed_CL_Mode())
572 
573  Cauchy_Serie = new su2double [config->GetCauchy_Elems()+1];
574 
575  /*--- Check for a restart and set up the variables at each node
576  appropriately. Coarse multigrid levels will be intitially set to
577  the farfield values bc the solver will immediately interpolate
578  the solution from the finest mesh to the coarser levels. ---*/
579 
580  if (!restart || (iMesh != MESH_0)) {
581 
582  /*--- Restart the solution from the free-stream state ---*/
583 
584  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++)
585  node[iPoint] = new CEulerVariable(Density_Inf, Velocity_Inf, Energy_Inf, nDim, nVar, config);
586 
587  } else {
588 
589  /*--- Multizone problems require the number of the zone to be appended. ---*/
590 
591  if (nZone > 1)
592  filename = config->GetMultizone_FileName(filename, iZone);
593 
594  /*--- Modify file name for a dual-time unsteady restart ---*/
595 
596  if (dual_time) {
597 
598  if (adjoint) { Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_AdjointIter()) - 1; }
599  else if (config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() == DT_STEPPING_1ST)
600  Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_RestartIter())-1;
601  else
602  Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_RestartIter())-2;
603 
604  filename = config->GetUnsteady_FileName(filename, Unst_RestartIter);
605  }
606 
607  /*--- Modify file name for a time stepping unsteady restart ---*/
608 
609  if (time_stepping) {
610  if (adjoint) {
611  Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_AdjointIter()) - 1;
612  } else {
613  Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_RestartIter())-1;
614  }
615  filename = config->GetUnsteady_FileName(filename, Unst_RestartIter);
616  }
617 
618 
619  /*--- Open the restart file, throw an error if this fails. ---*/
620 
621  restart_file.open(filename.data(), ios::in);
622  if (restart_file.fail()) {
623  if (rank == MASTER_NODE)
624  cout << "There is no flow restart file!! " << filename.data() << "."<< endl;
625  exit(EXIT_FAILURE);
626  }
627 
628  /*--- In case this is a parallel simulation, we need to perform the
629  Global2Local index transformation first. ---*/
630 
631  long *Global2Local = new long[geometry->GetGlobal_nPointDomain()];
632 
633  /*--- First, set all indices to a negative value by default ---*/
634 
635  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetGlobal_nPointDomain(); iPoint++)
636  Global2Local[iPoint] = -1;
637 
638  /*--- Now fill array with the transform values only for local points ---*/
639 
640  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++)
641  Global2Local[geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGlobalIndex()] = iPoint;
642 
643  /*--- Read all lines in the restart file ---*/
644 
645  long iPoint_Local;
646  unsigned long iPoint_Global_Local = 0, iPoint_Global = 0; string text_line;
647  unsigned short rbuf_NotMatching = 0, sbuf_NotMatching = 0;
648 
649  /*--- The first line is the header ---*/
650 
651  getline (restart_file, text_line);
652 
653  while (getline (restart_file, text_line)) {
654  istringstream point_line(text_line);
655 
656  /*--- Retrieve local index. If this node from the restart file lives
657  on a different processor, the value of iPoint_Local will be -1.
658  Otherwise, the local index for this node on the current processor
659  will be returned and used to instantiate the vars. ---*/
660 
661  iPoint_Local = Global2Local[iPoint_Global];
662 
663  /*--- Load the solution for this node. Note that the first entry
664  on the restart file line is the global index, followed by the
665  node coordinates, and then the conservative variables. ---*/
666 
667  if (iPoint_Local >= 0) {
668  if (compressible) {
669  if (nDim == 2) point_line >> index >> dull_val >> dull_val >> Solution[0] >> Solution[1] >> Solution[2] >> Solution[3];
670  if (nDim == 3) point_line >> index >> dull_val >> dull_val >> dull_val >> Solution[0] >> Solution[1] >> Solution[2] >> Solution[3] >> Solution[4];
671  }
672  if (incompressible) {
673  if (nDim == 2) point_line >> index >> dull_val >> dull_val >> Solution[0] >> Solution[1] >> Solution[2];
674  if (nDim == 3) point_line >> index >> dull_val >> dull_val >> dull_val >> Solution[0] >> Solution[1] >> Solution[2] >> Solution[3];
675  }
676  if (freesurface) {
677  if (nDim == 2) point_line >> index >> dull_val >> dull_val >> Solution[0] >> Solution[1] >> Solution[2] >> Solution[3];
678  if (nDim == 3) point_line >> index >> dull_val >> dull_val >> dull_val >> Solution[0] >> Solution[1] >> Solution[2] >> Solution[3] >> Solution[4];
679  }
680  node[iPoint_Local] = new CEulerVariable(Solution, nDim, nVar, config);
681  iPoint_Global_Local++;
682  }
683  iPoint_Global++;
684  }
685 
686  /*--- Detect a wrong solution file ---*/
687 
688  if (iPoint_Global_Local < nPointDomain) { sbuf_NotMatching = 1; }
689 
690 #ifndef HAVE_MPI
691  rbuf_NotMatching = sbuf_NotMatching;
692 #else
693  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&sbuf_NotMatching, &rbuf_NotMatching, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_SHORT, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
694 #endif
695 
696  if (rbuf_NotMatching != 0) {
697  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
698  cout << endl << "The solution file " << filename.data() << " doesn't match with the mesh file!" << endl;
699  cout << "It could be empty lines at the end of the file." << endl << endl;
700  }
701 #ifndef HAVE_MPI
702  exit(EXIT_FAILURE);
703 #else
704  MPI_Barrier(MPI_COMM_WORLD);
705  MPI_Abort(MPI_COMM_WORLD,1);
706  MPI_Finalize();
707 #endif
708  }
709 
710  /*--- Instantiate the variable class with an arbitrary solution
711  at any halo/periodic nodes. The initial solution can be arbitrary,
712  because a send/recv is performed immediately in the solver. ---*/
713 
714  for (iPoint = nPointDomain; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++)
715  node[iPoint] = new CEulerVariable(Solution, nDim, nVar, config);
716 
717  /*--- Close the restart file ---*/
718 
719  restart_file.close();
720 
721  /*--- Free memory needed for the transformation ---*/
722 
723  delete [] Global2Local;
724 
725  }
726 
727  /*--- Check that the initial solution is physical, report any non-physical nodes ---*/
728 
729  if (compressible) {
730 
731  counter_local = 0;
732 
733  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
734 
735  Density = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0);
736 
737  Velocity2 = 0.0;
738  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
739  Velocity2 += (node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1)/Density)*(node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1)/Density);
740 
741  StaticEnergy= node[iPoint]->GetSolution(nDim+1)/Density - 0.5*Velocity2;
742 
743  FluidModel->SetTDState_rhoe(Density, StaticEnergy);
744  Pressure= FluidModel->GetPressure();
745  Temperature= FluidModel->GetTemperature();
746 
747  /*--- Use the values at the infinity ---*/
748 
749  if ((Pressure < 0.0) || (Density < 0.0) || (Temperature < 0.0)) {
750  Solution[0] = Density_Inf;
751  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
752  Solution[iDim+1] = Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Density_Inf;
753  Solution[nDim+1] = Energy_Inf*Density_Inf;
754  node[iPoint]->SetSolution(Solution);
755  node[iPoint]->SetSolution_Old(Solution);
756  counter_local++;
757  }
758 
759  }
760 
761  /*--- Warning message about non-physical points ---*/
762 
763  if (config->GetConsole_Output_Verb() == VERB_HIGH) {
764 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
765  SU2_MPI::Reduce(&counter_local, &counter_global, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
766 #else
767  counter_global = counter_local;
768 #endif
769  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (counter_global != 0))
770  cout << "Warning. The original solution contains "<< counter_global << " points that are not physical." << endl;
771  }
772 
773  }
774 
775  /*--- Define solver parameters needed for execution of destructor ---*/
776 
777  if (config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_Flow() == SPACE_CENTERED ) space_centered = true;
778  else space_centered = false;
779 
780  if (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT) euler_implicit = true;
781  else euler_implicit = false;
782 
783  if (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method() == WEIGHTED_LEAST_SQUARES) least_squares = true;
784  else least_squares = false;
785 
786  /*--- Perform the MPI communication of the solution ---*/
787 
788  Set_MPI_Solution(geometry, config);
789 
790 }
791

917 void CEulerSolver::Set_MPI_Solution(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
918  unsigned short iVar, iMarker, iPeriodic_Index, MarkerS, MarkerR;
919  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, nVertexS, nVertexR, nBufferS_Vector, nBufferR_Vector;
920  su2double rotMatrix[3][3], *angles, theta, cosTheta, sinTheta, phi, cosPhi, sinPhi, psi, cosPsi, sinPsi, *Buffer_Receive_U = NULL, *Buffer_Send_U = NULL;
921 
922 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
923  int send_to, receive_from;
924  MPI_Status status;
925 #endif
926 
927  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
928 
929  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SEND_RECEIVE) &&
930  (config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(iMarker) > 0)) {
931 
932  MarkerS = iMarker; MarkerR = iMarker+1;
933 
934 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
935  send_to = config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerS)-1;
936  receive_from = abs(config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerR))-1;
937 #endif
938 
939  nVertexS = geometry->nVertex[MarkerS]; nVertexR = geometry->nVertex[MarkerR];
940  nBufferS_Vector = nVertexS*nVar; nBufferR_Vector = nVertexR*nVar;
941 
942  /*--- Allocate Receive and send buffers ---*/
943  Buffer_Receive_U = new su2double [nBufferR_Vector];
944  Buffer_Send_U = new su2double[nBufferS_Vector];
945 
946  /*--- Copy the solution that should be sended ---*/
947  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexS; iVertex++) {
948  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerS][iVertex]->GetNode();
949  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
950  Buffer_Send_U[iVar*nVertexS+iVertex] = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iVar);
951  }
952 
953 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
954 
955  /*--- Send/Receive information using Sendrecv ---*/
956  SU2_MPI::Sendrecv(Buffer_Send_U, nBufferS_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, send_to, 0,
957  Buffer_Receive_U, nBufferR_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, receive_from, 0, MPI_COMM_WORLD, &status);
958 
959 #else
960 
961  /*--- Receive information without MPI ---*/
962  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
963  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
964  Buffer_Receive_U[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] = Buffer_Send_U[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
965  }
966 
967 #endif
968 
969  /*--- Deallocate send buffer ---*/
970  delete [] Buffer_Send_U;
971 
972  /*--- Do the coordinate transformation ---*/
973  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
974 
975  /*--- Find point and its type of transformation ---*/
976  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetNode();
977  iPeriodic_Index = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type();
978 
979  /*--- Retrieve the supplied periodic information. ---*/
980  angles = config->GetPeriodicRotation(iPeriodic_Index);
981 
982  /*--- Store angles separately for clarity. ---*/
983  theta = angles[0]; phi = angles[1]; psi = angles[2];
984  cosTheta = cos(theta); cosPhi = cos(phi); cosPsi = cos(psi);
985  sinTheta = sin(theta); sinPhi = sin(phi); sinPsi = sin(psi);
986 
987  /*--- Compute the rotation matrix. Note that the implicit
988  ordering is rotation about the x-axis, y-axis,
989  then z-axis. Note that this is the transpose of the matrix
990  used during the preprocessing stage. ---*/
991  rotMatrix[0][0] = cosPhi*cosPsi; rotMatrix[1][0] = sinTheta*sinPhi*cosPsi - cosTheta*sinPsi; rotMatrix[2][0] = cosTheta*sinPhi*cosPsi + sinTheta*sinPsi;
992  rotMatrix[0][1] = cosPhi*sinPsi; rotMatrix[1][1] = sinTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi + cosTheta*cosPsi; rotMatrix[2][1] = cosTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi - sinTheta*cosPsi;
993  rotMatrix[0][2] = -sinPhi; rotMatrix[1][2] = sinTheta*cosPhi; rotMatrix[2][2] = cosTheta*cosPhi;
994 
995  /*--- Copy conserved variables before performing transformation. ---*/
996  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
997  Solution[iVar] = Buffer_Receive_U[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
998 
999  /*--- Rotate the momentum components. ---*/
1000  if (nDim == 2) {
1001  Solution[1] = rotMatrix[0][0]*Buffer_Receive_U[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1002  rotMatrix[0][1]*Buffer_Receive_U[2*nVertexR+iVertex];
1003  Solution[2] = rotMatrix[1][0]*Buffer_Receive_U[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1004  rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_U[2*nVertexR+iVertex];
1005  }
1006  else {
1007  Solution[1] = rotMatrix[0][0]*Buffer_Receive_U[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1008  rotMatrix[0][1]*Buffer_Receive_U[2*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1009  rotMatrix[0][2]*Buffer_Receive_U[3*nVertexR+iVertex];
1010  Solution[2] = rotMatrix[1][0]*Buffer_Receive_U[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1011  rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_U[2*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1012  rotMatrix[1][2]*Buffer_Receive_U[3*nVertexR+iVertex];
1013  Solution[3] = rotMatrix[2][0]*Buffer_Receive_U[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1014  rotMatrix[2][1]*Buffer_Receive_U[2*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1015  rotMatrix[2][2]*Buffer_Receive_U[3*nVertexR+iVertex];
1016  }
1017 
1018  /*--- Copy transformed conserved variables back into buffer. ---*/
1019  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1020  node[iPoint]->SetSolution(iVar, Solution[iVar]);
1021 
1022  }
1023 
1024  /*--- Deallocate receive buffer ---*/
1025  delete [] Buffer_Receive_U;
1026 
1027  }
1028 
1029  }
1030 
1031 }
1032 
1033 void CEulerSolver::Set_MPI_Solution_Old(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
1034  unsigned short iVar, iMarker, iPeriodic_Index, MarkerS, MarkerR;
1035  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, nVertexS, nVertexR, nBufferS_Vector, nBufferR_Vector;
1036  su2double rotMatrix[3][3], *angles, theta, cosTheta, sinTheta, phi, cosPhi, sinPhi, psi, cosPsi, sinPsi,
1037  *Buffer_Receive_U = NULL, *Buffer_Send_U = NULL;
1038 
1039 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1040  int send_to, receive_from;
1041  MPI_Status status;
1042 #endif
1043 
1044  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1045 
1046  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SEND_RECEIVE) &&
1047  (config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(iMarker) > 0)) {
1048 
1049  MarkerS = iMarker; MarkerR = iMarker+1;
1050 
1051 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1052  send_to = config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerS)-1;
1053  receive_from = abs(config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerR))-1;
1054 #endif
1055 
1056  nVertexS = geometry->nVertex[MarkerS]; nVertexR = geometry->nVertex[MarkerR];
1057  nBufferS_Vector = nVertexS*nVar; nBufferR_Vector = nVertexR*nVar;
1058 
1059  /*--- Allocate Receive and send buffers ---*/
1060  Buffer_Receive_U = new su2double [nBufferR_Vector];
1061  Buffer_Send_U = new su2double[nBufferS_Vector];
1062 
1063  /*--- Copy the solution old that should be sended ---*/
1064  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexS; iVertex++) {
1065  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerS][iVertex]->GetNode();
1066  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1067  Buffer_Send_U[iVar*nVertexS+iVertex] = node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Old(iVar);
1068  }
1069 
1070 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1071 
1072  /*--- Send/Receive information using Sendrecv ---*/
1073  SU2_MPI::Sendrecv(Buffer_Send_U, nBufferS_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, send_to, 0,
1074  Buffer_Receive_U, nBufferR_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, receive_from, 0, MPI_COMM_WORLD, &status);
1075 
1076 #else
1077 
1078  /*--- Receive information without MPI ---*/
1079  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
1080  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1081  Buffer_Receive_U[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] = Buffer_Send_U[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1082  }
1083 
1084 #endif
1085 
1086  /*--- Deallocate send buffer ---*/
1087  delete [] Buffer_Send_U;
1088 
1089  /*--- Do the coordinate transformation ---*/
1090  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
1091 
1092  /*--- Find point and its type of transformation ---*/
1093  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetNode();
1094  iPeriodic_Index = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type();
1095 
1096  /*--- Retrieve the supplied periodic information. ---*/
1097  angles = config->GetPeriodicRotation(iPeriodic_Index);
1098 
1099  /*--- Store angles separately for clarity. ---*/
1100  theta = angles[0]; phi = angles[1]; psi = angles[2];
1101  cosTheta = cos(theta); cosPhi = cos(phi); cosPsi = cos(psi);
1102  sinTheta = sin(theta); sinPhi = sin(phi); sinPsi = sin(psi);
1103 
1104  /*--- Compute the rotation matrix. Note that the implicit
1105  ordering is rotation about the x-axis, y-axis,
1106  then z-axis. Note that this is the transpose of the matrix
1107  used during the preprocessing stage. ---*/
1108  rotMatrix[0][0] = cosPhi*cosPsi; rotMatrix[1][0] = sinTheta*sinPhi*cosPsi - cosTheta*sinPsi; rotMatrix[2][0] = cosTheta*sinPhi*cosPsi + sinTheta*sinPsi;
1109  rotMatrix[0][1] = cosPhi*sinPsi; rotMatrix[1][1] = sinTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi + cosTheta*cosPsi; rotMatrix[2][1] = cosTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi - sinTheta*cosPsi;
1110  rotMatrix[0][2] = -sinPhi; rotMatrix[1][2] = sinTheta*cosPhi; rotMatrix[2][2] = cosTheta*cosPhi;
1111 
1112  /*--- Copy conserved variables before performing transformation. ---*/
1113  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1114  Solution[iVar] = Buffer_Receive_U[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1115 
1116  /*--- Rotate the momentum components. ---*/
1117  if (nDim == 2) {
1118  Solution[1] = rotMatrix[0][0]*Buffer_Receive_U[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1119  rotMatrix[0][1]*Buffer_Receive_U[2*nVertexR+iVertex];
1120  Solution[2] = rotMatrix[1][0]*Buffer_Receive_U[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1121  rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_U[2*nVertexR+iVertex];
1122  }
1123  else {
1124  Solution[1] = rotMatrix[0][0]*Buffer_Receive_U[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1125  rotMatrix[0][1]*Buffer_Receive_U[2*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1126  rotMatrix[0][2]*Buffer_Receive_U[3*nVertexR+iVertex];
1127  Solution[2] = rotMatrix[1][0]*Buffer_Receive_U[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1128  rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_U[2*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1129  rotMatrix[1][2]*Buffer_Receive_U[3*nVertexR+iVertex];
1130  Solution[3] = rotMatrix[2][0]*Buffer_Receive_U[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1131  rotMatrix[2][1]*Buffer_Receive_U[2*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1132  rotMatrix[2][2]*Buffer_Receive_U[3*nVertexR+iVertex];
1133  }
1134 
1135  /*--- Copy transformed conserved variables back into buffer. ---*/
1136  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1137  node[iPoint]->SetSolution_Old(iVar, Solution[iVar]);
1138 
1139  }
1140 
1141  /*--- Deallocate receive buffer ---*/
1142  delete [] Buffer_Receive_U;
1143 
1144  }
1145 
1146  }
1147 }

1149 void CEulerSolver::Set_MPI_Undivided_Laplacian(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
1150  unsigned short iVar, iMarker, iPeriodic_Index, MarkerS, MarkerR;
1151  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, nVertexS, nVertexR, nBufferS_Vector, nBufferR_Vector;
1152  su2double rotMatrix[3][3], *angles, theta, cosTheta, sinTheta, phi, cosPhi, sinPhi, psi, cosPsi, sinPsi,
1153  *Buffer_Receive_Undivided_Laplacian = NULL, *Buffer_Send_Undivided_Laplacian = NULL;
1154

1156  int send_to, receive_from;
1157  MPI_Status status;
1158 #endif
1159 
1160  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1161 
1162  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SEND_RECEIVE) &&
1163  (config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(iMarker) > 0)) {
1164

1166

1169  receive_from = abs(config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerR))-1;
1170 #endif

1184  }

1197  Buffer_Receive_Undivided_Laplacian[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] = Buffer_Send_Undivided_Laplacian[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1198  }
1199 
1200 #endif
1201

1203  delete [] Buffer_Send_Undivided_Laplacian;
1204

1210  iPeriodic_Index = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type();
1211

1213  angles = config->GetPeriodicRotation(iPeriodic_Index);
1214

1217  cosTheta = cos(theta); cosPhi = cos(phi); cosPsi = cos(psi);
1218  sinTheta = sin(theta); sinPhi = sin(phi); sinPsi = sin(psi);
1219

1225  rotMatrix[0][1] = cosPhi*sinPsi; rotMatrix[1][1] = sinTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi + cosTheta*cosPsi; rotMatrix[2][1] = cosTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi - sinTheta*cosPsi;

1237  rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_Undivided_Laplacian[2*nVertexR+iVertex];
1238  }

1266 void CEulerSolver::Set_MPI_MaxEigenvalue(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
1267  unsigned short iMarker, MarkerS, MarkerR, *Buffer_Receive_Neighbor = NULL, *Buffer_Send_Neighbor = NULL;
1268  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, nVertexS, nVertexR, nBufferS_Vector, nBufferR_Vector;
1269  su2double *Buffer_Receive_Lambda = NULL, *Buffer_Send_Lambda = NULL;
1270 
1271 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1272  int send_to, receive_from;
1273  MPI_Status status;
1274 #endif
1275 
1276  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1277 
1278  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SEND_RECEIVE) &&
1279  (config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(iMarker) > 0)) {
1280 
1281  MarkerS = iMarker; MarkerR = iMarker+1;
1282 
1283 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1284  send_to = config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerS)-1;
1285  receive_from = abs(config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerR))-1;
1286 #endif
1287 
1288  nVertexS = geometry->nVertex[MarkerS]; nVertexR = geometry->nVertex[MarkerR];
1289  nBufferS_Vector = nVertexS; nBufferR_Vector = nVertexR;
1290 
1291  /*--- Allocate Receive and send buffers ---*/
1292  Buffer_Receive_Lambda = new su2double [nBufferR_Vector];
1293  Buffer_Send_Lambda = new su2double[nBufferS_Vector];
1294  Buffer_Receive_Neighbor = new unsigned short [nBufferR_Vector];
1295  Buffer_Send_Neighbor = new unsigned short[nBufferS_Vector];
1296 
1297  /*--- Copy the solution old that should be sended ---*/
1298  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexS; iVertex++) {
1299  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerS][iVertex]->GetNode();
1300  Buffer_Send_Lambda[iVertex] = node[iPoint]->GetLambda();
1301  Buffer_Send_Neighbor[iVertex] = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetnPoint();
1302  }
1303 
1304 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1305 
1306  /*--- Send/Receive information using Sendrecv ---*/
1307  SU2_MPI::Sendrecv(Buffer_Send_Lambda, nBufferS_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, send_to, 0,
1308  Buffer_Receive_Lambda, nBufferR_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, receive_from, 0, MPI_COMM_WORLD, &status);
1309  SU2_MPI::Sendrecv(Buffer_Send_Neighbor, nBufferS_Vector, MPI_UNSIGNED_SHORT, send_to, 1,
1310  Buffer_Receive_Neighbor, nBufferR_Vector, MPI_UNSIGNED_SHORT, receive_from, 1, MPI_COMM_WORLD, &status);
1311 
1312 #else
1313 
1314  /*--- Receive information without MPI ---*/
1315  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
1316  Buffer_Receive_Lambda[iVertex] = Buffer_Send_Lambda[iVertex];
1317  Buffer_Receive_Neighbor[iVertex] = Buffer_Send_Neighbor[iVertex];
1318  }
1319 
1320 #endif
1321 
1322  /*--- Deallocate send buffer ---*/
1323  delete [] Buffer_Send_Lambda;
1324  delete [] Buffer_Send_Neighbor;
1325 
1326  /*--- Do the coordinate transformation ---*/
1327  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
1328 
1329  /*--- Find point and its type of transformation ---*/
1330  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetNode();
1331  node[iPoint]->SetLambda(Buffer_Receive_Lambda[iVertex]);
1332  geometry->node[iPoint]->SetnNeighbor(Buffer_Receive_Neighbor[iVertex]);
1333 
1334  }
1335 
1336  /*--- Deallocate receive buffer ---*/
1337  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Lambda;
1338  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Neighbor;
1339 
1340  }
1341 
1342  }
1343 }

1415 void CEulerSolver::Set_MPI_Solution_Gradient(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
1416  unsigned short iVar, iDim, iMarker, iPeriodic_Index, MarkerS, MarkerR;
1417  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, nVertexS, nVertexR, nBufferS_Vector, nBufferR_Vector;
1418  su2double rotMatrix[3][3], *angles, theta, cosTheta, sinTheta, phi, cosPhi, sinPhi, psi, cosPsi, sinPsi,
1419  *Buffer_Receive_Gradient = NULL, *Buffer_Send_Gradient = NULL;
1420 
1421  su2double **Gradient = new su2double* [nVar];
1422  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1423  Gradient[iVar] = new su2double[nDim];
1424 
1425 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1426  int send_to, receive_from;
1427  MPI_Status status;
1428 #endif
1429 
1430  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1431 
1432  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SEND_RECEIVE) &&
1433  (config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(iMarker) > 0)) {
1434 
1435  MarkerS = iMarker; MarkerR = iMarker+1;
1436 
1437 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1438  send_to = config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerS)-1;
1439  receive_from = abs(config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerR))-1;
1440 #endif
1441 
1442  nVertexS = geometry->nVertex[MarkerS]; nVertexR = geometry->nVertex[MarkerR];
1443  nBufferS_Vector = nVertexS*nVar*nDim; nBufferR_Vector = nVertexR*nVar*nDim;
1444 
1445  /*--- Allocate Receive and send buffers ---*/
1446  Buffer_Receive_Gradient = new su2double [nBufferR_Vector];
1447  Buffer_Send_Gradient = new su2double[nBufferS_Vector];
1448 
1449  /*--- Copy the solution old that should be sended ---*/
1450  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexS; iVertex++) {
1451  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerS][iVertex]->GetNode();
1452  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1453  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1454  Buffer_Send_Gradient[iDim*nVar*nVertexS+iVar*nVertexS+iVertex] = node[iPoint]->GetGradient(iVar, iDim);
1455  }
1456 
1457 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1458 
1459  /*--- Send/Receive information using Sendrecv ---*/
1460  SU2_MPI::Sendrecv(Buffer_Send_Gradient, nBufferS_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, send_to, 0,
1461  Buffer_Receive_Gradient, nBufferR_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, receive_from, 0, MPI_COMM_WORLD, &status);
1462 
1463 #else
1464 
1465  /*--- Receive information without MPI ---*/
1466  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
1467  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1468  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1469  Buffer_Receive_Gradient[iDim*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] = Buffer_Send_Gradient[iDim*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1470  }
1471 
1472 #endif
1473 
1474  /*--- Deallocate send buffer ---*/
1475  delete [] Buffer_Send_Gradient;
1476 
1477  /*--- Do the coordinate transformation ---*/
1478  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
1479 
1480  /*--- Find point and its type of transformation ---*/
1481  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetNode();
1482  iPeriodic_Index = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type();
1483 
1484  /*--- Retrieve the supplied periodic information. ---*/
1485  angles = config->GetPeriodicRotation(iPeriodic_Index);
1486 
1487  /*--- Store angles separately for clarity. ---*/
1488  theta = angles[0]; phi = angles[1]; psi = angles[2];
1489  cosTheta = cos(theta); cosPhi = cos(phi); cosPsi = cos(psi);
1490  sinTheta = sin(theta); sinPhi = sin(phi); sinPsi = sin(psi);
1491 
1492  /*--- Compute the rotation matrix. Note that the implicit
1493  ordering is rotation about the x-axis, y-axis,
1494  then z-axis. Note that this is the transpose of the matrix
1495  used during the preprocessing stage. ---*/
1496  rotMatrix[0][0] = cosPhi*cosPsi; rotMatrix[1][0] = sinTheta*sinPhi*cosPsi - cosTheta*sinPsi; rotMatrix[2][0] = cosTheta*sinPhi*cosPsi + sinTheta*sinPsi;
1497  rotMatrix[0][1] = cosPhi*sinPsi; rotMatrix[1][1] = sinTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi + cosTheta*cosPsi; rotMatrix[2][1] = cosTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi - sinTheta*cosPsi;
1498  rotMatrix[0][2] = -sinPhi; rotMatrix[1][2] = sinTheta*cosPhi; rotMatrix[2][2] = cosTheta*cosPhi;
1499 
1500  /*--- Copy conserved variables before performing transformation. ---*/
1501  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1502  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1503  Gradient[iVar][iDim] = Buffer_Receive_Gradient[iDim*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1504 
1505  /*--- Need to rotate the gradients for all conserved variables. ---*/
1506  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1507  if (nDim == 2) {
1508  Gradient[iVar][0] = rotMatrix[0][0]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[0*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[0][1]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[1*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1509  Gradient[iVar][1] = rotMatrix[1][0]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[0*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[1*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1510  }
1511  else {
1512  Gradient[iVar][0] = rotMatrix[0][0]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[0*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[0][1]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[1*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[0][2]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[2*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1513  Gradient[iVar][1] = rotMatrix[1][0]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[0*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[1*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[1][2]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[2*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1514  Gradient[iVar][2] = rotMatrix[2][0]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[0*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[2][1]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[1*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[2][2]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[2*nVar*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1515  }
1516  }
1517 
1518  /*--- Store the received information ---*/
1519  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1520  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1521  node[iPoint]->SetGradient(iVar, iDim, Gradient[iVar][iDim]);
1522 
1523  }
1524 
1525  /*--- Deallocate receive buffer ---*/
1526  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Gradient;
1527 
1528  }
1529 
1530  }
1531 
1532  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1533  delete [] Gradient[iVar];
1534  delete [] Gradient;
1535 
1536 }
1537 
1538 void CEulerSolver::Set_MPI_Solution_Limiter(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
1539  unsigned short iVar, iMarker, iPeriodic_Index, MarkerS, MarkerR;
1540  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, nVertexS, nVertexR, nBufferS_Vector, nBufferR_Vector;
1541  su2double rotMatrix[3][3], *angles, theta, cosTheta, sinTheta, phi, cosPhi, sinPhi, psi, cosPsi, sinPsi,
1542  *Buffer_Receive_Limit = NULL, *Buffer_Send_Limit = NULL;
1543 
1544  su2double *Limiter = new su2double [nVar];
1545 
1546 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1547  int send_to, receive_from;
1548  MPI_Status status;
1549 #endif
1550 
1551  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1552 
1553  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SEND_RECEIVE) &&
1554  (config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(iMarker) > 0)) {
1555 
1556  MarkerS = iMarker; MarkerR = iMarker+1;
1557 
1558 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1559  send_to = config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerS)-1;
1560  receive_from = abs(config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerR))-1;
1561 #endif
1562 
1563  nVertexS = geometry->nVertex[MarkerS]; nVertexR = geometry->nVertex[MarkerR];
1564  nBufferS_Vector = nVertexS*nVar; nBufferR_Vector = nVertexR*nVar;
1565 
1566  /*--- Allocate Receive and send buffers ---*/
1567  Buffer_Receive_Limit = new su2double [nBufferR_Vector];
1568  Buffer_Send_Limit = new su2double[nBufferS_Vector];
1569 
1570  /*--- Copy the solution old that should be sended ---*/
1571  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexS; iVertex++) {
1572  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerS][iVertex]->GetNode();
1573  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1574  Buffer_Send_Limit[iVar*nVertexS+iVertex] = node[iPoint]->GetLimiter(iVar);
1575  }
1576 
1577 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1578 
1579  /*--- Send/Receive information using Sendrecv ---*/
1580  SU2_MPI::Sendrecv(Buffer_Send_Limit, nBufferS_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, send_to, 0,
1581  Buffer_Receive_Limit, nBufferR_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, receive_from, 0, MPI_COMM_WORLD, &status);
1582 
1583 #else
1584 
1585  /*--- Receive information without MPI ---*/
1586  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
1587  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1588  Buffer_Receive_Limit[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] = Buffer_Send_Limit[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1589  }
1590 
1591 #endif
1592 
1593  /*--- Deallocate send buffer ---*/
1594  delete [] Buffer_Send_Limit;
1595 
1596  /*--- Do the coordinate transformation ---*/
1597  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
1598 
1599  /*--- Find point and its type of transformation ---*/
1600  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetNode();
1601  iPeriodic_Index = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type();
1602 
1603  /*--- Retrieve the supplied periodic information. ---*/
1604  angles = config->GetPeriodicRotation(iPeriodic_Index);
1605 
1606  /*--- Store angles separately for clarity. ---*/
1607  theta = angles[0]; phi = angles[1]; psi = angles[2];
1608  cosTheta = cos(theta); cosPhi = cos(phi); cosPsi = cos(psi);
1609  sinTheta = sin(theta); sinPhi = sin(phi); sinPsi = sin(psi);
1610 
1611  /*--- Compute the rotation matrix. Note that the implicit
1612  ordering is rotation about the x-axis, y-axis,
1613  then z-axis. Note that this is the transpose of the matrix
1614  used during the preprocessing stage. ---*/
1615  rotMatrix[0][0] = cosPhi*cosPsi; rotMatrix[1][0] = sinTheta*sinPhi*cosPsi - cosTheta*sinPsi; rotMatrix[2][0] = cosTheta*sinPhi*cosPsi + sinTheta*sinPsi;
1616  rotMatrix[0][1] = cosPhi*sinPsi; rotMatrix[1][1] = sinTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi + cosTheta*cosPsi; rotMatrix[2][1] = cosTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi - sinTheta*cosPsi;
1617  rotMatrix[0][2] = -sinPhi; rotMatrix[1][2] = sinTheta*cosPhi; rotMatrix[2][2] = cosTheta*cosPhi;
1618 
1619  /*--- Copy conserved variables before performing transformation. ---*/
1620  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1621  Limiter[iVar] = Buffer_Receive_Limit[iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1622 
1623  /*--- Rotate the momentum components. ---*/
1624  if (nDim == 2) {
1625  Limiter[1] = rotMatrix[0][0]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1626  rotMatrix[0][1]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[2*nVertexR+iVertex];
1627  Limiter[2] = rotMatrix[1][0]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1628  rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[2*nVertexR+iVertex];
1629  }
1630  else {
1631  Limiter[1] = rotMatrix[0][0]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1632  rotMatrix[0][1]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[2*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1633  rotMatrix[0][2]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[3*nVertexR+iVertex];
1634  Limiter[2] = rotMatrix[1][0]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1635  rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[2*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1636  rotMatrix[1][2]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[3*nVertexR+iVertex];
1637  Limiter[3] = rotMatrix[2][0]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[1*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1638  rotMatrix[2][1]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[2*nVertexR+iVertex] +
1639  rotMatrix[2][2]*Buffer_Receive_Limit[3*nVertexR+iVertex];
1640  }
1641 
1642  /*--- Copy transformed conserved variables back into buffer. ---*/
1643  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1644  node[iPoint]->SetLimiter(iVar, Limiter[iVar]);
1645 
1646  }
1647 
1648  /*--- Deallocate receive buffer ---*/
1649  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Limit;
1650 
1651  }
1652 
1653  }
1654 
1655  delete [] Limiter;
1656 
1657 }
1658 
1659 void CEulerSolver::Set_MPI_Primitive_Gradient(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
1660  unsigned short iVar, iDim, iMarker, iPeriodic_Index, MarkerS, MarkerR;
1661  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, nVertexS, nVertexR, nBufferS_Vector, nBufferR_Vector;
1662  su2double rotMatrix[3][3], *angles, theta, cosTheta, sinTheta, phi, cosPhi, sinPhi, psi, cosPsi, sinPsi,
1663  *Buffer_Receive_Gradient = NULL, *Buffer_Send_Gradient = NULL;
1664 
1665  su2double **Gradient = new su2double* [nPrimVarGrad];
1666  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++)
1667  Gradient[iVar] = new su2double[nDim];
1668 
1669 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1670  int send_to, receive_from;
1671  MPI_Status status;
1672 #endif
1673 
1674  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1675 
1676  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == SEND_RECEIVE) &&
1677  (config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(iMarker) > 0)) {
1678 
1679  MarkerS = iMarker; MarkerR = iMarker+1;
1680 
1681 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1682  send_to = config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerS)-1;
1683  receive_from = abs(config->GetMarker_All_SendRecv(MarkerR))-1;
1684 #endif
1685 
1686  nVertexS = geometry->nVertex[MarkerS]; nVertexR = geometry->nVertex[MarkerR];
1687  nBufferS_Vector = nVertexS*nPrimVarGrad*nDim; nBufferR_Vector = nVertexR*nPrimVarGrad*nDim;
1688 
1689  /*--- Allocate Receive and send buffers ---*/
1690  Buffer_Receive_Gradient = new su2double [nBufferR_Vector];
1691  Buffer_Send_Gradient = new su2double[nBufferS_Vector];
1692 
1693  /*--- Copy the solution old that should be sended ---*/
1694  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexS; iVertex++) {
1695  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerS][iVertex]->GetNode();
1696  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++)
1697  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1698  Buffer_Send_Gradient[iDim*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexS+iVar*nVertexS+iVertex] = node[iPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive(iVar, iDim);
1699  }
1700 
1701 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
1702 
1703  /*--- Send/Receive information using Sendrecv ---*/
1704  SU2_MPI::Sendrecv(Buffer_Send_Gradient, nBufferS_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, send_to, 0,
1705  Buffer_Receive_Gradient, nBufferR_Vector, MPI_DOUBLE, receive_from, 0, MPI_COMM_WORLD, &status);
1706 
1707 #else
1708 
1709  /*--- Receive information without MPI ---*/
1710  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
1711  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++)
1712  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1713  Buffer_Receive_Gradient[iDim*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] = Buffer_Send_Gradient[iDim*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1714  }
1715 
1716 #endif
1717 
1718  /*--- Deallocate send buffer ---*/
1719  delete [] Buffer_Send_Gradient;
1720 
1721  /*--- Do the coordinate transformation ---*/
1722  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertexR; iVertex++) {
1723 
1724  /*--- Find point and its type of transformation ---*/
1725  iPoint = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetNode();
1726  iPeriodic_Index = geometry->vertex[MarkerR][iVertex]->GetRotation_Type();
1727 
1728  /*--- Retrieve the supplied periodic information. ---*/
1729  angles = config->GetPeriodicRotation(iPeriodic_Index);
1730 
1731  /*--- Store angles separately for clarity. ---*/
1732  theta = angles[0]; phi = angles[1]; psi = angles[2];
1733  cosTheta = cos(theta); cosPhi = cos(phi); cosPsi = cos(psi);
1734  sinTheta = sin(theta); sinPhi = sin(phi); sinPsi = sin(psi);
1735 
1736  /*--- Compute the rotation matrix. Note that the implicit
1737  ordering is rotation about the x-axis, y-axis,
1738  then z-axis. Note that this is the transpose of the matrix
1739  used during the preprocessing stage. ---*/
1740  rotMatrix[0][0] = cosPhi*cosPsi; rotMatrix[1][0] = sinTheta*sinPhi*cosPsi - cosTheta*sinPsi; rotMatrix[2][0] = cosTheta*sinPhi*cosPsi + sinTheta*sinPsi;
1741  rotMatrix[0][1] = cosPhi*sinPsi; rotMatrix[1][1] = sinTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi + cosTheta*cosPsi; rotMatrix[2][1] = cosTheta*sinPhi*sinPsi - sinTheta*cosPsi;
1742  rotMatrix[0][2] = -sinPhi; rotMatrix[1][2] = sinTheta*cosPhi; rotMatrix[2][2] = cosTheta*cosPhi;
1743 
1744  /*--- Copy conserved variables before performing transformation. ---*/
1745  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++)
1746  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1747  Gradient[iVar][iDim] = Buffer_Receive_Gradient[iDim*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1748 
1749  /*--- Need to rotate the gradients for all conserved variables. ---*/
1750  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
1751  if (nDim == 2) {
1752  Gradient[iVar][0] = rotMatrix[0][0]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[0*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[0][1]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[1*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1753  Gradient[iVar][1] = rotMatrix[1][0]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[0*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[1*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1754  }
1755  else {
1756  Gradient[iVar][0] = rotMatrix[0][0]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[0*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[0][1]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[1*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[0][2]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[2*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1757  Gradient[iVar][1] = rotMatrix[1][0]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[0*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[1][1]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[1*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[1][2]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[2*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1758  Gradient[iVar][2] = rotMatrix[2][0]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[0*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[2][1]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[1*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex] + rotMatrix[2][2]*Buffer_Receive_Gradient[2*nPrimVarGrad*nVertexR+iVar*nVertexR+iVertex];
1759  }
1760  }
1761 
1762  /*--- Store the received information ---*/
1763  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++)
1764  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1765  node[iPoint]->SetGradient_Primitive(iVar, iDim, Gradient[iVar][iDim]);
1766 
1767  }
1768 
1769  /*--- Deallocate receive buffer ---*/
1770  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Gradient;
1771 
1772  }
1773 
1774  }
1775 
1776  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++)
1777  delete [] Gradient[iVar];
1778  delete [] Gradient;
1779 
1780 }

2108 void CEulerSolver::SetNondimensionalization(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
2109 
2110  su2double Temperature_FreeStream = 0.0, Mach2Vel_FreeStream = 0.0, ModVel_FreeStream = 0.0,
2111  Energy_FreeStream = 0.0, ModVel_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Velocity_Reynolds = 0.0,
2112  Omega_FreeStream = 0.0, Omega_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Viscosity_FreeStream = 0.0,
2113  Density_FreeStream = 0.0, Pressure_FreeStream = 0.0, Tke_FreeStream = 0.0,
2114  Length_Ref = 0.0, Density_Ref = 0.0, Pressure_Ref = 0.0, Velocity_Ref = 0.0,
2115  Temperature_Ref = 0.0, Time_Ref = 0.0, Omega_Ref = 0.0, Force_Ref = 0.0,
2116  Gas_Constant_Ref = 0.0, Viscosity_Ref = 0.0, Conductivity_Ref = 0.0, Energy_Ref= 0.0,
2117  Froude = 0.0, Pressure_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Density_FreeStreamND = 0.0,
2118  Temperature_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Gas_ConstantND = 0.0,
2119  Velocity_FreeStreamND[3] = {0.0, 0.0, 0.0}, Viscosity_FreeStreamND = 0.0,
2120  Tke_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Energy_FreeStreamND = 0.0,
2121  Total_UnstTimeND = 0.0, Delta_UnstTimeND = 0.0, TgammaR = 0.0;
2122 
2123  unsigned short iDim;
2124 
2125  int rank = MASTER_NODE;
2126 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
2127  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
2128 #endif
2129 
2130  /*--- Local variables ---*/
2131 
2132  su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
2133  su2double Beta = config->GetAoS()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
2134  su2double Mach = config->GetMach();
2135  su2double Reynolds = config->GetReynolds();
2136  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
2137  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
2138  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
2139  bool unsteady = (config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() != NO);
2140  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
2141  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
2142  bool gravity = config->GetGravityForce();
2143  bool turbulent = (config->GetKind_Solver() == RANS) || (config->GetKind_Solver() == DISC_ADJ_RANS);
2144  bool tkeNeeded = ((turbulent) && (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == SST));
2145  bool free_stream_temp = (config->GetKind_FreeStreamOption() == TEMPERATURE_FS);
2146  bool standard_air = (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == STANDARD_AIR);
2147  bool reynolds_init = (config->GetKind_InitOption() == REYNOLDS);
2148  bool aeroelastic = config->GetAeroelastic_Simulation();
2149 
2150  /*--- Set temperature via the flutter speed index ---*/
2151  if (aeroelastic) {
2152  su2double vf = config->GetAeroelastic_Flutter_Speed_Index();
2153  su2double w_alpha = config->GetAeroelastic_Frequency_Pitch();
2154  su2double b = config->GetLength_Reynolds()/2.0; // airfoil semichord, Reynolds length is by defaul 1.0
2155  su2double mu = config->GetAeroelastic_Airfoil_Mass_Ratio();
2156  // The temperature times gamma times the gas constant. Depending on the FluidModel temp is calculated below.
2157  TgammaR = ((vf*vf)*(b*b)*(w_alpha*w_alpha)*mu) / (Mach*Mach);
2158  }
2159 
2160  /*--- Compressible non dimensionalization ---*/
2161 
2162  if (compressible) {
2163 
2164  /*--- Compute the Free Stream velocity, using the Mach number ---*/
2165 
2166  Pressure_FreeStream = config->GetPressure_FreeStream();
2167  Density_FreeStream = config->GetDensity_FreeStream();
2168  Temperature_FreeStream = config->GetTemperature_FreeStream();
2169 
2170  switch (config->GetKind_FluidModel()) {
2171 
2172  case STANDARD_AIR:
2173 
2174  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) config->SetGas_Constant(287.058);
2175  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) config->SetGas_Constant(1716.49);
2176 
2177  FluidModel = new CIdealGas(1.4, config->GetGas_Constant());
2178  if (free_stream_temp) {
2179  if (aeroelastic) {
2180  Temperature_FreeStream = TgammaR / (config->GetGas_Constant()*1.4);
2181  config->SetTemperature_FreeStream(Temperature_FreeStream);
2182  }
2183  FluidModel->SetTDState_PT(Pressure_FreeStream, Temperature_FreeStream);
2184  Density_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetDensity();
2185  config->SetDensity_FreeStream(Density_FreeStream);
2186  }
2187  else {
2188  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_FreeStream, Density_FreeStream );
2189  Temperature_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetTemperature();
2190  config->SetTemperature_FreeStream(Temperature_FreeStream);
2191  }
2192  break;
2193 
2194  case IDEAL_GAS:
2195 
2196  FluidModel = new CIdealGas(Gamma, config->GetGas_Constant());
2197  if (free_stream_temp) {
2198  FluidModel->SetTDState_PT(Pressure_FreeStream, Temperature_FreeStream);
2199  Density_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetDensity();
2200  config->SetDensity_FreeStream(Density_FreeStream);
2201  }
2202  else {
2203  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_FreeStream, Density_FreeStream );
2204  Temperature_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetTemperature();
2205  config->SetTemperature_FreeStream(Temperature_FreeStream);
2206  }
2207  break;
2208 
2209  case VW_GAS:
2210 
2211  FluidModel = new CVanDerWaalsGas(Gamma, config->GetGas_Constant(),
2212  config->GetPressure_Critical(), config->GetTemperature_Critical());
2213  if (free_stream_temp) {
2214  FluidModel->SetTDState_PT(Pressure_FreeStream, Temperature_FreeStream);
2215  Density_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetDensity();
2216  config->SetDensity_FreeStream(Density_FreeStream);
2217  }
2218  else {
2219  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_FreeStream, Density_FreeStream );
2220  Temperature_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetTemperature();
2221  config->SetTemperature_FreeStream(Temperature_FreeStream);
2222  }
2223  break;
2224 
2225  case PR_GAS:
2226 
2227  FluidModel = new CPengRobinson(Gamma, config->GetGas_Constant(), config->GetPressure_Critical(),
2228  config->GetTemperature_Critical(), config->GetAcentric_Factor());
2229  if (free_stream_temp) {
2230  FluidModel->SetTDState_PT(Pressure_FreeStream, Temperature_FreeStream);
2231  Density_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetDensity();
2232  config->SetDensity_FreeStream(Density_FreeStream);
2233  }
2234  else {
2235  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_FreeStream, Density_FreeStream );
2236  Temperature_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetTemperature();
2237  config->SetTemperature_FreeStream(Temperature_FreeStream);
2238  }
2239  break;
2240 
2241  }
2242 
2243  Mach2Vel_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
2244 
2245  /*--- Compute the Free Stream velocity, using the Mach number ---*/
2246 
2247  if (nDim == 2) {
2248  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0] = cos(Alpha)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
2249  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1] = sin(Alpha)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
2250  }
2251  if (nDim == 3) {
2252  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0] = cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
2253  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1] = sin(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
2254  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[2] = sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
2255  }
2256 
2257  /*--- Compute the modulus of the free stream velocity ---*/
2258 
2259  ModVel_FreeStream = 0.0;
2260  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2261  ModVel_FreeStream += config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim]*config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim];
2262  ModVel_FreeStream = sqrt(ModVel_FreeStream); config->SetModVel_FreeStream(ModVel_FreeStream);
2263 
2264  /*--- Viscous initialization ---*/
2265 
2266  if (viscous) {
2267 
2268  /*--- Reynolds based initialization ---*/
2269 
2270  if (reynolds_init) {
2271 
2272  /*--- First, check if there is mesh motion. If yes, use the Mach
2273  number relative to the body to initialize the flow. ---*/
2274 
2275  if (grid_movement) Velocity_Reynolds = config->GetMach_Motion()*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
2276  else Velocity_Reynolds = ModVel_FreeStream;
2277 
2278  /*--- Change of measurement system, hard coded value working only with STANDAR AIR model ---*/
2279 
2280  if (standard_air) {
2281  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) {
2282  config->SetMu_RefND(1.716E-5);
2283  config->SetMu_SND(110.4);
2284  config->SetMu_Temperature_RefND(273.15);
2285  }
2286  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) {
2287  config->SetMu_RefND(3.62E-7);
2288  config->SetMu_SND(198.72);
2289  config->SetMu_Temperature_RefND(518.7);
2290  }
2291  }
2292 
2293  /*--- For viscous flows, pressure will be computed from a density
2294  that is found from the Reynolds number. The viscosity is computed
2295  from the dimensional version of Sutherland's law ---*/
2296 
2297  FluidModel->SetLaminarViscosityModel(config);
2298 
2299  Viscosity_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetLaminarViscosity();
2300  config->SetViscosity_FreeStream(Viscosity_FreeStream);
2301 
2302  Density_FreeStream = Reynolds*Viscosity_FreeStream/(Velocity_Reynolds*config->GetLength_Reynolds());
2303  config->SetDensity_FreeStream(Density_FreeStream);
2304  FluidModel->SetTDState_rhoT(Density_FreeStream, Temperature_FreeStream);
2305  Pressure_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetPressure();
2306  config->SetPressure_FreeStream(Pressure_FreeStream);
2307  Energy_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream;
2308 
2309  }
2310 
2311  /*--- Thermodynamics quantities based initialization ---*/
2312 
2313  else {
2314 
2315  FluidModel->SetLaminarViscosityModel(config);
2316  Viscosity_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetLaminarViscosity();
2317  config->SetViscosity_FreeStream(Viscosity_FreeStream);
2318  Energy_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream;
2319 
2320  }
2321 
2322  /*--- Turbulence kinetic energy ---*/
2323 
2324  Tke_FreeStream = 3.0/2.0*(ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream()*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream());
2325 
2326  }
2327  else {
2328 
2329  /*--- For inviscid flow, energy is calculated from the specified
2330  FreeStream quantities using the proper gas law. ---*/
2331 
2332  Energy_FreeStream = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream;
2333 
2334  }
2335 
2336  /*-- Compute the freestream energy. ---*/
2337 
2338  if (tkeNeeded) { Energy_FreeStream += Tke_FreeStream; }; config->SetEnergy_FreeStream(Energy_FreeStream);
2339 
2340  /*--- Compute non dimensional quantities. By definition,
2341  Lref is one because we have converted the grid to meters. ---*/
2342 
2343  if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == DIMENSIONAL) {
2344  Pressure_Ref = 1.0;
2345  Density_Ref = 1.0;
2346  Temperature_Ref = 1.0;
2347  }
2348  else if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == FREESTREAM_PRESS_EQ_ONE) {
2349  Pressure_Ref = Pressure_FreeStream; // Pressure_FreeStream = 1.0
2350  Density_Ref = Density_FreeStream; // Density_FreeStream = 1.0
2351  Temperature_Ref = Temperature_FreeStream; // Temperature_FreeStream = 1.0
2352  }
2353  else if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == FREESTREAM_VEL_EQ_MACH) {
2354  Pressure_Ref = Gamma*Pressure_FreeStream; // Pressure_FreeStream = 1.0/Gamma
2355  Density_Ref = Density_FreeStream; // Density_FreeStream = 1.0
2356  Temperature_Ref = Temperature_FreeStream; // Temp_FreeStream = 1.0
2357  }
2358  else if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == FREESTREAM_VEL_EQ_ONE) {
2359  Pressure_Ref = Mach*Mach*Gamma*Pressure_FreeStream; // Pressure_FreeStream = 1.0/(Gamma*(M_inf)^2)
2360  Density_Ref = Density_FreeStream; // Density_FreeStream = 1.0
2361  Temperature_Ref = Temperature_FreeStream; // Temp_FreeStream = 1.0
2362  }
2363  config->SetPressure_Ref(Pressure_Ref);
2364  config->SetDensity_Ref(Density_Ref);
2365  config->SetTemperature_Ref(Temperature_Ref);
2366 
2367  Length_Ref = 1.0; config->SetLength_Ref(Length_Ref);
2368  Velocity_Ref = sqrt(config->GetPressure_Ref()/config->GetDensity_Ref()); config->SetVelocity_Ref(Velocity_Ref);
2369  Time_Ref = Length_Ref/Velocity_Ref; config->SetTime_Ref(Time_Ref);
2370  Omega_Ref = Velocity_Ref/Length_Ref; config->SetOmega_Ref(Omega_Ref);
2371  Force_Ref = Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref/Length_Ref; config->SetForce_Ref(Force_Ref);
2372  Gas_Constant_Ref = Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref/config->GetTemperature_Ref(); config->SetGas_Constant_Ref(Gas_Constant_Ref);
2373  Viscosity_Ref = config->GetDensity_Ref()*Velocity_Ref*Length_Ref; config->SetViscosity_Ref(Viscosity_Ref);
2374  Conductivity_Ref = Viscosity_Ref*Gas_Constant_Ref; config->SetConductivity_Ref(Conductivity_Ref);
2375  Froude = ModVel_FreeStream/sqrt(STANDART_GRAVITY*Length_Ref); config->SetFroude(Froude);
2376 
2377  }
2378 
2379  /*--- Incompressible non dimensionalization ---*/
2380 
2381  else {
2382 
2383  /*--- Reference length = 1 (by default)
2384  Reference density = liquid density or freestream
2385  Reference viscosity = liquid viscosity or freestream
2386  Reference velocity = liquid velocity or freestream
2387  Reference pressure = Reference density * Reference velocity * Reference velocity
2388  Reynolds number based on the liquid or reference viscosity ---*/
2389 
2390  Pressure_FreeStream = 0.0; config->SetPressure_FreeStream(Pressure_FreeStream);
2391  Density_FreeStream = config->GetDensity_FreeStream();
2392  ModVel_FreeStream = 0.0;
2393  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
2394  ModVel_FreeStream += config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim]*config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim];
2395  ModVel_FreeStream = sqrt(ModVel_FreeStream); config->SetModVel_FreeStream(ModVel_FreeStream);
2396 
2397  /*--- Additional reference values defined by Pref, Tref, Rho_ref. By definition,
2398  Lref is one because we have converted the grid to meters.---*/
2399 
2400  Length_Ref = config->GetLength_Reynolds(); config->SetLength_Ref(Length_Ref);
2401  Density_Ref = Density_FreeStream; config->SetDensity_Ref(Density_Ref);
2402  Velocity_Ref = ModVel_FreeStream; config->SetVelocity_Ref(Velocity_Ref);
2403  Pressure_Ref = Density_Ref*(Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref); config->SetPressure_Ref(Pressure_Ref);
2404 
2405  if (viscous) {
2406  Viscosity_FreeStream = config->GetViscosity_FreeStream();
2407  Reynolds = Density_Ref*Velocity_Ref*Length_Ref / Viscosity_FreeStream; config->SetReynolds(Reynolds);
2408  Viscosity_Ref = Viscosity_FreeStream * Reynolds; config->SetViscosity_Ref(Viscosity_Ref);
2409  }
2410 
2411  /*--- Compute Mach number ---*/
2412 
2413  Mach = ModVel_FreeStream / sqrt(config->GetBulk_Modulus()/Density_FreeStream); config->SetMach(Mach);
2414 
2415  /*--- Compute Alpha angle ---*/
2416 
2417  if (nDim == 2) Alpha = atan(config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1]/config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0])*180.0/PI_NUMBER;
2418  else Alpha = atan(config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[2]/config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0])*180.0/PI_NUMBER;
2419  config->SetAoA(Alpha);
2420 
2421  /*--- Compute Beta angle ---*/
2422 
2423  if (nDim == 2) Beta = 0.0;
2424  else Beta = asin(config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1]/ModVel_FreeStream)*180.0/PI_NUMBER;
2425  config->SetAoS(Beta);
2426 
2427  /*--- Compute Froude ---*/
2428 
2429  Froude = ModVel_FreeStream/sqrt(STANDART_GRAVITY*Length_Ref); config->SetFroude(Froude);
2430  Time_Ref = Length_Ref/Velocity_Ref; config->SetTime_Ref(Time_Ref);
2431 
2432  }
2433 
2434  /*--- Divide by reference values, to compute the non-dimensional free-stream values ---*/
2435 
2436  Pressure_FreeStreamND = Pressure_FreeStream/config->GetPressure_Ref(); config->SetPressure_FreeStreamND(Pressure_FreeStreamND);
2437  Density_FreeStreamND = Density_FreeStream/config->GetDensity_Ref(); config->SetDensity_FreeStreamND(Density_FreeStreamND);
2438 
2439  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2440  Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim] = config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim]/Velocity_Ref; config->SetVelocity_FreeStreamND(Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim], iDim);
2441  }
2442 
2443  Temperature_FreeStreamND = Temperature_FreeStream/config->GetTemperature_Ref(); config->SetTemperature_FreeStreamND(Temperature_FreeStreamND);
2444 
2445  Gas_ConstantND = config->GetGas_Constant()/Gas_Constant_Ref; config->SetGas_ConstantND(Gas_ConstantND);
2446 
2447 
2448  ModVel_FreeStreamND = 0.0;
2449  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) ModVel_FreeStreamND += Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim]*Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim];
2450  ModVel_FreeStreamND = sqrt(ModVel_FreeStreamND); config->SetModVel_FreeStreamND(ModVel_FreeStreamND);
2451 
2452  Viscosity_FreeStreamND = Viscosity_FreeStream / Viscosity_Ref; config->SetViscosity_FreeStreamND(Viscosity_FreeStreamND);
2453 
2454  Tke_FreeStream = 3.0/2.0*(ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream()*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream());
2455  config->SetTke_FreeStream(Tke_FreeStream);
2456 
2457  Tke_FreeStreamND = 3.0/2.0*(ModVel_FreeStreamND*ModVel_FreeStreamND*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream()*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream());
2458  config->SetTke_FreeStreamND(Tke_FreeStreamND);
2459 
2460  Omega_FreeStream = Density_FreeStream*Tke_FreeStream/(Viscosity_FreeStream*config->GetTurb2LamViscRatio_FreeStream());
2461  config->SetOmega_FreeStream(Omega_FreeStream);
2462 
2463  Omega_FreeStreamND = Density_FreeStreamND*Tke_FreeStreamND/(Viscosity_FreeStreamND*config->GetTurb2LamViscRatio_FreeStream());
2464  config->SetOmega_FreeStreamND(Omega_FreeStreamND);
2465 
2466  /*--- Initialize the dimensionless Fluid Model that will be used to solve the dimensionless problem ---*/
2467 
2468  switch (config->GetKind_FluidModel()) {
2469 
2470  case STANDARD_AIR:
2471  FluidModel = new CIdealGas(1.4, Gas_ConstantND);
2472  FluidModel->SetEnergy_Prho(Pressure_FreeStreamND, Density_FreeStreamND);
2473  break;
2474 
2475  case IDEAL_GAS:
2476  FluidModel = new CIdealGas(Gamma, Gas_ConstantND);
2477  FluidModel->SetEnergy_Prho(Pressure_FreeStreamND, Density_FreeStreamND);
2478  break;
2479 
2480  case VW_GAS:
2481  FluidModel = new CVanDerWaalsGas(Gamma, Gas_ConstantND, config->GetPressure_Critical() /config->GetPressure_Ref(),
2482  config->GetTemperature_Critical()/config->GetTemperature_Ref());
2483  FluidModel->SetEnergy_Prho(Pressure_FreeStreamND, Density_FreeStreamND);
2484  break;
2485 
2486  case PR_GAS:
2487  FluidModel = new CPengRobinson(Gamma, Gas_ConstantND, config->GetPressure_Critical() /config->GetPressure_Ref(),
2488  config->GetTemperature_Critical()/config->GetTemperature_Ref(), config->GetAcentric_Factor());
2489  FluidModel->SetEnergy_Prho(Pressure_FreeStreamND, Density_FreeStreamND);
2490  break;
2491 
2492  }
2493 
2494  Energy_FreeStreamND = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStreamND*ModVel_FreeStreamND;
2495 
2496  if (viscous) {
2497 
2498  /*--- Constant viscosity model ---*/
2499  config->SetMu_ConstantND(config->GetMu_ConstantND()/Viscosity_Ref);
2500 
2501  /*--- Sutherland's model ---*/
2502 
2503  config->SetMu_RefND(config->GetMu_RefND()/Viscosity_Ref);
2504  config->SetMu_SND(config->GetMu_SND()/config->GetTemperature_Ref());
2505  config->SetMu_Temperature_RefND(config->GetMu_Temperature_RefND()/config->GetTemperature_Ref());
2506 
2507  /* constant thermal conductivity model */
2508  config->SetKt_ConstantND(config->GetKt_ConstantND()/Conductivity_Ref);
2509 
2510  FluidModel->SetLaminarViscosityModel(config);
2511  FluidModel->SetThermalConductivityModel(config);
2512 
2513  }
2514 
2515  if (tkeNeeded) { Energy_FreeStreamND += Tke_FreeStreamND; }; config->SetEnergy_FreeStreamND(Energy_FreeStreamND);
2516 
2517  Energy_Ref = Energy_FreeStream/Energy_FreeStreamND; config->SetEnergy_Ref(Energy_Ref);
2518 
2519  Total_UnstTimeND = config->GetTotal_UnstTime() / Time_Ref; config->SetTotal_UnstTimeND(Total_UnstTimeND);
2520  Delta_UnstTimeND = config->GetDelta_UnstTime() / Time_Ref; config->SetDelta_UnstTimeND(Delta_UnstTimeND);
2521 
2522  /*--- Write output to the console if this is the master node and first domain ---*/
2523 
2524  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (iMesh == MESH_0)) {
2525 
2526  cout.precision(6);
2527 
2528  if (compressible) {
2529  if (viscous) {
2530  cout << "Viscous flow: Computing pressure using the ideal gas law" << endl;
2531  cout << "based on the free-stream temperature and a density computed" << endl;
2532  cout << "from the Reynolds number." << endl;
2533  } else {
2534  cout << "Inviscid flow: Computing density based on free-stream" << endl;
2535  cout << "temperature and pressure using the ideal gas law." << endl;
2536  }
2537  }
2538 
2539  if (grid_movement) cout << "Force coefficients computed using MACH_MOTION." << endl;
2540  else cout << "Force coefficients computed using free-stream values." << endl;
2541 
2542  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
2543  cout << "Viscous and Inviscid flow: rho_ref, and vel_ref" << endl;
2544  cout << "are based on the free-stream values, p_ref = rho_ref*vel_ref^2." << endl;
2545  cout << "The free-stream value of the pressure is 0." << endl;
2546  cout << "Mach number: "<< config->GetMach() << ", computed using the Bulk modulus." << endl;
2547  cout << "Angle of attack (deg): "<< config->GetAoA() << ", computed using the the free-stream velocity." << endl;
2548  cout << "Side slip angle (deg): "<< config->GetAoS() << ", computed using the the free-stream velocity." << endl;
2549  if (viscous) cout << "Reynolds number: " << config->GetReynolds() << ", computed using free-stream values."<< endl;
2550  cout << "Only dimensional computation, the grid should be dimensional." << endl;
2551  }
2552 
2553  cout <<"-- Input conditions:"<< endl;
2554 
2555  if (compressible) {
2556  switch (config->GetKind_FluidModel()) {
2557 
2558  case STANDARD_AIR:
2559  cout << "Fluid Model: STANDARD_AIR "<< endl;
2560  cout << "Specific gas constant: " << config->GetGas_Constant();
2561  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " N.m/kg.K." << endl;
2562  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " lbf.ft/slug.R." << endl;
2563  cout << "Specific gas constant (non-dim): " << config->GetGas_ConstantND()<< endl;
2564  cout << "Specific Heat Ratio: "<< Gamma << endl;
2565  break;
2566 
2567  case IDEAL_GAS:
2568  cout << "Fluid Model: IDEAL_GAS "<< endl;
2569  cout << "Specific gas constant: " << config->GetGas_Constant() << " N.m/kg.K." << endl;
2570  cout << "Specific gas constant (non-dim): " << config->GetGas_ConstantND()<< endl;
2571  cout << "Specific Heat Ratio: "<< Gamma << endl;
2572  break;
2573 
2574  case VW_GAS:
2575  cout << "Fluid Model: Van der Waals "<< endl;
2576  cout << "Specific gas constant: " << config->GetGas_Constant() << " N.m/kg.K." << endl;
2577  cout << "Specific gas constant (non-dim): " << config->GetGas_ConstantND()<< endl;
2578  cout << "Specific Heat Ratio: "<< Gamma << endl;
2579  cout << "Critical Pressure: " << config->GetPressure_Critical() << " Pa." << endl;
2580  cout << "Critical Temperature: " << config->GetTemperature_Critical() << " K." << endl;
2581  cout << "Critical Pressure (non-dim): " << config->GetPressure_Critical() /config->GetPressure_Ref() << endl;
2582  cout << "Critical Temperature (non-dim) : " << config->GetTemperature_Critical() /config->GetTemperature_Ref() << endl;
2583  break;
2584 
2585  case PR_GAS:
2586  cout << "Fluid Model: Peng-Robinson "<< endl;
2587  cout << "Specific gas constant: " << config->GetGas_Constant() << " N.m/kg.K." << endl;
2588  cout << "Specific gas constant (non-dim): " << config->GetGas_ConstantND()<< endl;
2589  cout << "Specific Heat Ratio: "<< Gamma << endl;
2590  cout << "Critical Pressure: " << config->GetPressure_Critical() << " Pa." << endl;
2591  cout << "Critical Temperature: " << config->GetTemperature_Critical() << " K." << endl;
2592  cout << "Critical Pressure (non-dim): " << config->GetPressure_Critical() /config->GetPressure_Ref() << endl;
2593  cout << "Critical Temperature (non-dim) : " << config->GetTemperature_Critical() /config->GetTemperature_Ref() << endl;
2594  break;
2595 
2596  }
2597  if (viscous) {
2598  switch (config->GetKind_ViscosityModel()) {
2599 
2600  case CONSTANT_VISCOSITY:
2601  cout << "Viscosity Model: CONSTANT_VISCOSITY "<< endl;
2602  cout << "Laminar Viscosity: " << config->GetMu_ConstantND()*Viscosity_Ref;
2603  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " N.s/m^2." << endl;
2604  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " lbf.s/ft^2." << endl;
2605  cout << "Laminar Viscosity (non-dim): " << config->GetMu_ConstantND()<< endl;
2606  break;
2607 
2608  case SUTHERLAND:
2609  cout << "Viscosity Model: SUTHERLAND "<< endl;
2610  cout << "Ref. Laminar Viscosity: " << config->GetMu_RefND()*Viscosity_Ref;
2611  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " N.s/m^2." << endl;
2612  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " lbf.s/ft^2." << endl;
2613  cout << "Ref. Temperature: " << config->GetMu_Temperature_RefND()*config->GetTemperature_Ref();
2614  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " K." << endl;
2615  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " R." << endl;
2616  cout << "Sutherland Constant: "<< config->GetMu_SND()*config->GetTemperature_Ref();
2617  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " K." << endl;
2618  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " R." << endl;
2619  cout << "Laminar Viscosity (non-dim): " << config->GetMu_ConstantND()<< endl;
2620  cout << "Ref. Temperature (non-dim): " << config->GetMu_Temperature_RefND()<< endl;
2621  cout << "Sutherland constant (non-dim): "<< config->GetMu_SND()<< endl;
2622  break;
2623 
2624  }
2625  switch (config->GetKind_ConductivityModel()) {
2626 
2627  case CONSTANT_PRANDTL:
2628  cout << "Conductivity Model: CONSTANT_PRANDTL "<< endl;
2629  cout << "Prandtl: " << config->GetPrandtl_Lam()<< endl;
2630  break;
2631

2633  cout << "Conductivity Model: CONSTANT_CONDUCTIVITY "<< endl;
2634  cout << "Molecular Conductivity: " << config->GetKt_ConstantND()*Conductivity_Ref<< " W/m^2.K." << endl;
2635  cout << "Molecular Conductivity (non-dim): " << config->GetKt_ConstantND()<< endl;
2636  break;
2637 
2638  }
2639  }
2640  }
2641 
2642  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
2643  cout << "Bulk modulus: " << config->GetBulk_Modulus();
2644  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " Pa." << endl;
2645  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " psf." << endl;
2646  cout << "Artificial compressibility factor: " << config->GetArtComp_Factor();
2647  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " Pa." << endl;
2648  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " psf." << endl;
2649  }
2650 
2651  cout << "Free-stream static pressure: " << config->GetPressure_FreeStream();
2652  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " Pa." << endl;
2653  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " psf." << endl;
2654 
2655  cout << "Free-stream total pressure: " << config->GetPressure_FreeStream() * pow( 1.0+Mach*Mach*0.5*(Gamma-1.0), Gamma/(Gamma-1.0) );
2656  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " Pa." << endl;
2657  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " psf." << endl;
2658 
2659  if (compressible) {
2660  cout << "Free-stream temperature: " << config->GetTemperature_FreeStream();
2661  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " K." << endl;
2662  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " R." << endl;
2663  }
2664 
2665  cout << "Free-stream density: " << config->GetDensity_FreeStream();
2666  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " kg/m^3." << endl;
2667  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " slug/ft^3." << endl;
2668 
2669  if (nDim == 2) {
2670  cout << "Free-stream velocity: (" << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0] << ", ";
2671  cout << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1] << ")";
2672  }
2673  if (nDim == 3) {
2674  cout << "Free-stream velocity: (" << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0] << ", ";
2675  cout << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1] << ", " << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[2] << ")";
2676  }
2677  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " m/s. ";
2678  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " ft/s. ";
2679 
2680  cout << "Magnitude: " << config->GetModVel_FreeStream();
2681  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " m/s." << endl;
2682  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " ft/s." << endl;
2683 
2684  if (compressible) {
2685  cout << "Free-stream total energy per unit mass: " << config->GetEnergy_FreeStream();
2686  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " m^2/s^2." << endl;
2687  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " ft^2/s^2." << endl;
2688  }
2689 
2690  if (viscous) {
2691  cout << "Free-stream viscosity: " << config->GetViscosity_FreeStream();
2692  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " N.s/m^2." << endl;
2693  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " lbf.s/ft^2." << endl;
2694  if (turbulent) {
2695  cout << "Free-stream turb. kinetic energy per unit mass: " << config->GetTke_FreeStream();
2696  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " m^2/s^2." << endl;
2697  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " ft^2/s^2." << endl;
2698  cout << "Free-stream specific dissipation: " << config->GetOmega_FreeStream();
2699  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " 1/s." << endl;
2700  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " 1/s." << endl;
2701  }
2702  }
2703 
2704  if (unsteady) { cout << "Total time: " << config->GetTotal_UnstTime() << " s. Time step: " << config->GetDelta_UnstTime() << " s." << endl; }
2705 
2706  /*--- Print out reference values. ---*/
2707 
2708  cout <<"-- Reference values:"<< endl;
2709 
2710  if (compressible) {
2711  cout << "Reference specific gas constant: " << config->GetGas_Constant_Ref();
2712  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " N.m/kg.K." << endl;
2713  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " lbf.ft/slug.R." << endl;
2714  }
2715 
2716  cout << "Reference pressure: " << config->GetPressure_Ref();
2717  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " Pa." << endl;
2718  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " psf." << endl;
2719 
2720  if (compressible) {
2721  cout << "Reference temperature: " << config->GetTemperature_Ref();
2722  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " K." << endl;
2723  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " R." << endl;
2724  }
2725 
2726  cout << "Reference density: " << config->GetDensity_Ref();
2727  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " kg/m^3." << endl;
2728  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " slug/ft^3." << endl;
2729 
2730  cout << "Reference velocity: " << config->GetVelocity_Ref();
2731  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " m/s." << endl;
2732  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " ft/s." << endl;
2733 
2734  if (compressible) {
2735  cout << "Reference energy per unit mass: " << config->GetEnergy_Ref();
2736  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " m^2/s^2." << endl;
2737  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " ft^2/s^2." << endl;
2738  }
2739 
2740  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
2741  cout << "Reference length: " << config->GetLength_Ref();
2742  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " m." << endl;
2743  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " in." << endl;
2744  }
2745 
2746  if (viscous) {
2747  cout << "Reference viscosity: " << config->GetViscosity_Ref();
2748  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " N.s/m^2." << endl;
2749  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " lbf.s/ft^2." << endl;
2750  if (compressible){
2751  cout << "Reference conductivity: " << config->GetConductivity_Ref();
2752  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " W/m^2.K." << endl;
2753  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " lbf/ft.s.R." << endl;
2754  }
2755  }
2756 
2757 
2758  if (unsteady) cout << "Reference time: " << config->GetTime_Ref() <<" s." << endl;
2759 
2760  /*--- Print out resulting non-dim values here. ---*/
2761 
2762  cout << "-- Resulting non-dimensional state:" << endl;
2763  cout << "Mach number (non-dim): " << config->GetMach() << endl;
2764  if (viscous) {
