2766  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << " m." << endl;
2767  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << " ft." << endl;
2768  }
2769  if (gravity) {
2770  cout << "Froude number (non-dim): " << Froude << endl;
2771  cout << "Lenght of the baseline wave (non-dim): " << 2.0*PI_NUMBER*Froude*Froude << endl;
2772  }
2773 
2774  if (compressible) {
2775  cout << "Specific gas constant (non-dim): " << config->GetGas_ConstantND() << endl;
2776  cout << "Free-stream temperature (non-dim): " << config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND() << endl;
2777  }
2778 
2779  cout << "Free-stream pressure (non-dim): " << config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND() << endl;
2780 
2781  cout << "Free-stream density (non-dim): " << config->GetDensity_FreeStreamND() << endl;
2782 
2783  if (nDim == 2) {
2784  cout << "Free-stream velocity (non-dim): (" << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[0] << ", ";
2785  cout << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[1] << "). ";
2786  } else {
2787  cout << "Free-stream velocity (non-dim): (" << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[0] << ", ";
2788  cout << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[1] << ", " << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[2] << "). ";
2789  }
2790  cout << "Magnitude: " << config->GetModVel_FreeStreamND() << endl;
2791 
2792  if (compressible)
2793  cout << "Free-stream total energy per unit mass (non-dim): " << config->GetEnergy_FreeStreamND() << endl;
2794 
2795  if (viscous) {
2796  cout << "Free-stream viscosity (non-dim): " << config->GetViscosity_FreeStreamND() << endl;
2797  if (turbulent) {
2798  cout << "Free-stream turb. kinetic energy (non-dim): " << config->GetTke_FreeStreamND() << endl;
2799  cout << "Free-stream specific dissipation (non-dim): " << config->GetOmega_FreeStreamND() << endl;
2800  }
2801  }
2802 
2803  if (unsteady) {
2804  cout << "Total time (non-dim): " << config->GetTotal_UnstTimeND() << endl;
2805  cout << "Time step (non-dim): " << config->GetDelta_UnstTimeND() << endl;
2806  }
2807 
2808  cout << endl;
2809 
2810  }
2811 
2812 }
2813 
2814 void CEulerSolver::SetInitialCondition(CGeometry **geometry, CSolver ***solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned long ExtIter) {
2815 
2816  unsigned long iPoint, Point_Fine;
2817  unsigned short iMesh, iChildren, iVar, iDim;
2818  su2double Density, Pressure, yFreeSurface, PressFreeSurface, Froude, yCoord, Velx, Vely, Velz, RhoVelx, RhoVely, RhoVelz, YCoord = 0.0,
2819  ZCoord = 0.0, DensityInc, ViscosityInc, Heaviside, LevelSet, lambda, Area_Children, Area_Parent, LevelSet_Fine, epsilon,
2820  *Solution_Fine, *Solution, PressRef, yCoordRef;
2821 
2822  unsigned short nDim = geometry[MESH_0]->GetnDim();
2823  bool restart = (config->GetRestart() || config->GetRestart_Flow());
2824  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
2825  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
2826  bool rans = ((config->GetKind_Solver() == RANS) ||
2827  (config->GetKind_Solver() == ADJ_RANS) ||
2828  (config->GetKind_Solver() == DISC_ADJ_RANS));
2829  bool dual_time = ((config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() == DT_STEPPING_1ST) ||
2830  (config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() == DT_STEPPING_2ND));
2831  bool gravity = (config->GetGravityForce() == YES);
2832  bool engine_intake = config->GetEngine_Intake();
2833 
2834 
2835  /*--- Set the location and value of the free-surface ---*/
2836 
2837  if (freesurface) {
2838 
2839  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
2840 
2841  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry[iMesh]->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2842 
2843  /*--- Set initial boundary condition at iter 0 ---*/
2844 
2845  if ((ExtIter == 0) && (!restart)) {
2846 
2847  /*--- Compute the level set value in all the MG levels (basic case, distance to
2848  the Y/Z plane, and interpolate the solution to the coarse levels ---*/
2849 
2850  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
2851  YCoord = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(1);
2852  if (nDim == 2) LevelSet = YCoord - config->GetFreeSurface_Zero();
2853  else {
2854  ZCoord = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(2);
2855  LevelSet = ZCoord - config->GetFreeSurface_Zero();
2856  }
2857  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(nDim+1, LevelSet);
2858  }
2859  else {
2860  Area_Parent = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetVolume();
2861  LevelSet = 0.0;
2862  for (iChildren = 0; iChildren < geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetnChildren_CV(); iChildren++) {
2863  Point_Fine = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetChildren_CV(iChildren);
2864  Area_Children = geometry[iMesh-1]->node[Point_Fine]->GetVolume();
2865  LevelSet_Fine = solver_container[iMesh-1][FLOW_SOL]->node[Point_Fine]->GetSolution(nDim+1);
2866  LevelSet += LevelSet_Fine*Area_Children/Area_Parent;
2867  }
2868  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(nDim+1, LevelSet);
2869  }
2870 
2871  /*--- Compute the flow solution using the level set value. ---*/
2872 
2873  epsilon = config->GetFreeSurface_Thickness();
2874  Heaviside = 0.0;
2875  if (LevelSet < -epsilon) Heaviside = 1.0;
2876  if (fabs(LevelSet) <= epsilon) Heaviside = 1.0 - (0.5*(1.0+(LevelSet/epsilon)+(1.0/PI_NUMBER)*sin(PI_NUMBER*LevelSet/epsilon)));
2877  if (LevelSet > epsilon) Heaviside = 0.0;
2878 
2879  /*--- Set the value of the incompressible density for free surface flows (density ratio g/l) ---*/
2880 
2881  lambda = config->GetRatioDensity();
2882  DensityInc = (lambda + (1.0 - lambda)*Heaviside)*config->GetDensity_FreeStreamND();
2883  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetDensityInc(DensityInc);
2884 
2885  /*--- Set the value of the incompressible viscosity for free surface flows (viscosity ratio g/l) ---*/
2886 
2887  lambda = config->GetRatioViscosity();
2888  ViscosityInc = (lambda + (1.0 - lambda)*Heaviside)*config->GetViscosity_FreeStreamND();
2889  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetLaminarViscosityInc(ViscosityInc);
2890 
2891  /*--- Update solution with the new pressure ---*/
2892 
2893  yFreeSurface = config->GetFreeSurface_Zero();
2894  PressFreeSurface = solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetPressure_Inf();
2895  Density = solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc();
2896  Froude = config->GetFroude();
2897  yCoord = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(nDim-1);
2898  Pressure = PressFreeSurface + Density*((yFreeSurface-yCoord)/(Froude*Froude));
2899  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(0, Pressure);
2900 
2901  /*--- Update solution with the new velocity ---*/
2902 
2903  Velx = solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetVelocity_Inf(0);
2904  Vely = solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetVelocity_Inf(1);
2905  RhoVelx = Velx * Density; RhoVely = Vely * Density;
2906  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(1, RhoVelx);
2907  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(2, RhoVely);
2908  if (nDim == 3) {
2909  Velz = solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetVelocity_Inf(2);
2910  RhoVelz = Velz * Density;
2911  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(3, RhoVelz);
2912  }
2913 
2914  }
2915 
2916  }
2917 
2918  /*--- Set the MPI communication ---*/
2919 
2920  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->Set_MPI_Solution(geometry[iMesh], config);
2921  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->Set_MPI_Solution_Old(geometry[iMesh], config);
2922 
2923  }
2924 
2925  }
2926 
2927  /*--- Set the pressure value in simulations with gravity ---*/
2928 
2929 
2930  if (incompressible && gravity ) {
2931 
2932 
2933  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
2934 
2935  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry[iMesh]->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2936 
2937  /*--- Set initial boundary condition at iter 0 ---*/
2938 
2939  if ((ExtIter == 0) && (!restart)) {
2940 
2941  /*--- Update solution with the new pressure ---*/
2942 
2943  PressRef = solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetPressure_Inf();
2944  Density = solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetDensity_Inf();
2945  yCoordRef = 0.0;
2946  yCoord = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(nDim-1);
2947  Pressure = PressRef + Density*((yCoordRef-yCoord)/(config->GetFroude()*config->GetFroude()));
2948  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(0, Pressure);
2949 
2950  }
2951 
2952  }
2953 
2954  /*--- Set the MPI communication ---*/
2955 
2956  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->Set_MPI_Solution(geometry[iMesh], config);
2957  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->Set_MPI_Solution_Old(geometry[iMesh], config);
2958 
2959  }
2960 
2961  }
2962 
2963 
2964  /*--- Set subsonic initial condition for engine intakes ---*/
2965 
2966  if (engine_intake) {
2967 
2968  /*--- Set initial boundary condition at iteration 0 ---*/
2969 
2970  if ((ExtIter == 0) && (!restart)) {
2971 
2972  su2double Velocity_Box[3] = {0.0, 0.0, 0.0}, Velocity_BoxND[3] = {0.0, 0.0, 0.0}, Viscosity_Box,
2973  Density_Box, Density_BoxND, Pressure_Box, Pressure_BoxND, ModVel_Box, ModVel_BoxND, Energy_BoxND,
2974  T_ref = 0.0, S = 0.0, Mu_ref = 0.0, *Coord, MinCoordValues[3],
2975  MaxCoordValues[3], *Subsonic_Engine_Box;
2976 
2977  su2double Mach = 0.40;
2978  su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
2979  su2double Beta = config->GetAoS()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
2980 
2981  su2double Gamma_Minus_One = Gamma - 1.0;
2982  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_Constant();
2983 
2984  su2double Temperature_Box = config->GetTemperature_FreeStream();
2985  su2double Mach2Vel_Box = sqrt(Gamma*Gas_Constant*Temperature_Box);
2986 
2987  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
2988 
2989  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry[iMesh]->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2990 
2991  Velocity_Box[0] = cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_Box;
2992  Velocity_Box[1] = sin(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_Box;
2993  Velocity_Box[2] = sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_Box;
2994 
2995  ModVel_Box = 0.0;
2996  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2997  ModVel_Box += Velocity_Box[iDim]*Velocity_Box[iDim];
2998  }
2999  ModVel_Box = sqrt(ModVel_Box);
3000 
3001  if (config->GetViscous()) {
3002  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) { T_ref = 273.15; S = 110.4; Mu_ref = 1.716E-5; }
3003  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) { T_ref = 518.7; S = 198.72; Mu_ref = 3.62E-7; }
3004  Viscosity_Box = Mu_ref*(pow(Temperature_Box/T_ref, 1.5) * (T_ref+S)/(Temperature_Box+S));
3005  Density_Box = config->GetReynolds()*Viscosity_Box/(ModVel_Box*config->GetLength_Reynolds());
3006  Pressure_Box = Density_Box*Gas_Constant*Temperature_Box;
3007  }
3008  else {
3009  Pressure_Box = config->GetPressure_FreeStream();
3010  Density_Box = Pressure_Box/(Gas_Constant*Temperature_Box);
3011  }
3012 
3013  Density_BoxND = Density_Box/config->GetDensity_Ref();
3014  Pressure_BoxND = Pressure_Box/config->GetPressure_Ref();
3015 
3016  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3017  Velocity_BoxND[iDim] = Velocity_Box[iDim]/config->GetVelocity_Ref();
3018  }
3019 
3020  ModVel_BoxND = 0.0;
3021  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3022  ModVel_BoxND += Velocity_BoxND[iDim]*Velocity_BoxND[iDim];
3023  }
3024  ModVel_BoxND = sqrt(ModVel_BoxND);
3025 
3026  Energy_BoxND = Pressure_BoxND/(Density_BoxND*Gamma_Minus_One)+0.5*ModVel_BoxND*ModVel_BoxND;
3027 
3028  Coord = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetCoord();
3029 
3030  Subsonic_Engine_Box = config->GetSubsonic_Engine_Box();
3031 
3032  MinCoordValues[0] = Subsonic_Engine_Box[0]; MinCoordValues[1] = Subsonic_Engine_Box[1]; MinCoordValues[2] = Subsonic_Engine_Box[2];
3033  MaxCoordValues[0] = Subsonic_Engine_Box[3]; MaxCoordValues[1] = Subsonic_Engine_Box[4]; MaxCoordValues[2] = Subsonic_Engine_Box[5];
3034 
3035  if (((Coord[0] >= MinCoordValues[0]) && (Coord[0] <= MaxCoordValues[0])) &&
3036  ((Coord[1] >= MinCoordValues[1]) && (Coord[1] <= MaxCoordValues[1])) &&
3037  ((Coord[2] >= MinCoordValues[2]) && (Coord[2] <= MaxCoordValues[2]))) {
3038 
3039  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(0, Density_BoxND);
3040  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3041  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(iDim+1, Density_BoxND*Velocity_BoxND[iDim]);
3042  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(nVar-1, Density_BoxND*Energy_BoxND);
3043 
3044  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution_Old(0, Density_BoxND);
3045  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3046  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution_Old(iDim+1, Density_BoxND*Velocity_BoxND[iDim]);
3047  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution_Old(nVar-1, Density_BoxND*Energy_BoxND);
3048 
3049  }
3050 
3051  }
3052 
3053  /*--- Set the MPI communication ---*/
3054 
3055  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->Set_MPI_Solution(geometry[iMesh], config);
3056  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->Set_MPI_Solution_Old(geometry[iMesh], config);
3057 
3058  }
3059 
3060  }
3061 
3062  }
3063 
3064  /*--- If restart solution, then interpolate the flow solution to
3065  all the multigrid levels, this is important with the dual time strategy ---*/
3066 
3067  if (restart && (ExtIter == 0)) {
3068 
3069  Solution = new su2double[nVar];
3070  for (iMesh = 1; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
3071  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry[iMesh]->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
3072  Area_Parent = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetVolume();
3073  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Solution[iVar] = 0.0;
3074  for (iChildren = 0; iChildren < geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetnChildren_CV(); iChildren++) {
3075  Point_Fine = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetChildren_CV(iChildren);
3076  Area_Children = geometry[iMesh-1]->node[Point_Fine]->GetVolume();
3077  Solution_Fine = solver_container[iMesh-1][FLOW_SOL]->node[Point_Fine]->GetSolution();
3078  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
3079  Solution[iVar] += Solution_Fine[iVar]*Area_Children/Area_Parent;
3080  }
3081  }
3082  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(Solution);
3083  }
3084  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->Set_MPI_Solution(geometry[iMesh], config);
3085  }
3086  delete [] Solution;
3087 
3088  /*--- Interpolate the turblence variable also, if needed ---*/
3089 
3090  if (rans) {
3091 
3092  unsigned short nVar_Turb = solver_container[MESH_0][TURB_SOL]->GetnVar();
3093  Solution = new su2double[nVar_Turb];
3094  for (iMesh = 1; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
3095  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry[iMesh]->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
3096  Area_Parent = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetVolume();
3097  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Turb; iVar++) Solution[iVar] = 0.0;
3098  for (iChildren = 0; iChildren < geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetnChildren_CV(); iChildren++) {
3099  Point_Fine = geometry[iMesh]->node[iPoint]->GetChildren_CV(iChildren);
3100  Area_Children = geometry[iMesh-1]->node[Point_Fine]->GetVolume();
3101  Solution_Fine = solver_container[iMesh-1][TURB_SOL]->node[Point_Fine]->GetSolution();
3102  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_Turb; iVar++) {
3103  Solution[iVar] += Solution_Fine[iVar]*Area_Children/Area_Parent;
3104  }
3105  }
3106  solver_container[iMesh][TURB_SOL]->node[iPoint]->SetSolution(Solution);
3107  }
3108  solver_container[iMesh][TURB_SOL]->Set_MPI_Solution(geometry[iMesh], config);
3109  solver_container[iMesh][TURB_SOL]->Postprocessing(geometry[iMesh], solver_container[iMesh], config, iMesh);
3110  }
3111  delete [] Solution;
3112  }
3113 
3114  }
3115 
3116  /*--- The value of the solution for the first iteration of the dual time ---*/
3117 
3118  if (dual_time && (ExtIter == 0 || (restart && (long)ExtIter == config->GetUnst_RestartIter()))) {
3119 
3120  /*--- Push back the initial condition to previous solution containers
3121  for a 1st-order restart or when simply intitializing to freestream. ---*/
3122 
3123  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
3124  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry[iMesh]->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
3125  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->Set_Solution_time_n();
3126  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->Set_Solution_time_n1();
3127  if (rans) {
3128  solver_container[iMesh][TURB_SOL]->node[iPoint]->Set_Solution_time_n();
3129  solver_container[iMesh][TURB_SOL]->node[iPoint]->Set_Solution_time_n1();
3130  }
3131  }
3132  }
3133 
3134  if ((restart && (long)ExtIter == config->GetUnst_RestartIter()) &&
3135  (config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() == DT_STEPPING_2ND)) {
3136 
3137  /*--- Load an additional restart file for a 2nd-order restart ---*/
3138 
3139  solver_container[MESH_0][FLOW_SOL]->LoadRestart(geometry, solver_container, config, SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_RestartIter()-1));
3140 
3141  /*--- Load an additional restart file for the turbulence model ---*/
3142  if (rans)
3143  solver_container[MESH_0][TURB_SOL]->LoadRestart(geometry, solver_container, config, SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_RestartIter()-1));
3144 
3145  /*--- Push back this new solution to time level N. ---*/
3146 
3147  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
3148  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry[iMesh]->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
3149  solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->node[iPoint]->Set_Solution_time_n();
3150  if (rans) {
3151  solver_container[iMesh][TURB_SOL]->node[iPoint]->Set_Solution_time_n();
3152  }
3153  }
3154  }
3155  }
3156  }
3157 }

3159 void CEulerSolver::Preprocessing(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, unsigned short iRKStep, unsigned short RunTime_EqSystem, bool Output) {
3160 
3161  unsigned long ErrorCounter = 0;
3162 
3163 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
3164  int rank;
3165  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
3166 #endif
3167 
3168  unsigned long ExtIter = config->GetExtIter();
3169  bool adjoint = config->GetContinuous_Adjoint();
3170  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
3171  bool low_fidelity = (config->GetLowFidelitySim() && (iMesh == MESH_1));
3172  bool second_order = ((config->GetSpatialOrder_Flow() == SECOND_ORDER) || (config->GetSpatialOrder_Flow() == SECOND_ORDER_LIMITER) || (adjoint && config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_AdjFlow() == ROE));
3173  bool limiter = ((config->GetSpatialOrder_Flow() == SECOND_ORDER_LIMITER) && (!low_fidelity) && (ExtIter <= config->GetLimiterIter()));
3174  bool center = (config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_Flow() == SPACE_CENTERED) || (adjoint && config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_AdjFlow() == SPACE_CENTERED);
3175  bool center_jst = center && (config->GetKind_Centered_Flow() == JST);
3176  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
3177  bool engine = ((config->GetnMarker_EngineInflow() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_EngineBleed() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_EngineExhaust() != 0));
3178  bool actuator_disk = ((config->GetnMarker_ActDisk_Inlet() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_ActDisk_Outlet() != 0));
3179  bool fixed_cl = config->GetFixed_CL_Mode();
3180 
3181  /*--- Compute the engine properties ---*/
3182 
3183  if (engine) { GetEngine_Properties(geometry, config, iMesh, Output); }
3184 
3185  /*--- Compute the actuator disk properties ---*/
3186 
3187  if (actuator_disk) { GetActuatorDisk_Properties(geometry, config, iMesh, Output); }
3188 
3189  /*--- Update the angle of attack at the far-field for fixed CL calculations. ---*/
3190 
3191  if (fixed_cl) { SetFarfield_AoA(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Output); }
3192 
3193  /*--- Compute distance function to zero level set (Set LevelSet and Distance primitive variables)---*/
3194 
3195  if (freesurface) { SetFreeSurface_Distance(geometry, config); }
3196 
3197  /*--- Set the primitive variables ---*/
3198 
3199  ErrorCounter = SetPrimitive_Variables(solver_container, config, Output);
3200 
3201  /*--- Upwind second order reconstruction ---*/
3202 
3203  if ((second_order && !center) && ((iMesh == MESH_0) || low_fidelity) && !Output) {
3204 
3205  /*--- Gradient computation ---*/
3206 
3207  if (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method() == GREEN_GAUSS) {
3208  SetPrimitive_Gradient_GG(geometry, config);
3209  // if (compressible && !ideal_gas) SetSecondary_Gradient_GG(geometry, config);
3210  }
3211  if (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method() == WEIGHTED_LEAST_SQUARES) {
3212  SetPrimitive_Gradient_LS(geometry, config);
3213  // if (compressible && !ideal_gas) SetSecondary_Gradient_LS(geometry, config);
3214  }
3215 
3216 
3217  /*--- Limiter computation ---*/
3218 
3219  if ((limiter) && (iMesh == MESH_0) && !Output) {
3220  SetPrimitive_Limiter(geometry, config);
3221  // if (compressible && !ideal_gas) SetSecondary_Limiter(geometry, config);
3222  }
3223 
3224  }
3225 
3226  /*--- Artificial dissipation ---*/
3227 
3228  if (center && !Output) {
3229  SetMax_Eigenvalue(geometry, config);
3230  if ((center_jst) && ((iMesh == MESH_0) || low_fidelity)) {
3231  SetDissipation_Switch(geometry, config);
3232  SetUndivided_Laplacian(geometry, config);
3233  }
3234  }
3235 
3236  /*--- Initialize the Jacobian matrices ---*/
3237 
3238  if (implicit && !config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()) Jacobian.SetValZero();
3239 
3240  /*--- Error message ---*/
3241 
3242  if (config->GetConsole_Output_Verb() == VERB_HIGH) {
3243 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
3244  unsigned long MyErrorCounter = ErrorCounter; ErrorCounter = 0;
3245  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyErrorCounter, &ErrorCounter, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3246 #endif
3247  if (iMesh == MESH_0) config->SetNonphysical_Points(ErrorCounter);
3248  }
3249 
3250 }

3255 unsigned long CEulerSolver::SetPrimitive_Variables(CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config, bool Output) {
3256 
3257  unsigned long iPoint, ErrorCounter = 0;
3258  bool RightSol = true;
3259 
3260  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
3261  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
3262  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
3263 
3264  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint ++) {
3265 
3266  /*--- Initialize the non-physical points vector ---*/
3267 
3268  node[iPoint]->SetNon_Physical(false);
3269 
3270  /*--- Incompressible flow, primitive variables nDim+3, (P, vx, vy, vz, rho, beta),
3271  FreeSurface Incompressible flow, primitive variables nDim+4, (P, vx, vy, vz, rho, beta, dist),
3272  Compressible flow, primitive variables nDim+5, (T, vx, vy, vz, P, rho, h, c, lamMu, eddyMu, ThCond, Cp) ---*/
3273 
3274  if (compressible) {
3275  RightSol = node[iPoint]->SetPrimVar_Compressible(FluidModel);
3276  node[iPoint]->SetSecondaryVar_Compressible(FluidModel);
3277  }
3278 
3279  if (incompressible) {
3280  RightSol = node[iPoint]->SetPrimVar_Incompressible(Density_Inf, config);
3281  }
3282 
3283 
3284  if (freesurface){
3285  RightSol = node[iPoint]->SetPrimVar_FreeSurface(config);
3286  }
3287 
3288  if (!RightSol) { node[iPoint]->SetNon_Physical(true); ErrorCounter++; }
3289 
3290  /*--- Initialize the convective, source and viscous residual vector ---*/
3291 
3292  if (!Output) LinSysRes.SetBlock_Zero(iPoint);
3293 
3294  }
3295 
3296  return ErrorCounter;
3297 }
3298 void CEulerSolver::SetTime_Step(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config,
3299  unsigned short iMesh, unsigned long Iteration) {
3300 
3301  su2double *Normal, Area, Vol, Mean_SoundSpeed = 0.0, Mean_ProjVel = 0.0, Mean_BetaInc2, Lambda, Local_Delta_Time, Mean_DensityInc, Mean_LevelSet,
3302  Global_Delta_Time = 1E6, Global_Delta_UnstTimeND, ProjVel, ProjVel_i, ProjVel_j, Delta = 0.0, a, b, c, e, f;
3303  unsigned long iEdge, iVertex, iPoint, jPoint;
3304  unsigned short iDim, iMarker;
3305 
3306  su2double epsilon = config->GetFreeSurface_Thickness();
3307  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
3308  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
3309  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
3310  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
3311  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
3312  bool time_steping = config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() == TIME_STEPPING;
3313  bool dual_time = ((config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() == DT_STEPPING_1ST) ||
3314  (config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() == DT_STEPPING_2ND));
3315 
3316  Min_Delta_Time = 1.E6; Max_Delta_Time = 0.0;
3317 
3318  /*--- Set maximum inviscid eigenvalue to zero, and compute sound speed ---*/
3319 
3320  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++)
3321  node[iPoint]->SetMax_Lambda_Inv(0.0);
3322 
3323  /*--- Loop interior edges ---*/
3324  for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
3325 
3326  /*--- Point identification, Normal vector and area ---*/
3327 
3328  iPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(0);
3329  jPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(1);
3330 
3331  Normal = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNormal();
3332  Area = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim]; Area = sqrt(Area);
3333 
3334  /*--- Mean Values ---*/
3335 
3336  if (compressible) {
3337  Mean_ProjVel = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal) + node[jPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal));
3338  Mean_SoundSpeed = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetSoundSpeed() + node[jPoint]->GetSoundSpeed()) * Area;
3339  }
3340  if (incompressible) {
3341  Mean_ProjVel = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal) + node[jPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal));
3342  Mean_BetaInc2 = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetBetaInc2() + node[jPoint]->GetBetaInc2());
3343  Mean_DensityInc = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc() + node[jPoint]->GetDensityInc());
3344  Mean_SoundSpeed = sqrt(Mean_ProjVel*Mean_ProjVel + (Mean_BetaInc2/Mean_DensityInc)*Area*Area);
3345  }
3346  if (freesurface) {
3347  Mean_ProjVel = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal) + node[jPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal));
3348  Mean_BetaInc2 = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetBetaInc2() + node[jPoint]->GetBetaInc2());
3349  Mean_DensityInc = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc() + node[jPoint]->GetDensityInc());
3350  Mean_LevelSet = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetLevelSet() + node[jPoint]->GetLevelSet());
3351 
3352  if (Mean_LevelSet < -epsilon) Delta = 0.0;
3353  if (fabs(Mean_LevelSet) <= epsilon) Delta = 0.5*(1.0+cos(PI_NUMBER*Mean_LevelSet/epsilon))/epsilon;
3354  if (Mean_LevelSet > epsilon) Delta = 0.0;
3355 
3356  a = Mean_BetaInc2/Mean_DensityInc, b = Mean_LevelSet/Mean_DensityInc;
3357  c = (1.0 - config->GetRatioDensity())*Delta*config->GetDensity_FreeStreamND();
3358  e = (2.0*fabs(Mean_ProjVel) + b*c*fabs(Mean_ProjVel)), f = sqrt(4.0*a*Area*Area + e*e);
3359  Mean_SoundSpeed = 0.5*f;
3360  Mean_ProjVel = 0.5*e;
3361 
3362  }
3363 
3364  /*--- Adjustment for grid movement ---*/
3365 
3366  if (grid_movement) {
3367  su2double *GridVel_i = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
3368  su2double *GridVel_j = geometry->node[jPoint]->GetGridVel();
3369  ProjVel_i = 0.0; ProjVel_j = 0.0;
3370  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3371  ProjVel_i += GridVel_i[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
3372  ProjVel_j += GridVel_j[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
3373  }
3374  Mean_ProjVel -= 0.5 * (ProjVel_i + ProjVel_j);
3375  }
3376 
3377  /*--- Inviscid contribution ---*/
3378 
3379  Lambda = fabs(Mean_ProjVel) + Mean_SoundSpeed;
3380  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) node[iPoint]->AddMax_Lambda_Inv(Lambda);
3381  if (geometry->node[jPoint]->GetDomain()) node[jPoint]->AddMax_Lambda_Inv(Lambda);
3382 
3383  }
3384 
3385  /*--- Loop boundary edges ---*/
3386 
3387  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < geometry->GetnMarker(); iMarker++) {
3388  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
3389 
3390  /*--- Point identification, Normal vector and area ---*/
3391 
3392  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
3393  Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
3394  Area = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim]; Area = sqrt(Area);
3395 
3396  /*--- Mean Values ---*/
3397 
3398  if (compressible) {
3399  Mean_ProjVel = node[iPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal);
3400  Mean_SoundSpeed = node[iPoint]->GetSoundSpeed() * Area;
3401  }
3402  if (incompressible) {
3403  Mean_ProjVel = node[iPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal);
3404  Mean_BetaInc2 = node[iPoint]->GetBetaInc2();
3405  Mean_DensityInc = node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc();
3406  Mean_SoundSpeed = sqrt(Mean_ProjVel*Mean_ProjVel + (Mean_BetaInc2/Mean_DensityInc)*Area*Area);
3407  }
3408  if (freesurface) {
3409  Mean_ProjVel = node[iPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal);
3410  Mean_BetaInc2 = node[iPoint]->GetBetaInc2();
3411  Mean_DensityInc = node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc();
3412  Mean_LevelSet = node[iPoint]->GetLevelSet();
3413 
3414  if (Mean_LevelSet < -epsilon) Delta = 0.0;
3415  if (fabs(Mean_LevelSet) <= epsilon) Delta = 0.5*(1.0+cos(PI_NUMBER*Mean_LevelSet/epsilon))/epsilon;
3416  if (Mean_LevelSet > epsilon) Delta = 0.0;
3417 
3418  a = Mean_BetaInc2/Mean_DensityInc; b = Mean_LevelSet/Mean_DensityInc;
3419  c = (1.0 - config->GetRatioDensity())*Delta*config->GetDensity_FreeStreamND();
3420  e = (2.0*fabs(Mean_ProjVel) + b*c*fabs(Mean_ProjVel)); f = sqrt(4.0*a*Area*Area + e*e);
3421  Mean_SoundSpeed = 0.5*f;
3422  Mean_ProjVel = 0.5*e;
3423  }
3424 
3425  /*--- Adjustment for grid movement ---*/
3426 
3427  if (grid_movement) {
3428  su2double *GridVel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
3429  ProjVel = 0.0;
3430  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
3431  ProjVel += GridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
3432  Mean_ProjVel -= ProjVel;
3433  }
3434 
3435  /*--- Inviscid contribution ---*/
3436  Lambda = fabs(Mean_ProjVel) + Mean_SoundSpeed;
3437  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
3438  node[iPoint]->AddMax_Lambda_Inv(Lambda);
3439  }
3440 
3441  }
3442  }
3443 
3444  /*--- Each element uses their own speed, steady state simulation ---*/
3445 
3446  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
3447 
3448  Vol = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetVolume();
3449 
3450  if (Vol != 0.0) {
3451  Local_Delta_Time = config->GetCFL(iMesh)*Vol / node[iPoint]->GetMax_Lambda_Inv();
3452  Global_Delta_Time = min(Global_Delta_Time, Local_Delta_Time);
3453  Min_Delta_Time = min(Min_Delta_Time, Local_Delta_Time);
3454  Max_Delta_Time = max(Max_Delta_Time, Local_Delta_Time);
3455  if (Local_Delta_Time > config->GetMax_DeltaTime())
3456  Local_Delta_Time = config->GetMax_DeltaTime();
3457  node[iPoint]->SetDelta_Time(Local_Delta_Time);
3458  }
3459  else {
3460  node[iPoint]->SetDelta_Time(0.0);
3461  }
3462 
3463  }
3464 
3465 
3466  /*--- Compute the max and the min dt (in parallel) ---*/
3467  if (config->GetConsole_Output_Verb() == VERB_HIGH) {
3468 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
3469  su2double rbuf_time, sbuf_time;
3470  sbuf_time = Min_Delta_Time;
3471  SU2_MPI::Reduce(&sbuf_time, &rbuf_time, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_MIN, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3472  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&rbuf_time, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3473  Min_Delta_Time = rbuf_time;
3474 
3475  sbuf_time = Max_Delta_Time;
3476  SU2_MPI::Reduce(&sbuf_time, &rbuf_time, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_MAX, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3477  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&rbuf_time, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3478  Max_Delta_Time = rbuf_time;
3479 #endif
3480  }
3481 
3482  /*--- For exact time solution use the minimum delta time of the whole mesh ---*/
3483 
3484  if (time_steping) {
3485 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
3486  su2double rbuf_time, sbuf_time;
3487  sbuf_time = Global_Delta_Time;
3488  SU2_MPI::Reduce(&sbuf_time, &rbuf_time, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_MIN, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3489  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&rbuf_time, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3490  Global_Delta_Time = rbuf_time;
3491 #endif
3492  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++){
3493 
3494  /*--- Sets the regular CFL equal to the unsteady CFL ---*/
3495  config->SetCFL(iMesh,config->GetUnst_CFL());
3496 
3497  /*--- If the unsteady CFL is set to zero, it uses the defined unsteady time step, otherwise
3498  it computes the time step based on the unsteady CFL ---*/
3499  if (config->GetCFL(iMesh) == 0.0){
3500  node[iPoint]->SetDelta_Time(config->GetDelta_UnstTime());
3501  } else {
3502  node[iPoint]->SetDelta_Time(Global_Delta_Time);
3503  }
3504  }
3505  }
3506 
3507  /*--- Recompute the unsteady time step for the dual time strategy
3508  if the unsteady CFL is diferent from 0 ---*/
3509 
3510  if ((dual_time) && (Iteration == 0) && (config->GetUnst_CFL() != 0.0) && (iMesh == MESH_0)) {
3511  Global_Delta_UnstTimeND = config->GetUnst_CFL()*Global_Delta_Time/config->GetCFL(iMesh);
3512 
3513 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
3514  su2double rbuf_time, sbuf_time;
3515  sbuf_time = Global_Delta_UnstTimeND;
3516  SU2_MPI::Reduce(&sbuf_time, &rbuf_time, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_MIN, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3517  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&rbuf_time, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3518  Global_Delta_UnstTimeND = rbuf_time;
3519 #endif
3520  config->SetDelta_UnstTimeND(Global_Delta_UnstTimeND);
3521  }
3522 
3523  /*--- The pseudo local time (explicit integration) cannot be greater than the physical time ---*/
3524 
3525  if (dual_time)
3526  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
3527  if (!implicit) {
3528  Local_Delta_Time = min((2.0/3.0)*config->GetDelta_UnstTimeND(), node[iPoint]->GetDelta_Time());
3529  node[iPoint]->SetDelta_Time(Local_Delta_Time);
3530  }
3531  }
3532 
3533 }
3534 
3535 void CEulerSolver::Centered_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *numerics,
3536  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, unsigned short iRKStep) {
3537 
3538  unsigned long iEdge, iPoint, jPoint;
3539 
3540  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
3541  bool second_order = ((config->GetKind_Centered_Flow() == JST) && (iMesh == MESH_0));
3542  bool low_fidelity = (config->GetLowFidelitySim() && (iMesh == MESH_1));
3543  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
3544 
3545  for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
3546 
3547  /*--- Points in edge, set normal vectors, and number of neighbors ---*/
3548 
3549  iPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(0); jPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(1);
3550  numerics->SetNormal(geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNormal());
3551  numerics->SetNeighbor(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetnNeighbor(), geometry->node[jPoint]->GetnNeighbor());
3552 
3553  /*--- Set primitive variables w/o reconstruction ---*/
3554 
3555  numerics->SetPrimitive(node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive(), node[jPoint]->GetPrimitive());
3556 
3557  /*--- Set the largest convective eigenvalue ---*/
3558 
3559  numerics->SetLambda(node[iPoint]->GetLambda(), node[jPoint]->GetLambda());
3560 
3561  /*--- Set undivided laplacian an pressure based sensor ---*/
3562 
3563  if ((second_order || low_fidelity)) {
3564  numerics->SetUndivided_Laplacian(node[iPoint]->GetUndivided_Laplacian(), node[jPoint]->GetUndivided_Laplacian());
3565  numerics->SetSensor(node[iPoint]->GetSensor(), node[jPoint]->GetSensor());
3566  }
3567 
3568  /*--- Grid movement ---*/
3569 
3570  if (grid_movement) {
3571  numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel(), geometry->node[jPoint]->GetGridVel());
3572  }
3573 
3574  /*--- Compute residuals, and Jacobians ---*/
3575 
3576  numerics->ComputeResidual(Res_Conv, Jacobian_i, Jacobian_j, config);
3577 
3578  /*--- Update convective and artificial dissipation residuals ---*/
3579 
3580  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Res_Conv);
3581  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(jPoint, Res_Conv);
3582 
3583  /*--- Set implicit computation ---*/
3584  if (implicit) {
3585  Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
3586  Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, jPoint, Jacobian_j);
3587  Jacobian.SubtractBlock(jPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
3588  Jacobian.SubtractBlock(jPoint, jPoint, Jacobian_j);
3589  }
3590  }
3591 
3592 }
3593 
3594 void CEulerSolver::Upwind_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *numerics,
3595  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
3596 
3597  su2double **Gradient_i, **Gradient_j, Project_Grad_i, Project_Grad_j, RoeVelocity[3] = {0.0,0.0,0.0}, R, sq_vel, RoeEnthalpy,
3598  *V_i, *V_j, *S_i, *S_j, *Limiter_i = NULL, *Limiter_j = NULL, YDistance, GradHidrosPress, sqvel, Non_Physical = 1.0;
3599  unsigned long iEdge, iPoint, jPoint, counter_local = 0, counter_global = 0;
3600  unsigned short iDim, iVar;
3601  bool neg_density_i = false, neg_density_j = false, neg_pressure_i = false, neg_pressure_j = false, neg_sound_speed = false;
3602 
3603 
3604  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
3605  bool low_fidelity = (config->GetLowFidelitySim() && (iMesh == MESH_1));
3606  bool second_order = (((config->GetSpatialOrder_Flow() == SECOND_ORDER) || (config->GetSpatialOrder_Flow() == SECOND_ORDER_LIMITER)) && ((iMesh == MESH_0) || low_fidelity));
3607  bool limiter = ((config->GetSpatialOrder_Flow() == SECOND_ORDER_LIMITER) && !low_fidelity);
3608  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
3609  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
3610  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
3611  bool roe_turkel = (config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == TURKEL);
3612  bool ideal_gas = (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == STANDARD_AIR || config->GetKind_FluidModel() == IDEAL_GAS );
3613  bool low_mach_corr = config->Low_Mach_Correction();
3614 
3615  /*--- Loop over all the edges ---*/
3616 
3617  for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
3618 
3619  /*--- Points in edge and normal vectors ---*/
3620 
3621  iPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(0); jPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(1);
3622  numerics->SetNormal(geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNormal());
3623 
3624  /*--- Roe Turkel preconditioning ---*/
3625 
3626  if (roe_turkel) {
3627  sqvel = 0.0;
3628  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim ++)
3629  sqvel += config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim]*config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim];
3630  numerics->SetVelocity2_Inf(sqvel);
3631  }
3632 
3633  /*--- Grid movement ---*/
3634 
3635  if (grid_movement)
3636  numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel(), geometry->node[jPoint]->GetGridVel());
3637 
3638  /*--- Get primitive variables ---*/
3639 
3640  V_i = node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive(); V_j = node[jPoint]->GetPrimitive();
3641  S_i = node[iPoint]->GetSecondary(); S_j = node[jPoint]->GetSecondary();
3642 
3643  /*--- The zero order reconstruction includes the gradient
3644  of the hydrostatic pressure contribution ---*/
3645 
3646  if (freesurface) {
3647 
3648  YDistance = 0.5*(geometry->node[jPoint]->GetCoord(nDim-1)-geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(nDim-1));
3649  GradHidrosPress = node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc()/(config->GetFroude()*config->GetFroude());
3650  Primitive_i[0] = V_i[0] - GradHidrosPress*YDistance;
3651  GradHidrosPress = node[jPoint]->GetDensityInc()/(config->GetFroude()*config->GetFroude());
3652  Primitive_j[0] = V_j[0] + GradHidrosPress*YDistance;
3653 
3654  for (iVar = 1; iVar < nPrimVar; iVar++) {
3655  Primitive_i[iVar] = V_i[iVar]+EPS;
3656  Primitive_j[iVar] = V_j[iVar]+EPS;
3657  }
3658 
3659  }
3660 
3661  /*--- High order reconstruction using MUSCL strategy ---*/
3662 
3663  if (second_order) {
3664 
3665  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3666  Vector_i[iDim] = 0.5*(geometry->node[jPoint]->GetCoord(iDim) - geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(iDim));
3667  Vector_j[iDim] = 0.5*(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(iDim) - geometry->node[jPoint]->GetCoord(iDim));
3668  }
3669 
3670  Gradient_i = node[iPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive();
3671  Gradient_j = node[jPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive();
3672  if (limiter) {
3673  Limiter_i = node[iPoint]->GetLimiter_Primitive();
3674  Limiter_j = node[jPoint]->GetLimiter_Primitive();
3675  }
3676 
3677  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
3678  Project_Grad_i = 0.0; Project_Grad_j = 0.0;
3679  Non_Physical = node[iPoint]->GetNon_Physical()*node[jPoint]->GetNon_Physical();
3680  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3681  Project_Grad_i += Vector_i[iDim]*Gradient_i[iVar][iDim]*Non_Physical;
3682  Project_Grad_j += Vector_j[iDim]*Gradient_j[iVar][iDim]*Non_Physical;
3683  }
3684  if (limiter) {
3685  Primitive_i[iVar] = V_i[iVar] + Limiter_i[iVar]*Project_Grad_i;
3686  Primitive_j[iVar] = V_j[iVar] + Limiter_j[iVar]*Project_Grad_j;
3687  }
3688  else {
3689  Primitive_i[iVar] = V_i[iVar] + Project_Grad_i;
3690  Primitive_j[iVar] = V_j[iVar] + Project_Grad_j;
3691  }
3692  }
3693 
3694  /*--- Recompute the extrapolated quantities in a
3695  thermodynamic consistent way ---*/
3696 
3697  if (!ideal_gas || low_mach_corr) { ComputeConsExtrapolation(config); }
3698 
3699  /*--- Low-Mach number correction ---*/
3700 
3701  if (low_mach_corr) {
3702  su2double z, velocity2_i = 0.0, velocity2_j = 0.0, mach_i, mach_j, vel_i_corr[3], vel_j_corr[3];
3703 
3704  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3705  velocity2_i += Primitive_i[iDim+1]*Primitive_i[iDim+1];
3706  velocity2_j += Primitive_j[iDim+1]*Primitive_j[iDim+1];
3707  }
3708  mach_i = sqrt(velocity2_i)/Primitive_i[nDim+4];
3709  mach_j = sqrt(velocity2_j)/Primitive_j[nDim+4];
3710 
3711  z = min(max(mach_i,mach_j),1.0);
3712  velocity2_i = 0.0;
3713  velocity2_j = 0.0;
3714  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3715  vel_i_corr[iDim+1] = ( Primitive_i[iDim+1] + Primitive_j[iDim+1] )/2.0 \
3716  + z * ( Primitive_i[iDim+1] - Primitive_j[iDim+1] )/2.0;
3717  vel_j_corr[iDim+1] = ( Primitive_i[iDim+1] + Primitive_j[iDim+1] )/2.0 \
3718  + z * ( Primitive_j[iDim+1] - Primitive_i[iDim+1] )/2.0;
3719 
3720  velocity2_j += vel_j_corr[iDim+1]*vel_j_corr[iDim+1];
3721  velocity2_i += vel_i_corr[iDim+1]*vel_i_corr[iDim+1];
3722 
3723  Primitive_i[iDim+1] = vel_i_corr[iDim+1];
3724  Primitive_j[iDim+1] = vel_j_corr[iDim+1];
3725  }
3726 
3727  FluidModel->SetEnergy_Prho(Primitive_i[nDim+1],Primitive_i[nDim+2]);
3728  Primitive_i[nDim+3]= FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + Primitive_i[nDim+1]/Primitive_i[nDim+2] + 0.5*velocity2_i;
3729  FluidModel->SetEnergy_Prho(Primitive_j[nDim+1],Primitive_j[nDim+2]);
3730  Primitive_j[nDim+3]= FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + Primitive_j[nDim+1]/Primitive_j[nDim+2] + 0.5*velocity2_j;
3731  }
3732 
3733  /*--- Check for non-physical solutions after reconstruction. If found,
3734  use the cell-average value of the solution. This results in a locally
3735  first-order approximation, but this is typically only active
3736  during the start-up of a calculation. If non-physical, use the
3737  cell-averaged state. ---*/
3738 
3739  if (compressible) {
3740 
3741  neg_pressure_i = (Primitive_i[nDim+1] < 0.0); neg_pressure_j = (Primitive_j[nDim+1] < 0.0);
3742  neg_density_i = (Primitive_i[nDim+2] < 0.0); neg_density_j = (Primitive_j[nDim+2] < 0.0);
3743 
3744  R = sqrt(fabs(Primitive_j[nDim+2]/Primitive_i[nDim+2]));
3745  sq_vel = 0.0;
3746  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3747  RoeVelocity[iDim] = (R*Primitive_j[iDim+1]+Primitive_i[iDim+1])/(R+1);
3748  sq_vel += RoeVelocity[iDim]*RoeVelocity[iDim];
3749  }
3750  RoeEnthalpy = (R*Primitive_j[nDim+3]+Primitive_i[nDim+3])/(R+1);
3751  neg_sound_speed = ((Gamma-1)*(RoeEnthalpy-0.5*sq_vel) < 0.0);
3752 
3753  }
3754 
3755  if (neg_sound_speed) {
3756  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar; iVar++) {
3757  Primitive_i[iVar] = V_i[iVar];
3758  Primitive_j[iVar] = V_j[iVar]; }
3759  if (compressible) {
3760  Secondary_i[0] = S_i[0]; Secondary_i[1] = S_i[1];
3761  Secondary_j[0] = S_i[0]; Secondary_j[1] = S_i[1]; }
3762  counter_local++;
3763  }
3764 
3765  if (neg_density_i || neg_pressure_i) {
3766  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar; iVar++) Primitive_i[iVar] = V_i[iVar];
3767  if (compressible) { Secondary_i[0] = S_i[0]; Secondary_i[1] = S_i[1]; }
3768  counter_local++;
3769  }
3770 
3771  if (neg_density_j || neg_pressure_j) {
3772  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar; iVar++) Primitive_j[iVar] = V_j[iVar];
3773  if (compressible) { Secondary_j[0] = S_j[0]; Secondary_j[1] = S_j[1]; }
3774  counter_local++;
3775  }
3776 
3777  numerics->SetPrimitive(Primitive_i, Primitive_j);
3778  numerics->SetSecondary(Secondary_i, Secondary_j);
3779 
3780  }
3781  else {
3782 
3783  /*--- Set conservative variables without reconstruction ---*/
3784 
3785  numerics->SetPrimitive(V_i, V_j);
3786  numerics->SetSecondary(S_i, S_j);
3787 
3788  if (freesurface) {
3789  numerics->SetPrimitive(Primitive_i, Primitive_j);
3790  }
3791 
3792  }
3793 
3794  /*--- Compute the residual ---*/
3795 
3796  numerics->ComputeResidual(Res_Conv, Jacobian_i, Jacobian_j, config);
3797 
3798  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
3799 
3800  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Res_Conv);
3801  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(jPoint, Res_Conv);
3802 
3803  /*--- Set implicit Jacobians ---*/
3804 
3805  if (implicit) {
3806  Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
3807  Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, jPoint, Jacobian_j);
3808  Jacobian.SubtractBlock(jPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
3809  Jacobian.SubtractBlock(jPoint, jPoint, Jacobian_j);
3810  }
3811 
3812  /*--- Roe Turkel preconditioning, set the value of beta ---*/
3813 
3814  if (roe_turkel) {
3815  node[iPoint]->SetPreconditioner_Beta(numerics->GetPrecond_Beta());
3816  node[jPoint]->SetPreconditioner_Beta(numerics->GetPrecond_Beta());
3817  }
3818 
3819  }
3820 
3821  /*--- Warning message about non-physical reconstructions ---*/
3822 
3823  if (config->GetConsole_Output_Verb() == VERB_HIGH) {
3824 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
3825  SU2_MPI::Reduce(&counter_local, &counter_global, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, MASTER_NODE, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
3826 #else
3827  counter_global = counter_local;
3828 #endif
3829  if (iMesh == MESH_0) config->SetNonphysical_Reconstr(counter_global);
3830  }
3831 
3832 }
3833 
3834 void CEulerSolver::ComputeConsExtrapolation(CConfig *config) {
3835 
3836  unsigned short iDim;
3837 
3838  su2double density_i = Primitive_i[nDim+2];
3839  su2double pressure_i = Primitive_i[nDim+1];
3840  su2double velocity2_i = 0.0;
3841  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3842  velocity2_i += Primitive_i[iDim+1]*Primitive_i[iDim+1];
3843  }
3844 
3845  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(pressure_i, density_i);
3846 
3847  Primitive_i[0]= FluidModel->GetTemperature();
3848  Primitive_i[nDim+3]= FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + Primitive_i[nDim+1]/Primitive_i[nDim+2] + 0.5*velocity2_i;
3849  Primitive_i[nDim+4]= FluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
3850  Secondary_i[0]=FluidModel->GetdPdrho_e();
3851  Secondary_i[1]=FluidModel->GetdPde_rho();
3852 
3853 
3854  su2double density_j = Primitive_j[nDim+2];
3855  su2double pressure_j = Primitive_j[nDim+1];
3856  su2double velocity2_j = 0.0;
3857  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3858  velocity2_j += Primitive_j[iDim+1]*Primitive_j[iDim+1];
3859  }
3860 
3861  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(pressure_j, density_j);
3862 
3863  Primitive_j[0]= FluidModel->GetTemperature();
3864  Primitive_j[nDim+3]= FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + Primitive_j[nDim+1]/Primitive_j[nDim+2] + 0.5*velocity2_j;
3865  Primitive_j[nDim+4]=FluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
3866  Secondary_j[0]=FluidModel->GetdPdrho_e();
3867  Secondary_j[1]=FluidModel->GetdPde_rho();
3868 
3869 }

3871 void CEulerSolver::Source_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *numerics, CNumerics *second_numerics,
3872  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
3873 
3874  unsigned short iVar, jVar;
3875  unsigned long iPoint;
3876  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
3877  bool rotating_frame = config->GetRotating_Frame();
3878  bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
3879  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
3880  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
3881  bool gravity = (config->GetGravityForce() == YES);
3882  bool time_spectral = (config->GetUnsteady_Simulation() == TIME_SPECTRAL);
3883  bool windgust = config->GetWind_Gust();
3884 
3885  /*--- Initialize the source residual to zero ---*/
3886  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) Residual[iVar] = 0.0;
3887 
3888  if (rotating_frame) {
3889 
3890  /*--- Loop over all points ---*/
3891  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
3892 
3893  /*--- Load the conservative variables ---*/
3894  numerics->SetConservative(node[iPoint]->GetSolution(),
3895  node[iPoint]->GetSolution());
3896 
3897  /*--- Load the volume of the dual mesh cell ---*/
3898  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetVolume());
3899 
3900  /*--- Compute the rotating frame source residual ---*/
3901  numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual, Jacobian_i, config);
3902 
3903  /*--- Add the source residual to the total ---*/
3904  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
3905 
3906  /*--- Add the implicit Jacobian contribution ---*/
3907  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
3908 
3909  }
3910  }
3911 
3912  if (axisymmetric) {
3913 
3914  /*--- Zero out Jacobian structure ---*/
3915  if (implicit) {
3916  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar ++)
3917  for (unsigned short jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar ++)
3918  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] = 0.0;
3919  }
3920 
3921  /*--- loop over points ---*/
3922  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
3923 
3924  /*--- Set solution ---*/
3925  numerics->SetConservative(node[iPoint]->GetSolution(), node[iPoint]->GetSolution());
3926 
3927  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
3928  /*--- Set incompressible density ---*/
3929  numerics->SetDensityInc(node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc(), node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc());
3930  }
3931 
3932  /*--- Set control volume ---*/
3933  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetVolume());
3934 
3935  /*--- Set y coordinate ---*/
3936  numerics->SetCoord(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(), geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord());
3937 
3938  /*--- Compute Source term Residual ---*/
3939  numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual, Jacobian_i, config);
3940 
3941  /*--- Add Residual ---*/
3942  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
3943 
3944  /*--- Implicit part ---*/
3945  if (implicit)
3946  Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
3947  }
3948  }
3949 
3950  if (gravity) {
3951 
3952  /*--- loop over points ---*/
3953  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
3954 
3955  /*--- Set solution ---*/
3956  numerics->SetConservative(node[iPoint]->GetSolution(), node[iPoint]->GetSolution());
3957 
3958  /*--- Set incompressible density ---*/
3959  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
3960  numerics->SetDensityInc(node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc(), node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc());
3961  }
3962 
3963  /*--- Set control volume ---*/
3964  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetVolume());
3965 
3966  /*--- Compute Source term Residual ---*/
3967  numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual, config);
3968 
3969  /*--- Add Residual ---*/
3970  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
3971 
3972  }
3973 
3974  }
3975 
3976  if (freesurface) {
3977 
3978  unsigned long iPoint;
3979  su2double Vol, x_o, x_od, x, z, levelset, DampingFactor;
3980  su2double factor = config->GetFreeSurface_Damping_Length();
3981 
3982  x_o = config->GetFreeSurface_Outlet();
3983  x_od = x_o - factor*2.0*PI_NUMBER*config->GetFroude()*config->GetFroude();
3984 
3985  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
3986 
3987  Vol = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetVolume();
3988  x = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord()[0];
3989  z = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord()[nDim-1]-config->GetFreeSurface_Zero();
3990  levelset = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(nDim+1);
3991 
3992  DampingFactor = 0.0;
3993  if (x >= x_od)
3994  DampingFactor = config->GetFreeSurface_Damping_Coeff()*pow((x-x_od)/(x_o-x_od), 2.0);
3995 
3996  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
3997  Residual[iVar] = 0.0;
3998  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
3999  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] = 0.0;
4000  }
4001 
4002  Residual[nDim+1] = Vol*(levelset-z)*DampingFactor;
4003  Jacobian_i[nDim+1][nDim+1] = Vol*DampingFactor;
4004 
4005  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
4006  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
4007 
4008  }
4009 
4010  }
4011 
4012  if (time_spectral) {
4013 
4014  su2double Volume, Source;
4015 
4016  /*--- loop over points ---*/
4017  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
4018 
4019  /*--- Get control volume ---*/
4020  Volume = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetVolume();
4021 
4022  /*--- Get stored time spectral source term ---*/
4023  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4024  Source = node[iPoint]->GetTimeSpectral_Source(iVar);
4025  Residual[iVar] = Source*Volume;
4026  }
4027 
4028  /*--- Add Residual ---*/
4029  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
4030 
4031  }
4032  }
4033 
4034  if (windgust) {
4035 
4036  /*--- Loop over all points ---*/
4037  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
4038 
4039  /*--- Load the wind gust ---*/
4040  numerics->SetWindGust(node[iPoint]->GetWindGust(), node[iPoint]->GetWindGust());
4041 
4042  /*--- Load the wind gust derivatives ---*/
4043  numerics->SetWindGustDer(node[iPoint]->GetWindGustDer(), node[iPoint]->GetWindGustDer());
4044 
4045  /*--- Load the primitive variables ---*/
4046  numerics->SetPrimitive(node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive(), node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive());
4047 
4048  /*--- Load the volume of the dual mesh cell ---*/
4049  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetVolume());
4050 
4051  /*--- Compute the rotating frame source residual ---*/
4052  numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual, Jacobian_i, config);
4053 
4054  /*--- Add the source residual to the total ---*/
4055  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
4056 
4057  /*--- Add the implicit Jacobian contribution ---*/
4058  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
4059 
4060  }
4061  }
4062 
4063 }

4079 void CEulerSolver::SetMax_Eigenvalue(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
4080 
4081  su2double *Normal, Area, Mean_SoundSpeed = 0.0, Mean_ProjVel = 0.0, Mean_BetaInc2, Lambda, Mean_DensityInc,
4082  ProjVel, ProjVel_i, ProjVel_j, *GridVel, *GridVel_i, *GridVel_j;
4083  unsigned long iEdge, iVertex, iPoint, jPoint;
4084  unsigned short iDim, iMarker;
4085 
4086  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
4087  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
4088  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
4089  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
4090 
4091  /*--- Set maximum inviscid eigenvalue to zero, and compute sound speed ---*/
4092 
4093  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
4094  node[iPoint]->SetLambda(0.0);
4095  }
4096 
4097  /*--- Loop interior edges ---*/
4098 
4099  for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
4100 
4101  /*--- Point identification, Normal vector and area ---*/
4102 
4103  iPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(0);
4104  jPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(1);
4105 
4106  Normal = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNormal();
4107  Area = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim]; Area = sqrt(Area);
4108 
4109  /*--- Mean Values ---*/
4110 
4111  if (compressible) {
4112  Mean_ProjVel = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal) + node[jPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal));
4113  Mean_SoundSpeed = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetSoundSpeed() + node[jPoint]->GetSoundSpeed()) * Area;
4114  }
4115  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
4116  Mean_ProjVel = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal) + node[jPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal));
4117  Mean_BetaInc2 = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetBetaInc2() + node[jPoint]->GetBetaInc2());
4118  Mean_DensityInc = 0.5 * (node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc() + node[jPoint]->GetDensityInc());
4119  Mean_SoundSpeed = sqrt(Mean_ProjVel*Mean_ProjVel + (Mean_BetaInc2/Mean_DensityInc)*Area*Area);
4120  }
4121 
4122  /*--- Adjustment for grid movement ---*/
4123 
4124  if (grid_movement) {
4125  GridVel_i = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
4126  GridVel_j = geometry->node[jPoint]->GetGridVel();
4127  ProjVel_i = 0.0; ProjVel_j =0.0;
4128  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4129  ProjVel_i += GridVel_i[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
4130  ProjVel_j += GridVel_j[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
4131  }
4132  Mean_ProjVel -= 0.5 * (ProjVel_i + ProjVel_j);
4133  }
4134 
4135  /*--- Inviscid contribution ---*/
4136 
4137  Lambda = fabs(Mean_ProjVel) + Mean_SoundSpeed;
4138  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) node[iPoint]->AddLambda(Lambda);
4139  if (geometry->node[jPoint]->GetDomain()) node[jPoint]->AddLambda(Lambda);
4140 
4141  }
4142 
4143  /*--- Loop boundary edges ---*/
4144 
4145  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < geometry->GetnMarker(); iMarker++) {
4146  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
4147 
4148  /*--- Point identification, Normal vector and area ---*/
4149 
4150  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
4151  Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
4152  Area = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim]; Area = sqrt(Area);
4153 
4154  /*--- Mean Values ---*/
4155 
4156  if (compressible) {
4157  Mean_ProjVel = node[iPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal);
4158  Mean_SoundSpeed = node[iPoint]->GetSoundSpeed() * Area;
4159  }
4160  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
4161  Mean_ProjVel = node[iPoint]->GetProjVel(Normal);
4162  Mean_BetaInc2 = node[iPoint]->GetBetaInc2();
4163  Mean_DensityInc = node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc();
4164  Mean_SoundSpeed = sqrt(Mean_ProjVel*Mean_ProjVel + (Mean_BetaInc2/Mean_DensityInc)*Area*Area);
4165  }
4166 
4167  /*--- Adjustment for grid movement ---*/
4168 
4169  if (grid_movement) {
4170  GridVel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
4171  ProjVel = 0.0;
4172  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4173  ProjVel += GridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
4174  Mean_ProjVel -= ProjVel;
4175  }
4176 
4177  /*--- Inviscid contribution ---*/
4178 
4179  Lambda = fabs(Mean_ProjVel) + Mean_SoundSpeed;
4180  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
4181  node[iPoint]->AddLambda(Lambda);
4182  }
4183 
4184  }
4185  }
4186 
4187  /*--- MPI parallelization ---*/
4188 
4189  Set_MPI_MaxEigenvalue(geometry, config);
4190 
4191 }

4193 void CEulerSolver::SetUndivided_Laplacian(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
4194 
4195  unsigned long iPoint, jPoint, iEdge;
4196  su2double Pressure_i = 0, Pressure_j = 0, *Diff;
4197  unsigned short iVar;
4198  bool boundary_i, boundary_j;
4199 
4200  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
4201 
4202  Diff = new su2double[nVar];
4203 
4204  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++)
4205  node[iPoint]->SetUnd_LaplZero();
4206 
4207  for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
4208 
4209  iPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(0);
4210  jPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(1);
4211 
4212  /*--- Solution differences ---*/
4213 
4214  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
4215  Diff[iVar] = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iVar) - node[jPoint]->GetSolution(iVar);
4216 
4217  /*--- Correction for compressible flows which use the enthalpy ---*/
4218 
4219  if (compressible) {
4220  Pressure_i = node[iPoint]->GetPressure();
4221  Pressure_j = node[jPoint]->GetPressure();
4222  Diff[nVar-1] = (node[iPoint]->GetSolution(nVar-1) + Pressure_i) - (node[jPoint]->GetSolution(nVar-1) + Pressure_j);
4223  }
4224 
4225  boundary_i = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetPhysicalBoundary();
4226  boundary_j = geometry->node[jPoint]->GetPhysicalBoundary();
4227 
4228  /*--- Both points inside the domain, or both in the boundary ---*/
4229 
4230  if ((!boundary_i && !boundary_j) || (boundary_i && boundary_j)) {
4231  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) node[iPoint]->SubtractUnd_Lapl(Diff);
4232  if (geometry->node[jPoint]->GetDomain()) node[jPoint]->AddUnd_Lapl(Diff);
4233  }
4234 
4235  /*--- iPoint inside the domain, jPoint on the boundary ---*/
4236 
4237  if (!boundary_i && boundary_j)
4238  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) node[iPoint]->SubtractUnd_Lapl(Diff);
4239 
4240  /*--- jPoint inside the domain, iPoint on the boundary ---*/
4241 
4242  if (boundary_i && !boundary_j)
4243  if (geometry->node[jPoint]->GetDomain()) node[jPoint]->AddUnd_Lapl(Diff);
4244 
4245  }
4246 
4247  /*--- MPI parallelization ---*/
4248 
4249  Set_MPI_Undivided_Laplacian(geometry, config);
4250 
4251  delete [] Diff;
4252 
4253 }

4255 void CEulerSolver::SetDissipation_Switch(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
4256 
4257  unsigned long iEdge, iPoint, jPoint;
4258  su2double Pressure_i = 0.0, Pressure_j = 0.0;
4259  bool boundary_i, boundary_j;
4260 
4261  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
4262  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
4263  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
4264 
4265  /*--- Reset variables to store the undivided pressure ---*/
4266 
4267  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
4268  iPoint_UndLapl[iPoint] = 0.0;
4269  jPoint_UndLapl[iPoint] = 0.0;
4270  }
4271 
4272  /*--- Evaluate the pressure sensor ---*/
4273 
4274  for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
4275 
4276  iPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(0);
4277  jPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(1);
4278 
4279  /*--- Get the pressure, or density for incompressible solvers ---*/
4280 
4281  if (compressible) {
4282  Pressure_i = node[iPoint]->GetPressure();
4283  Pressure_j = node[jPoint]->GetPressure();
4284  }
4285  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
4286  Pressure_i = node[iPoint]->GetDensityInc();
4287  Pressure_j = node[jPoint]->GetDensityInc();
4288  }
4289 
4290  boundary_i = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetPhysicalBoundary();
4291  boundary_j = geometry->node[jPoint]->GetPhysicalBoundary();
4292 
4293  /*--- Both points inside the domain, or both on the boundary ---*/
4294 
4295  if ((!boundary_i && !boundary_j) || (boundary_i && boundary_j)) {
4296  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) { iPoint_UndLapl[iPoint] += (Pressure_j - Pressure_i); jPoint_UndLapl[iPoint] += (Pressure_i + Pressure_j); }
4297  if (geometry->node[jPoint]->GetDomain()) { iPoint_UndLapl[jPoint] += (Pressure_i - Pressure_j); jPoint_UndLapl[jPoint] += (Pressure_i + Pressure_j); }
4298  }
4299 
4300  /*--- iPoint inside the domain, jPoint on the boundary ---*/
4301 
4302  if (!boundary_i && boundary_j)
4303  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) { iPoint_UndLapl[iPoint] += (Pressure_j - Pressure_i); jPoint_UndLapl[iPoint] += (Pressure_i + Pressure_j); }
4304 
4305  /*--- jPoint inside the domain, iPoint on the boundary ---*/
4306 
4307  if (boundary_i && !boundary_j)
4308  if (geometry->node[jPoint]->GetDomain()) { iPoint_UndLapl[jPoint] += (Pressure_i - Pressure_j); jPoint_UndLapl[jPoint] += (Pressure_i + Pressure_j); }
4309 
4310  }
4311 
4312  /*--- Set pressure switch for each point ---*/
4313 
4314  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++)
4315  node[iPoint]->SetSensor(fabs(iPoint_UndLapl[iPoint]) / jPoint_UndLapl[iPoint]);
4316 
4317  /*--- MPI parallelization ---*/
4318 
4319  Set_MPI_Dissipation_Switch(geometry, config);
4320 
4321 }

4323 void CEulerSolver::Inviscid_Forces(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
4324 
4325  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
4326  unsigned short iDim, iMarker, Boundary, Monitoring, iMarker_Monitoring;
4327  su2double Pressure = 0.0, *Normal = NULL, MomentDist[3] = {0.0,0.0,0.0}, *Coord, Area,
4328  factor, NFPressOF, RefVel2, RefTemp, RefDensity, RefPressure, Mach2Vel, Mach_Motion,
4329  Force[3] = {0.0,0.0,0.0};
4330  string Marker_Tag, Monitoring_Tag;
4331 
4332 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
4333  su2double MyAllBound_CDrag_Inv, MyAllBound_CLift_Inv, MyAllBound_CSideForce_Inv, MyAllBound_CMx_Inv, MyAllBound_CMy_Inv, MyAllBound_CMz_Inv, MyAllBound_CFx_Inv, MyAllBound_CFy_Inv, MyAllBound_CFz_Inv, MyAllBound_CT_Inv, MyAllBound_CQ_Inv, MyAllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv, *MySurface_CLift_Inv = NULL, *MySurface_CDrag_Inv = NULL, *MySurface_CSideForce_Inv = NULL, *MySurface_CEff_Inv = NULL, *MySurface_CFx_Inv = NULL, *MySurface_CFy_Inv = NULL, *MySurface_CFz_Inv = NULL, *MySurface_CMx_Inv = NULL, *MySurface_CMy_Inv = NULL, *MySurface_CMz_Inv = NULL;
4334 #endif
4335 
4336  su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
4337  su2double Beta = config->GetAoS()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
4338  su2double RefAreaCoeff = config->GetRefAreaCoeff();
4339  su2double RefLengthMoment = config->GetRefLengthMoment();
4340  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
4341  su2double *Origin = config->GetRefOriginMoment(0);
4342  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
4343  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
4344  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
4345  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
4346 
4347  /*--- Evaluate reference values for non-dimensionalization.
4348  For dynamic meshes, use the motion Mach number as a reference value
4349  for computing the force coefficients. Otherwise, use the freestream
4350  values, which is the standard convention. ---*/
4351 
4352  RefTemp = Temperature_Inf;
4353  RefDensity = Density_Inf;
4354  RefPressure = Pressure_Inf;
4355  if (grid_movement) {
4356  Mach2Vel = sqrt(Gamma*Gas_Constant*RefTemp);
4357  Mach_Motion = config->GetMach_Motion();
4358  RefVel2 = (Mach_Motion*Mach2Vel)*(Mach_Motion*Mach2Vel);
4359  }
4360  else {
4361  RefVel2 = 0.0;
4362  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4363  RefVel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Velocity_Inf[iDim];
4364  }
4365 
4366  factor = 1.0 / (0.5*RefDensity*RefAreaCoeff*RefVel2);
4367 
4368  /*-- Variables initialization ---*/
4369 
4370  Total_CDrag = 0.0; Total_CLift = 0.0; Total_CSideForce = 0.0; Total_CEff = 0.0;
4371  Total_CMx = 0.0; Total_CMy = 0.0; Total_CMz = 0.0;
4372  Total_CFx = 0.0; Total_CFy = 0.0; Total_CFz = 0.0;
4373  Total_CT = 0.0; Total_CQ = 0.0; Total_CMerit = 0.0;
4374  Total_CNearFieldOF = 0.0; Total_Heat = 0.0; Total_MaxHeat = 0.0;
4375 
4376  AllBound_CDrag_Inv = 0.0; AllBound_CLift_Inv = 0.0; AllBound_CSideForce_Inv = 0.0;
4377  AllBound_CMx_Inv = 0.0; AllBound_CMy_Inv = 0.0; AllBound_CMz_Inv = 0.0;
4378  AllBound_CFx_Inv = 0.0; AllBound_CFy_Inv = 0.0; AllBound_CFz_Inv = 0.0;
4379  AllBound_CT_Inv = 0.0; AllBound_CQ_Inv = 0.0; AllBound_CMerit_Inv = 0.0;
4380  AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv = 0.0; AllBound_CEff_Inv = 0.0;
4381 
4382  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
4383  Surface_CLift_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0; Surface_CDrag_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4384  Surface_CSideForce_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0; Surface_CEff_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4385  Surface_CFx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0; Surface_CFy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4386  Surface_CFz_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0; Surface_CMx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4387  Surface_CMy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0; Surface_CMz_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4388  Surface_CLift[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0; Surface_CDrag[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4389  Surface_CSideForce[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0; Surface_CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4390  Surface_CFx[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0; Surface_CFy[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4391  Surface_CFz[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0; Surface_CMx[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4392  Surface_CMy[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0; Surface_CMz[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4393  }
4394 
4395  /*--- Loop over the Euler and Navier-Stokes markers ---*/
4396 
4397  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
4398 
4399  Boundary = config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker);
4400  Monitoring = config->GetMarker_All_Monitoring(iMarker);
4401 
4402  /*--- Obtain the origin for the moment computation for a particular marker ---*/
4403 
4404  if (Monitoring == YES) {
4405  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
4406  Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring(iMarker_Monitoring);
4407  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
4408  if (Marker_Tag == Monitoring_Tag)
4409  Origin = config->GetRefOriginMoment(iMarker_Monitoring);
4410  }
4411  }
4412 
4413  if ((Boundary == EULER_WALL) || (Boundary == HEAT_FLUX) ||
4414  (Boundary == ISOTHERMAL) || (Boundary == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)) {
4415 
4416  /*--- Forces initialization at each Marker ---*/
4417 
4418  CDrag_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0; CLift_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0; CSideForce_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0;
4419  CMx_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0; CMy_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0; CMz_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0;
4420  CFx_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0; CFy_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0; CFz_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0;
4421  CT_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0; CQ_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0; CMerit_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0;
4422  CNearFieldOF_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0; CEff_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0;
4423 
4424  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) ForceInviscid[iDim] = 0.0;
4425  MomentInviscid[0] = 0.0; MomentInviscid[1] = 0.0; MomentInviscid[2] = 0.0;
4426  NFPressOF = 0.0;
4427 
4428  /*--- Loop over the vertices to compute the forces ---*/
4429 
4430  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
4431 
4432  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
4433 
4434  if (compressible) Pressure = node[iPoint]->GetPressure();
4435  if (incompressible || freesurface) Pressure = node[iPoint]->GetPressureInc();
4436 
4437  CPressure[iMarker][iVertex] = (Pressure - RefPressure)*factor*RefAreaCoeff;
4438 
4439  /*--- Note that the pressure coefficient is computed at the
4440  halo cells (for visualization purposes), but not the forces ---*/
4441 
4442  if ( (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) && (Monitoring == YES) ) {
4443 
4444  Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
4445  Coord = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord();
4446 
4447  /*--- Quadratic objective function for the near-field.
4448  This uses the infinity pressure regardless of Mach number. ---*/
4449 
4450  NFPressOF += 0.5*(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Normal[nDim-1];
4451 
4452  Area = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim]; Area = sqrt(Area);
4453  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4454  MomentDist[iDim] = Coord[iDim] - Origin[iDim];
4455  }
4456 
4457  /*--- Force computation, note the minus sign due to the
4458  orientation of the normal (outward) ---*/
4459 
4460  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4461  Force[iDim] = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Normal[iDim]*factor;
4462  ForceInviscid[iDim] += Force[iDim];
4463  }
4464 
4465  /*--- Moment with respect to the reference axis ---*/
4466 
4467  if (nDim == 3) {
4468  MomentInviscid[0] += (Force[2]*MomentDist[1]-Force[1]*MomentDist[2])/RefLengthMoment;
4469  MomentInviscid[1] += (Force[0]*MomentDist[2]-Force[2]*MomentDist[0])/RefLengthMoment;
4470  }
4471  MomentInviscid[2] += (Force[1]*MomentDist[0]-Force[0]*MomentDist[1])/RefLengthMoment;
4472  }
4473 
4474  }
4475 
4476  /*--- Project forces and store the non-dimensional coefficients ---*/
4477 
4478  if (Monitoring == YES) {
4479 
4480  if (Boundary != NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY) {
4481  if (nDim == 2) {
4482  CDrag_Inv[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[0]*cos(Alpha) + ForceInviscid[1]*sin(Alpha);
4483  CLift_Inv[iMarker] = -ForceInviscid[0]*sin(Alpha) + ForceInviscid[1]*cos(Alpha);
4484  CEff_Inv[iMarker] = CLift_Inv[iMarker] / (CDrag_Inv[iMarker]+EPS);
4485  CMz_Inv[iMarker] = MomentInviscid[2];
4486  CFx_Inv[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[0];
4487  CFy_Inv[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[1];
4488  CT_Inv[iMarker] = -CFx_Inv[iMarker];
4489  CQ_Inv[iMarker] = -CMz_Inv[iMarker];
4490  CMerit_Inv[iMarker] = CT_Inv[iMarker] / (CQ_Inv[iMarker] + EPS);
4491  }
4492  if (nDim == 3) {
4493  CDrag_Inv[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[0]*cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta) + ForceInviscid[1]*sin(Beta) + ForceInviscid[2]*sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta);
4494  CLift_Inv[iMarker] = -ForceInviscid[0]*sin(Alpha) + ForceInviscid[2]*cos(Alpha);
4495  CSideForce_Inv[iMarker] = -ForceInviscid[0]*sin(Beta)*cos(Alpha) + ForceInviscid[1]*cos(Beta) - ForceInviscid[2]*sin(Beta)*sin(Alpha);
4496  CEff_Inv[iMarker] = CLift_Inv[iMarker] / (CDrag_Inv[iMarker] + EPS);
4497  CMx_Inv[iMarker] = MomentInviscid[0];
4498  CMy_Inv[iMarker] = MomentInviscid[1];
4499  CMz_Inv[iMarker] = MomentInviscid[2];
4500  CFx_Inv[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[0];
4501  CFy_Inv[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[1];
4502  CFz_Inv[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[2];
4503  CT_Inv[iMarker] = -CFz_Inv[iMarker];
4504  CQ_Inv[iMarker] = -CMz_Inv[iMarker];
4505  CMerit_Inv[iMarker] = CT_Inv[iMarker] / (CQ_Inv[iMarker] + EPS);
4506  }
4507 
4508  AllBound_CDrag_Inv += CDrag_Inv[iMarker];
4509  AllBound_CLift_Inv += CLift_Inv[iMarker];
4510  AllBound_CSideForce_Inv += CSideForce_Inv[iMarker];
4511  AllBound_CEff_Inv = AllBound_CLift_Inv / (AllBound_CDrag_Inv + EPS);
4512  AllBound_CMx_Inv += CMx_Inv[iMarker];
4513  AllBound_CMy_Inv += CMy_Inv[iMarker];
4514  AllBound_CMz_Inv += CMz_Inv[iMarker];
4515  AllBound_CFx_Inv += CFx_Inv[iMarker];
4516  AllBound_CFy_Inv += CFy_Inv[iMarker];
4517  AllBound_CFz_Inv += CFz_Inv[iMarker];
4518  AllBound_CT_Inv += CT_Inv[iMarker];
4519  AllBound_CQ_Inv += CQ_Inv[iMarker];
4520  AllBound_CMerit_Inv = AllBound_CT_Inv / (AllBound_CQ_Inv + EPS);
4521 
4522  /*--- Compute the coefficients per surface ---*/
4523 
4524  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
4525  Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring(iMarker_Monitoring);
4526  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
4527  if (Marker_Tag == Monitoring_Tag) {
4528  Surface_CLift_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] += CLift_Inv[iMarker];
4529  Surface_CDrag_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] += CDrag_Inv[iMarker];
4530  Surface_CSideForce_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] += CSideForce_Inv[iMarker];
4531  Surface_CEff_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = CLift_Inv[iMarker] / (CDrag_Inv[iMarker] + EPS);
4532  Surface_CFx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] += CFx_Inv[iMarker];
4533  Surface_CFy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] += CFy_Inv[iMarker];
4534  Surface_CFz_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] += CFz_Inv[iMarker];
4535  Surface_CMx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] += CMx_Inv[iMarker];
4536  Surface_CMy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] += CMy_Inv[iMarker];
4537  Surface_CMz_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] += CMz_Inv[iMarker];
4538  }
4539  }
4540 
4541  }
4542 
4543  /*--- At the Nearfield SU2 only cares about the pressure coeffient ---*/
4544 
4545  else {
4546  CNearFieldOF_Inv[iMarker] = NFPressOF;
4547  AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv += CNearFieldOF_Inv[iMarker];
4548  }
4549 
4550  }
4551 
4552 
4553  }
4554  }
4555 
4556 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
4557 
4558  /*--- Add AllBound information using all the nodes ---*/
4559 
4560  MyAllBound_CDrag_Inv = AllBound_CDrag_Inv; AllBound_CDrag_Inv = 0.0;
4561  MyAllBound_CLift_Inv = AllBound_CLift_Inv; AllBound_CLift_Inv = 0.0;
4562  MyAllBound_CSideForce_Inv = AllBound_CSideForce_Inv; AllBound_CSideForce_Inv = 0.0;
4563  AllBound_CEff_Inv = 0.0;
4564  MyAllBound_CMx_Inv = AllBound_CMx_Inv; AllBound_CMx_Inv = 0.0;
4565  MyAllBound_CMy_Inv = AllBound_CMy_Inv; AllBound_CMy_Inv = 0.0;
4566  MyAllBound_CMz_Inv = AllBound_CMz_Inv; AllBound_CMz_Inv = 0.0;
4567  MyAllBound_CFx_Inv = AllBound_CFx_Inv; AllBound_CFx_Inv = 0.0;
4568  MyAllBound_CFy_Inv = AllBound_CFy_Inv; AllBound_CFy_Inv = 0.0;
4569  MyAllBound_CFz_Inv = AllBound_CFz_Inv; AllBound_CFz_Inv = 0.0;
4570  MyAllBound_CT_Inv = AllBound_CT_Inv; AllBound_CT_Inv = 0.0;
4571  MyAllBound_CQ_Inv = AllBound_CQ_Inv; AllBound_CQ_Inv = 0.0;
4572  AllBound_CMerit_Inv = 0.0;
4573  MyAllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv = AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv; AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv = 0.0;
4574 
4575  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CDrag_Inv, &AllBound_CDrag_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4576  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CLift_Inv, &AllBound_CLift_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4577  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CSideForce_Inv, &AllBound_CSideForce_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4578  AllBound_CEff_Inv = AllBound_CLift_Inv / (AllBound_CDrag_Inv + EPS);
4579  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CMx_Inv, &AllBound_CMx_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4580  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CMy_Inv, &AllBound_CMy_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4581  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CMz_Inv, &AllBound_CMz_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4582  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CFx_Inv, &AllBound_CFx_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4583  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CFy_Inv, &AllBound_CFy_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4584  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CFz_Inv, &AllBound_CFz_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4585  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CT_Inv, &AllBound_CT_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4586  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CQ_Inv, &AllBound_CQ_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4587  AllBound_CMerit_Inv = AllBound_CT_Inv / (AllBound_CQ_Inv + EPS);
4588  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyAllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv, &AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4589 
4590  /*--- Add the forces on the surfaces using all the nodes ---*/
4591 
4592  MySurface_CLift_Inv = new su2double[config->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4593  MySurface_CDrag_Inv = new su2double[config->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4594  MySurface_CSideForce_Inv = new su2double[config->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4595  MySurface_CEff_Inv = new su2double[config->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4596  MySurface_CFx_Inv = new su2double[config->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4597  MySurface_CFy_Inv = new su2double[config->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4598  MySurface_CFz_Inv = new su2double[config->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4599  MySurface_CMx_Inv = new su2double[config->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4600  MySurface_CMy_Inv = new su2double[config->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4601  MySurface_CMz_Inv = new su2double[config->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
4602 
4603  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
4604  MySurface_CLift_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CLift_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4605  MySurface_CDrag_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CDrag_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4606  MySurface_CSideForce_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CSideForce_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4607  MySurface_CEff_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CEff_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4608  MySurface_CFx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CFx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4609  MySurface_CFy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CFy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4610  MySurface_CFz_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CFz_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4611  MySurface_CMx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CMx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4612  MySurface_CMy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CMy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];

4615  Surface_CLift_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4616  Surface_CDrag_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4617  Surface_CSideForce_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4618  Surface_CEff_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4619  Surface_CFx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4620  Surface_CFy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4621  Surface_CFz_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4622  Surface_CMx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4623  Surface_CMy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4624  Surface_CMz_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
4625  }
