4627  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MySurface_CLift_Inv, Surface_CLift_Inv, config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4628  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MySurface_CDrag_Inv, Surface_CDrag_Inv, config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4629  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MySurface_CSideForce_Inv, Surface_CSideForce_Inv, config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4630  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++)
4631  Surface_CEff_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CLift_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] / (Surface_CDrag_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
4632  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MySurface_CFx_Inv, Surface_CFx_Inv, config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4633  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MySurface_CFy_Inv, Surface_CFy_Inv, config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4634  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MySurface_CFz_Inv, Surface_CFz_Inv, config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4635  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MySurface_CMx_Inv, Surface_CMx_Inv, config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4636  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MySurface_CMy_Inv, Surface_CMy_Inv, config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4637  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MySurface_CMz_Inv, Surface_CMz_Inv, config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(), MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
4638 
4639  delete [] MySurface_CLift_Inv; delete [] MySurface_CDrag_Inv; delete [] MySurface_CSideForce_Inv;
4640  delete [] MySurface_CEff_Inv; delete [] MySurface_CFx_Inv; delete [] MySurface_CFy_Inv;
4641  delete [] MySurface_CFz_Inv; delete [] MySurface_CMx_Inv; delete [] MySurface_CMy_Inv;
4642  delete [] MySurface_CMz_Inv;
4643 
4644 #endif
4645 
4646  /*--- Update the total coefficients (note that all the nodes have the same value) ---*/
4647 
4648  Total_CDrag = AllBound_CDrag_Inv;
4649  Total_CLift = AllBound_CLift_Inv;
4650  Total_CSideForce = AllBound_CSideForce_Inv;
4651  Total_CEff = Total_CLift / (Total_CDrag + EPS);
4652  Total_CMx = AllBound_CMx_Inv;
4653  Total_CMy = AllBound_CMy_Inv;
4654  Total_CMz = AllBound_CMz_Inv;
4655  Total_CFx = AllBound_CFx_Inv;
4656  Total_CFy = AllBound_CFy_Inv;
4657  Total_CFz = AllBound_CFz_Inv;
4658  Total_CT = AllBound_CT_Inv;
4659  Total_CQ = AllBound_CQ_Inv;
4660  Total_CMerit = Total_CT / (Total_CQ + EPS);
4661  Total_CNearFieldOF = AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv;
4662 
4663  /*--- Update the total coefficients per surface (note that all the nodes have the same value)---*/
4664 
4665  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
4666  Surface_CLift[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CLift_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4667  Surface_CDrag[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CDrag_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4668  Surface_CSideForce[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CSideForce_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4669  Surface_CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CLift_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] / (Surface_CDrag_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
4670  Surface_CFx[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CFx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4671  Surface_CFy[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CFy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4672  Surface_CFz[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CFz_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4673  Surface_CMx[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CMx_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4674  Surface_CMy[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CMy_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4675  Surface_CMz[iMarker_Monitoring] = Surface_CMz_Inv[iMarker_Monitoring];
4676  }

4680 void CEulerSolver::TurboPerformance(CSolver *solver, CConfig *config, unsigned short inMarker, unsigned short outMarker, unsigned short Kind_TurboPerf, unsigned short inMarkerTP ){
4681 
4682  su2double avgVel2In, avgVel2Out,avgVelRel2In, avgVelRel2Out, avgGridVel2In, avgGridVel2Out, avgTotalEnthalpyIn= 0.0,avgTotalRothalpyIn,
4683  avgTotalEnthalpyOut, avgTotalRothalpyOut, avgTotalEnthalpyOutIs, avgEnthalpyOut, avgEnthalpyOutIs,
4684  avgPressureOut, avgTotalRelPressureIn, avgTotalRelPressureOut, avgEntropyIn, avgEntropyOut;
4685  unsigned short iDim;
4686 
4687 
4688  /*--- compute or retrieve inlet information ---*/
4689  avgVelRel2In= 0.0;
4690  avgGridVel2In= 0.0;
4691  avgVel2In= 0.0;
4692  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
4693  avgVelRel2In +=( AveragedVelocity[inMarker][iDim] - AveragedGridVel[inMarker][iDim])*( AveragedVelocity[inMarker][iDim] - AveragedGridVel[inMarker][iDim]);
4694  avgGridVel2In += AveragedGridVel[inMarker][iDim]*AveragedGridVel[inMarker][iDim];
4695  avgVel2In += AveragedVelocity[inMarker][iDim]*AveragedVelocity[inMarker][iDim];
4696  }
4697 
4698  avgTotalRothalpyIn = AveragedEnthalpy[inMarker] + 0.5*avgVelRel2In - 0.5*avgGridVel2In;
4699  avgTotalEnthalpyIn = AveragedEnthalpy[inMarker] + 0.5*avgVel2In;
4700  avgEntropyIn = AveragedEntropy[inMarker];
4701  FluidModel->SetTDState_hs(avgTotalRothalpyIn, avgEntropyIn);
4702  avgTotalRelPressureIn = FluidModel->GetPressure();
4703 
4704 
4705 
4706  /*--- compute or retrieve outlet information ---*/
4707  avgVelRel2Out = 0.0;
4708  avgGridVel2Out = 0.0;
4709  avgVel2Out = 0.0;
4710  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
4711  avgVelRel2Out += (solver->GetAveragedVelocity(outMarker)[iDim]- solver->GetAveragedGridVelocity(outMarker)[iDim])*(solver->GetAveragedVelocity(outMarker)[iDim]- solver->GetAveragedGridVelocity(outMarker)[iDim]);
4712  avgGridVel2Out += solver->GetAveragedGridVelocity(outMarker)[iDim]*solver->GetAveragedGridVelocity(outMarker)[iDim];
4713  avgVel2Out += solver->GetAveragedVelocity(outMarker)[iDim]*solver->GetAveragedVelocity(outMarker)[iDim];
4714  }
4715  avgTotalRothalpyOut = solver->GetAveragedEnthalpy(outMarker) + 0.5*avgVelRel2Out - 0.5*avgGridVel2Out;
4716  avgTotalEnthalpyOut = solver->GetAveragedEnthalpy(outMarker) + 0.5*avgVel2Out;
4717  avgEntropyOut = solver->GetAveragedEntropy(outMarker);
4718  avgEnthalpyOut = solver->GetAveragedEnthalpy(outMarker);
4719  FluidModel->SetTDState_hs(avgTotalRothalpyOut, avgEntropyOut);
4720  avgTotalRelPressureOut = FluidModel->GetPressure();
4721  avgPressureOut= solver->GetAveragedPressure(outMarker);
4722 
4723  /*--- compute outlet isoentropic conditions ---*/
4724  FluidModel->SetTDState_Ps(avgPressureOut, avgEntropyIn);
4725  avgEnthalpyOutIs = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + avgPressureOut/FluidModel->GetDensity();
4726  avgTotalEnthalpyOutIs = avgEnthalpyOutIs + 0.5*avgVel2Out;
4727 
4728  /*--- store turboperformance informations ---*/
4729  PressureOut[inMarkerTP] = avgPressureOut;
4730  PressureRatio[inMarkerTP] = avgTotalRelPressureIn/avgPressureOut;
4731 
4732  switch(Kind_TurboPerf){
4733  case BLADE:
4734 
4735  TotalPressureLoss[inMarkerTP] = (avgTotalRelPressureIn - avgTotalRelPressureOut)/(avgTotalRelPressureOut - avgPressureOut) ;
4736  KineticEnergyLoss[inMarkerTP] = (avgEnthalpyOut - avgEnthalpyOutIs)/(avgTotalRothalpyIn - avgEnthalpyOut + 0.5*avgGridVel2Out);
4737  EulerianWork[inMarkerTP] = avgTotalEnthalpyIn - avgTotalEnthalpyOut;
4738  TotalEnthalpyIn[inMarkerTP] = avgTotalRothalpyIn;
4739  FlowAngleIn[inMarkerTP]= FlowAngle[inMarker];
4740  FlowAngleOut[inMarkerTP]= solver->GetFlowAngle(outMarker);
4741  MassFlowIn[inMarkerTP]= MassFlow[inMarker];
4742  MassFlowOut[inMarkerTP]= solver->GetMassFlow(outMarker);
4743  MachIn[inMarkerTP]= AveragedMach[inMarker];
4744  MachOut[inMarkerTP]= solver->GetAveragedMach(outMarker);
4745  NormalMachIn[inMarkerTP]= AveragedNormalMach[inMarker];
4746  NormalMachOut[inMarkerTP]= solver->GetAveragedNormalMach(outMarker);
4747  EnthalpyOut[inMarkerTP]= avgEnthalpyOut;
4748  VelocityOutIs[inMarkerTP]=sqrt(2.0*(avgTotalRothalpyIn - avgEnthalpyOut + 0.5*avgGridVel2Out));
4749  break;
4750 
4751  case STAGE: case TURBINE:
4752 
4753  TotalTotalEfficiency[inMarkerTP] = (avgTotalEnthalpyIn - avgTotalEnthalpyOut)/(avgTotalEnthalpyIn - avgTotalEnthalpyOutIs);
4754  TotalStaticEfficiency[inMarkerTP] = (avgTotalEnthalpyIn - avgTotalEnthalpyOut)/(avgTotalEnthalpyIn - avgEnthalpyOutIs);
4755  TotalEnthalpyIn[inMarkerTP]= avgTotalEnthalpyIn;
4756  EnthalpyOut[inMarkerTP] = avgTotalEnthalpyOut;
4757  break;
4758 
4759  default:
4760  cout << "Warning! Invalid TurboPerformance option!" << endl;
4761  exit(EXIT_FAILURE);
4762  break;
4763  }
4764 
4765 
4766 
4767 
4768 
4769 }

4771 void CEulerSolver::ExplicitRK_Iteration(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
4772  CConfig *config, unsigned short iRKStep) {
4773  su2double *Residual, *Res_TruncError, Vol, Delta, Res;
4774  unsigned short iVar;
4775  unsigned long iPoint;
4776 
4777  su2double RK_AlphaCoeff = config->Get_Alpha_RKStep(iRKStep);
4778  bool adjoint = config->GetContinuous_Adjoint();
4779 
4780  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4781  SetRes_RMS(iVar, 0.0);
4782  SetRes_Max(iVar, 0.0, 0);
4783  }
4784 
4785  /*--- Update the solution ---*/
4786 
4787  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
4788  Vol = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetVolume();
4789  Delta = node[iPoint]->GetDelta_Time() / Vol;
4790 
4791  Res_TruncError = node[iPoint]->GetResTruncError();
4792  Residual = LinSysRes.GetBlock(iPoint);
4793 
4794  if (!adjoint) {
4795  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4796  Res = Residual[iVar] + Res_TruncError[iVar];
4797  node[iPoint]->AddSolution(iVar, -Res*Delta*RK_AlphaCoeff);
4798  AddRes_RMS(iVar, Res*Res);
4799  AddRes_Max(iVar, fabs(Res), geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGlobalIndex(), geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord());
4800  }
4801  }
4802 
4803  }
4804 
4805  /*--- MPI solution ---*/
4806 
4807  Set_MPI_Solution(geometry, config);
4808 
4809  /*--- Compute the root mean square residual ---*/
4810 
4811  SetResidual_RMS(geometry, config);
4812 
4813 
4814 }

4818  unsigned short iVar;

4820 
4821  bool adjoint = config->GetContinuous_Adjoint();

4823  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {

4825  SetRes_Max(iVar, 0.0, 0);

4843  }

4858 void CEulerSolver::ImplicitEuler_Iteration(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config) {
4859 
4860  unsigned short iVar, jVar;
4861  unsigned long iPoint, total_index, IterLinSol = 0;
4862  su2double Delta, *local_Res_TruncError, Vol;
4863 
4864  bool adjoint = config->GetContinuous_Adjoint();
4865  bool roe_turkel = config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == TURKEL;
4866 
4867  /*--- Set maximum residual to zero ---*/
4868 
4869  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4870  SetRes_RMS(iVar, 0.0);
4871  SetRes_Max(iVar, 0.0, 0);
4872  }
4873 
4874  /*--- Build implicit system ---*/
4875 
4876  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
4877 
4878  /*--- Read the residual ---*/
4879 
4880  local_Res_TruncError = node[iPoint]->GetResTruncError();
4881 
4882  /*--- Read the volume ---*/
4883 
4884  Vol = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetVolume();
4885 
4886  /*--- Modify matrix diagonal to assure diagonal dominance ---*/
4887 
4888 
4889  if (node[iPoint]->GetDelta_Time() != 0.0) {
4890  Delta = Vol / node[iPoint]->GetDelta_Time();
4891  if (roe_turkel) {
4892  SetPreconditioner(config, iPoint);
4893  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar ++ )
4894  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar ++ )
4895  LowMach_Precontioner[iVar][jVar] = Delta*LowMach_Precontioner[iVar][jVar];
4896  Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, LowMach_Precontioner);
4897  }
4898  else {
4899  Jacobian.AddVal2Diag(iPoint, Delta);
4900  }
4901  }
4902  else {
4903  Jacobian.SetVal2Diag(iPoint, 1.0);
4904  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4905  total_index = iPoint*nVar + iVar;
4906  LinSysRes[total_index] = 0.0;
4907  local_Res_TruncError[iVar] = 0.0;
4908  }
4909  }
4910 
4911  /*--- Right hand side of the system (-Residual) and initial guess (x = 0) ---*/
4912 
4913  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4914  total_index = iPoint*nVar + iVar;
4915  LinSysRes[total_index] = - (LinSysRes[total_index] + local_Res_TruncError[iVar]);
4916  LinSysSol[total_index] = 0.0;
4917  AddRes_RMS(iVar, LinSysRes[total_index]*LinSysRes[total_index]);
4918  AddRes_Max(iVar, fabs(LinSysRes[total_index]), geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGlobalIndex(), geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord());
4919  }
4920  }
4921 
4922  /*--- Initialize residual and solution at the ghost points ---*/
4923 
4924  for (iPoint = nPointDomain; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
4925  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4926  total_index = iPoint*nVar + iVar;
4927  LinSysRes[total_index] = 0.0;
4928  LinSysSol[total_index] = 0.0;
4929  }
4930  }
4931 
4932  /*--- Solve or smooth the linear system ---*/
4933 
4934  CSysSolve system;
4935  IterLinSol = system.Solve(Jacobian, LinSysRes, LinSysSol, geometry, config);
4936 
4937  /*--- The the number of iterations of the linear solver ---*/
4938 
4939  SetIterLinSolver(IterLinSol);
4940 
4941  /*--- Update solution (system written in terms of increments) ---*/
4942 
4943  if (!adjoint) {
4944  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
4945  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4946  node[iPoint]->AddSolution(iVar, config->GetRelaxation_Factor_Flow()*LinSysSol[iPoint*nVar+iVar]);
4947  }
4948  }
4949  }
4950 
4951  /*--- MPI solution ---*/
4952 
4953  Set_MPI_Solution(geometry, config);
4954 
4955  /*--- Compute the root mean square residual ---*/
4956 
4957  SetResidual_RMS(geometry, config);
4958 
4959 }

4961 void CEulerSolver::SetPrimitive_Gradient_GG(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
4962  unsigned long iPoint, jPoint, iEdge, iVertex;
4963  unsigned short iDim, iVar, iMarker;
4964  su2double *PrimVar_Vertex, *PrimVar_i, *PrimVar_j, PrimVar_Average,
4965  Partial_Gradient, Partial_Res, *Normal;
4966 
4967  /*--- Gradient primitive variables compressible (temp, vx, vy, vz, P, rho)
4968  Gradient primitive variables incompressible (rho, vx, vy, vz, beta) ---*/
4969  PrimVar_Vertex = new su2double [nPrimVarGrad];
4970  PrimVar_i = new su2double [nPrimVarGrad];
4971  PrimVar_j = new su2double [nPrimVarGrad];
4972 
4973  /*--- Set Gradient_Primitive to zero ---*/
4974  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++)
4975  node[iPoint]->SetGradient_PrimitiveZero(nPrimVarGrad);
4976 
4977  /*--- Loop interior edges ---*/
4978  for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
4979  iPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(0);
4980  jPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(1);
4981 
4982  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
4983  PrimVar_i[iVar] = node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive(iVar);
4984  PrimVar_j[iVar] = node[jPoint]->GetPrimitive(iVar);
4985  }
4986 
4987  Normal = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNormal();
4988  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
4989  PrimVar_Average = 0.5 * ( PrimVar_i[iVar] + PrimVar_j[iVar] );
4990  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4991  Partial_Res = PrimVar_Average*Normal[iDim];
4992  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain())
4993  node[iPoint]->AddGradient_Primitive(iVar, iDim, Partial_Res);
4994  if (geometry->node[jPoint]->GetDomain())
4995  node[jPoint]->SubtractGradient_Primitive(iVar, iDim, Partial_Res);
4996  }
4997  }
4998  }
4999 
5000  /*--- Loop boundary edges ---*/
5001  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < geometry->GetnMarker(); iMarker++) {
5002  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
5003  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
5004  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
5005 
5006  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++)
5007  PrimVar_Vertex[iVar] = node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive(iVar);
5008 
5009  Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
5010  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++)
5011  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5012  Partial_Res = PrimVar_Vertex[iVar]*Normal[iDim];
5013  node[iPoint]->SubtractGradient_Primitive(iVar, iDim, Partial_Res);
5014  }
5015  }
5016  }
5017  }
5018 
5019  /*--- Update gradient value ---*/
5020  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
5021  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
5022  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5023  Partial_Gradient = node[iPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive(iVar, iDim) / (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetVolume());
5024  node[iPoint]->SetGradient_Primitive(iVar, iDim, Partial_Gradient);
5025  }
5026  }
5027  }
5028 
5029  delete [] PrimVar_Vertex;
5030  delete [] PrimVar_i;
5031  delete [] PrimVar_j;
5032 
5033  Set_MPI_Primitive_Gradient(geometry, config);
5034 
5035 }

5037 void CEulerSolver::SetPrimitive_Gradient_LS(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
5038 
5039  unsigned short iVar, iDim, jDim, iNeigh;
5040  unsigned long iPoint, jPoint;
5041  su2double *PrimVar_i, *PrimVar_j, *Coord_i, *Coord_j, r11, r12, r13, r22, r23, r23_a,
5042  r23_b, r33, weight, product, z11, z12, z13, z22, z23, z33, detR2;
5043  bool singular;
5044 
5045  /*--- Loop over points of the grid ---*/
5046 
5047  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
5048 
5049  /*--- Set the value of the singular ---*/
5050  singular = false;
5051 
5052  /*--- Get coordinates ---*/
5053 
5054  Coord_i = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord();
5055 
5056  /*--- Get primitives from CVariable ---*/
5057 
5058  PrimVar_i = node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive();
5059 
5060  /*--- Inizialization of variables ---*/
5061 
5062  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++)
5063  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5064  cvector[iVar][iDim] = 0.0;
5065 
5066  r11 = 0.0; r12 = 0.0; r13 = 0.0; r22 = 0.0;
5067  r23 = 0.0; r23_a = 0.0; r23_b = 0.0; r33 = 0.0;
5068 
5069  AD::StartPreacc();
5070  AD::SetPreaccIn(PrimVar_i, nPrimVarGrad);
5071  AD::SetPreaccIn(Coord_i, nDim);
5072 
5073  for (iNeigh = 0; iNeigh < geometry->node[iPoint]->GetnPoint(); iNeigh++) {
5074  jPoint = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetPoint(iNeigh);
5075  Coord_j = geometry->node[jPoint]->GetCoord();
5076 
5077  PrimVar_j = node[jPoint]->GetPrimitive();
5078 
5079  AD::SetPreaccIn(Coord_j, nDim);
5080  AD::SetPreaccIn(PrimVar_j, nPrimVarGrad);
5081 
5082  weight = 0.0;
5083  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5084  weight += (Coord_j[iDim]-Coord_i[iDim])*(Coord_j[iDim]-Coord_i[iDim]);
5085 
5086  /*--- Sumations for entries of upper triangular matrix R ---*/
5087 
5088  if (weight != 0.0) {
5089 
5090  r11 += (Coord_j[0]-Coord_i[0])*(Coord_j[0]-Coord_i[0])/weight;
5091  r12 += (Coord_j[0]-Coord_i[0])*(Coord_j[1]-Coord_i[1])/weight;
5092  r22 += (Coord_j[1]-Coord_i[1])*(Coord_j[1]-Coord_i[1])/weight;
5093 
5094  if (nDim == 3) {
5095  r13 += (Coord_j[0]-Coord_i[0])*(Coord_j[2]-Coord_i[2])/weight;
5096  r23_a += (Coord_j[1]-Coord_i[1])*(Coord_j[2]-Coord_i[2])/weight;
5097  r23_b += (Coord_j[0]-Coord_i[0])*(Coord_j[2]-Coord_i[2])/weight;
5098  r33 += (Coord_j[2]-Coord_i[2])*(Coord_j[2]-Coord_i[2])/weight;
5099  }
5100 
5101  /*--- Entries of c:= transpose(A)*b ---*/
5102 
5103  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++)
5104  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5105  cvector[iVar][iDim] += (Coord_j[iDim]-Coord_i[iDim])*(PrimVar_j[iVar]-PrimVar_i[iVar])/weight;
5106 
5107  }
5108 
5109  }
5110 
5111  /*--- Entries of upper triangular matrix R ---*/
5112 
5113  if (r11 >= 0.0) r11 = sqrt(r11); else r11 = 0.0;
5114  if (r11 != 0.0) r12 = r12/r11; else r12 = 0.0;
5115  if (r22-r12*r12 >= 0.0) r22 = sqrt(r22-r12*r12); else r22 = 0.0;
5116 
5117  if (nDim == 3) {
5118  if (r11 != 0.0) r13 = r13/r11; else r13 = 0.0;
5119  if ((r22 != 0.0) && (r11*r22 != 0.0)) r23 = r23_a/r22 - r23_b*r12/(r11*r22); else r23 = 0.0;
5120  if (r33-r23*r23-r13*r13 >= 0.0) r33 = sqrt(r33-r23*r23-r13*r13); else r33 = 0.0;
5121  }
5122 
5123  /*--- Compute determinant ---*/
5124 
5125  if (nDim == 2) detR2 = (r11*r22)*(r11*r22);
5126  else detR2 = (r11*r22*r33)*(r11*r22*r33);
5127 
5128  /*--- Detect singular matrices ---*/
5129 
5130  if (abs(detR2) <= EPS) { detR2 = 1.0; singular = true; }
5131 
5132  /*--- S matrix := inv(R)*traspose(inv(R)) ---*/
5133 
5134  if (singular) {
5135  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5136  for (jDim = 0; jDim < nDim; jDim++)
5137  Smatrix[iDim][jDim] = 0.0;
5138  }
5139  else {
5140  if (nDim == 2) {
5141  Smatrix[0][0] = (r12*r12+r22*r22)/detR2;
5142  Smatrix[0][1] = -r11*r12/detR2;
5143  Smatrix[1][0] = Smatrix[0][1];
5144  Smatrix[1][1] = r11*r11/detR2;
5145  }
5146  else {
5147  z11 = r22*r33; z12 = -r12*r33; z13 = r12*r23-r13*r22;
5148  z22 = r11*r33; z23 = -r11*r23; z33 = r11*r22;
5149  Smatrix[0][0] = (z11*z11+z12*z12+z13*z13)/detR2;
5150  Smatrix[0][1] = (z12*z22+z13*z23)/detR2;
5151  Smatrix[0][2] = (z13*z33)/detR2;
5152  Smatrix[1][0] = Smatrix[0][1];
5153  Smatrix[1][1] = (z22*z22+z23*z23)/detR2;
5154  Smatrix[1][2] = (z23*z33)/detR2;
5155  Smatrix[2][0] = Smatrix[0][2];
5156  Smatrix[2][1] = Smatrix[1][2];
5157  Smatrix[2][2] = (z33*z33)/detR2;
5158  }
5159  }
5160 
5161  /*--- Computation of the gradient: S*c ---*/
5162  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
5163  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5164  product = 0.0;
5165  for (jDim = 0; jDim < nDim; jDim++) {
5166  product += Smatrix[iDim][jDim]*cvector[iVar][jDim];
5167  }
5168 
5169  node[iPoint]->SetGradient_Primitive(iVar, iDim, product);
5170  }
5171  }
5172 
5173  AD::SetPreaccOut(node[iPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive(), nPrimVarGrad, nDim);
5174  AD::EndPreacc();
5175  }
5176 
5177  Set_MPI_Primitive_Gradient(geometry, config);
5178 
5179 }
5180 
5181 void CEulerSolver::SetPrimitive_Limiter(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
5182 
5183  unsigned long iEdge, iPoint, jPoint;
5184  unsigned short iVar, iDim;
5185  su2double **Gradient_i, **Gradient_j, *Coord_i, *Coord_j, *Primitive_i, *Primitive_j,
5186  dave, LimK, eps2, eps1, dm, dp, du, y, limiter;
5187 
5188  /*--- Initialize solution max and solution min and the limiter in the entire domain --*/
5189 
5190  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
5191  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
5192  node[iPoint]->SetSolution_Max(iVar, -EPS);
5193  node[iPoint]->SetSolution_Min(iVar, EPS);
5194  node[iPoint]->SetLimiter_Primitive(iVar, 2.0);
5195  }
5196  }
5197 
5198  /*--- Establish bounds for Spekreijse monotonicity by finding max & min values of neighbor variables --*/
5199 
5200  for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
5201 
5202  /*--- Point identification, Normal vector and area ---*/
5203 
5204  iPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(0);
5205  jPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(1);
5206 
5207  /*--- Get the primitive variables ---*/
5208 
5209  Primitive_i = node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive();
5210  Primitive_j = node[jPoint]->GetPrimitive();
5211 
5212  /*--- Compute the maximum, and minimum values for nodes i & j ---*/
5213 
5214  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
5215  du = (Primitive_j[iVar] - Primitive_i[iVar]);
5216  node[iPoint]->SetSolution_Min(iVar, min(node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Min(iVar), du));
5217  node[iPoint]->SetSolution_Max(iVar, max(node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Max(iVar), du));
5218  node[jPoint]->SetSolution_Min(iVar, min(node[jPoint]->GetSolution_Min(iVar), -du));
5219  node[jPoint]->SetSolution_Max(iVar, max(node[jPoint]->GetSolution_Max(iVar), -du));
5220  }
5221 
5222  }
5223 
5224 
5225  /*--- Barth-Jespersen limiter with Venkatakrishnan modification ---*/
5226 
5227  if (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Flow() == BARTH_JESPERSEN) {
5228 
5229  for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
5230 
5231  iPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(0);
5232  jPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(1);
5233  Gradient_i = node[iPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive();
5234  Gradient_j = node[jPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive();
5235  Coord_i = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord();
5236  Coord_j = geometry->node[jPoint]->GetCoord();
5237 
5238  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
5239 
5240  /*--- Calculate the interface left gradient, delta- (dm) ---*/
5241 
5242  dm = 0.0;
5243  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5244  dm += 0.5*(Coord_j[iDim]-Coord_i[iDim])*Gradient_i[iVar][iDim];
5245 
5246  if (dm == 0.0) { limiter = 2.0; }
5247  else {
5248  if ( dm > 0.0 ) dp = node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Max(iVar);
5249  else dp = node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Min(iVar);
5250  limiter = dp/dm;
5251  }
5252 
5253  if (limiter < node[iPoint]->GetLimiter_Primitive(iVar))
5254  node[iPoint]->SetLimiter_Primitive(iVar, limiter);
5255 
5256  /*--- Calculate the interface right gradient, delta+ (dp) ---*/
5257 
5258  dm = 0.0;
5259  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5260  dm += 0.5*(Coord_i[iDim]-Coord_j[iDim])*Gradient_j[iVar][iDim];
5261 
5262  if (dm == 0.0) { limiter = 2.0; }
5263  else {
5264  if ( dm > 0.0 ) dp = node[jPoint]->GetSolution_Max(iVar);
5265  else dp = node[jPoint]->GetSolution_Min(iVar);
5266  limiter = dp/dm;
5267  }
5268 
5269  if (limiter < node[jPoint]->GetLimiter_Primitive(iVar))
5270  node[jPoint]->SetLimiter_Primitive(iVar, limiter);
5271 
5272  }
5273 
5274  }
5275 
5276  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
5277  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
5278  y = node[iPoint]->GetLimiter_Primitive(iVar);
5279  limiter = (y*y + 2.0*y) / (y*y + y + 2.0);
5280  node[iPoint]->SetLimiter_Primitive(iVar, limiter);
5281  }
5282  }
5283 
5284  }
5285 
5286  /*--- Venkatakrishnan limiter ---*/
5287 
5288  if (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Flow() == VENKATAKRISHNAN) {
5289 
5290  /*-- Get limiter parameters from the configuration file ---*/
5291 
5292  dave = config->GetRefElemLength();
5293  LimK = config->GetLimiterCoeff();
5294  eps1 = LimK*dave;
5295  eps2 = eps1*eps1*eps1;
5296 
5297  for (iEdge = 0; iEdge < geometry->GetnEdge(); iEdge++) {
5298 
5299  iPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(0);
5300  jPoint = geometry->edge[iEdge]->GetNode(1);
5301  Gradient_i = node[iPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive();
5302  Gradient_j = node[jPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive();
5303  Coord_i = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord();
5304  Coord_j = geometry->node[jPoint]->GetCoord();
5305 
5306 
5307  AD::StartPreacc();
5308  AD::SetPreaccIn(Gradient_i, nPrimVarGrad, nDim);
5309  AD::SetPreaccIn(Gradient_j, nPrimVarGrad, nDim);
5310  AD::SetPreaccIn(Coord_i, nDim); AD::SetPreaccIn(Coord_j, nDim);
5311 
5312 
5313  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
5314 
5315  AD::SetPreaccIn(node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Max(iVar));
5316  AD::SetPreaccIn(node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Min(iVar));
5317  AD::SetPreaccIn(node[jPoint]->GetSolution_Max(iVar));
5318  AD::SetPreaccIn(node[jPoint]->GetSolution_Min(iVar));
5319 
5320  /*--- Calculate the interface left gradient, delta- (dm) ---*/
5321 
5322  dm = 0.0;
5323  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5324  dm += 0.5*(Coord_j[iDim]-Coord_i[iDim])*Gradient_i[iVar][iDim];
5325 
5326  /*--- Calculate the interface right gradient, delta+ (dp) ---*/
5327 
5328  if ( dm > 0.0 ) dp = node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Max(iVar);
5329  else dp = node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Min(iVar);
5330 
5331  limiter = ( dp*dp + 2.0*dp*dm + eps2 )/( dp*dp + dp*dm + 2.0*dm*dm + eps2);
5332 
5333  if (limiter < node[iPoint]->GetLimiter_Primitive(iVar)){
5334  node[iPoint]->SetLimiter_Primitive(iVar, limiter);
5335  AD::SetPreaccOut(node[iPoint]->GetLimiter_Primitive()[iVar]);
5336  }
5337 
5338  /*-- Repeat for point j on the edge ---*/
5339 
5340  dm = 0.0;
5341  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5342  dm += 0.5*(Coord_i[iDim]-Coord_j[iDim])*Gradient_j[iVar][iDim];
5343 
5344  if ( dm > 0.0 ) dp = node[jPoint]->GetSolution_Max(iVar);
5345  else dp = node[jPoint]->GetSolution_Min(iVar);
5346 
5347  limiter = ( dp*dp + 2.0*dp*dm + eps2 )/( dp*dp + dp*dm + 2.0*dm*dm + eps2);
5348 
5349  if (limiter < node[jPoint]->GetLimiter_Primitive(iVar)){
5350  node[jPoint]->SetLimiter_Primitive(iVar, limiter);
5351  AD::SetPreaccOut(node[jPoint]->GetLimiter_Primitive()[iVar]);
5352  }
5353  }
5354 
5355  AD::EndPreacc();
5356 
5357  }
5358 
5359  }
5360 
5361  /*--- Limiter MPI ---*/
5362 
5363  Set_MPI_Primitive_Limiter(geometry, config);
5364 
5365 }

5675 
5676 void CEulerSolver::SetPreconditioner(CConfig *config, unsigned long iPoint) {
5677  unsigned short iDim, jDim, iVar, jVar;
5678  su2double Beta, local_Mach, Beta2, rho, enthalpy, soundspeed, sq_vel;
5679  su2double *U_i = NULL;
5680  su2double Beta_min = config->GetminTurkelBeta();
5681  su2double Beta_max = config->GetmaxTurkelBeta();
5682 
5683 
5684  /*--- Variables to calculate the preconditioner parameter Beta ---*/
5685  local_Mach = sqrt(node[iPoint]->GetVelocity2())/node[iPoint]->GetSoundSpeed();
5686  Beta = max(Beta_min, min(local_Mach, Beta_max));
5687  Beta2 = Beta*Beta;
5688 
5689  U_i = node[iPoint]->GetSolution();
5690 
5691  rho = U_i[0];
5692  enthalpy = node[iPoint]->GetEnthalpy();
5693  soundspeed = node[iPoint]->GetSoundSpeed();
5694  sq_vel = node[iPoint]->GetVelocity2();
5695 
5696  /*---Calculating the inverse of the preconditioning matrix that multiplies the time derivative */
5697  LowMach_Precontioner[0][0] = 0.5*sq_vel;
5698  LowMach_Precontioner[0][nVar-1] = 1.0;
5699  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim ++)
5700  LowMach_Precontioner[0][1+iDim] = -1.0*U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
5701 
5702  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim ++) {
5703  LowMach_Precontioner[iDim+1][0] = 0.5*sq_vel*U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
5704  LowMach_Precontioner[iDim+1][nVar-1] = U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
5705  for (jDim = 0; jDim < nDim; jDim ++) {
5706  LowMach_Precontioner[iDim+1][1+jDim] = -1.0*U_i[jDim+1]/rho*U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
5707  }
5708  }
5709 
5710  LowMach_Precontioner[nVar-1][0] = 0.5*sq_vel*enthalpy;
5711  LowMach_Precontioner[nVar-1][nVar-1] = enthalpy;
5712  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim ++)
5713  LowMach_Precontioner[nVar-1][1+iDim] = -1.0*U_i[iDim+1]/rho*enthalpy;
5714 
5715 
5716  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar ++ ) {
5717  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar ++ ) {
5718  LowMach_Precontioner[iVar][jVar] = (1.0/(Beta2+EPS) - 1.0) * (Gamma-1.0)/(soundspeed*soundspeed)*LowMach_Precontioner[iVar][jVar];
5719  if (iVar == jVar)
5720  LowMach_Precontioner[iVar][iVar] += 1.0;
5721  }
5722  }
5723 
5724 }
5725 
5726 void CEulerSolver::GetEngine_Properties(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
5727 
5728  unsigned short iDim, iMarker, iMarker_EngineInflow, iMarker_EngineBleed, iMarker_EngineExhaust, iVar;
5729  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
5730  su2double Pressure, Temperature, Velocity[3], Velocity2, MassFlow, Density, Energy, Area,
5731  Mach, SoundSpeed, Flow_Dir[3], alpha;
5732 
5733  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
5734  unsigned short nMarker_EngineInflow = config->GetnMarker_EngineInflow();
5735  unsigned short nMarker_EngineBleed = config->GetnMarker_EngineBleed();
5736  unsigned short nMarker_EngineExhaust = config->GetnMarker_EngineExhaust();
5737 
5738  int rank = MASTER_NODE;
5739 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
5740  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
5741 #endif
5742 
5743  /*--- Compute the numerical fan face Mach number, and the total area of the inflow ---*/
5744 
5745  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
5746 
5747  Inflow_MassFlow[iMarker] = 0.0;
5748  Inflow_Mach[iMarker] = 0.0;
5749  Inflow_Pressure[iMarker] = 0.0;
5750  Inflow_Area[iMarker] = 0.0;
5751 
5752  Bleed_MassFlow[iMarker] = 0.0;
5753  Bleed_Pressure[iMarker] = 0.0;
5754  Bleed_Temperature[iMarker] = 0.0;
5755  Bleed_Area[iMarker] = 0.0;
5756 
5757  Exhaust_MassFlow[iMarker] = 0.0;
5758  Exhaust_Pressure[iMarker] = 0.0;
5759  Exhaust_Temperature[iMarker] = 0.0;
5760  Exhaust_Area[iMarker] = 0.0;
5761 
5762  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW) {
5763 
5764  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
5765 
5766  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
5767 
5768  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
5769 
5770  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
5771 
5772  Density = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0);
5773  Velocity2 = 0.0; Area = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0;
5774  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5775  Area += Vector[iDim]*Vector[iDim];
5776  Velocity[iDim] = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1)/Density;
5777  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
5778  MassFlow -= Vector[iDim]*node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1);
5779  }
5780 
5781  Area = sqrt (Area);
5782  Energy = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(nVar-1)/Density;
5783  Pressure = Gamma_Minus_One*Density*(Energy-0.5*Velocity2);
5784  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
5785  Mach = sqrt(Velocity2)/SoundSpeed;
5786 
5787  /*--- Compute the Inflow_MassFlow, Inflow_Pressure, Inflow_Mach, and Inflow_Area ---*/
5788 
5789  Inflow_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
5790  Inflow_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*Area;
5791  Inflow_Mach[iMarker] += Mach*Area;
5792  Inflow_Area[iMarker] += Area;
5793 
5794  }
5795  }
5796 
5797  }
5798 
5799  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_BLEED) {
5800 
5801  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
5802 
5803  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
5804 
5805  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
5806 
5807  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
5808 
5809  Density = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0);
5810  Velocity2 = 0.0; Area = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0;
5811  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5812  Area += Vector[iDim]*Vector[iDim];
5813  Velocity[iDim] = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1)/Density;
5814  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
5815  MassFlow += Vector[iDim]*node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1);
5816  }
5817 
5818  Area = sqrt (Area);
5819  Energy = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(nVar-1)/Density;
5820  Pressure = Gamma_Minus_One*Density*(Energy-0.5*Velocity2);
5821  Temperature = Pressure / (Gas_Constant * Density);
5822 
5823  /*--- Compute the Bleed_MassFlow, Bleed_Pressure, Bleed_Temperature, and Bleed_Area ---*/
5824 
5825  Bleed_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
5826  Bleed_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*Area;
5827  Bleed_Temperature[iMarker] += Temperature*Area;
5828  Bleed_Area[iMarker] += Area;
5829 
5830  }
5831  }
5832 
5833  }
5834 
5835  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_EXHAUST) {
5836 
5837  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
5838  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
5839 
5840  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
5841 
5842  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
5843 
5844  Density = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0);
5845  Velocity2 = 0.0; Area = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0;
5846  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5847  Area += Vector[iDim]*Vector[iDim];
5848  Velocity[iDim] = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1)/Density;
5849  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
5850  MassFlow += Vector[iDim]*node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1);
5851  }
5852 
5853  Area = sqrt (Area);
5854  Energy = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(nVar-1)/Density;
5855  Pressure = Gamma_Minus_One*Density*(Energy-0.5*Velocity2);
5856  Temperature = Pressure / (Gas_Constant * Density);
5857 
5858  /*--- Compute the mass Exhaust_MassFlow ---*/
5859 
5860  Exhaust_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
5861  Exhaust_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*Area;
5862  Exhaust_Temperature[iMarker] += Temperature*Area;
5863  Exhaust_Area[iMarker] += Area;
5864 
5865  }
5866  }
5867 
5868  }
5869 
5870  }
5871 
5872  /*--- Copy to the appropriate structure ---*/
5873 
5874  su2double *Inflow_MassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineInflow];
5875  su2double *Inflow_Mach_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineInflow];
5876  su2double *Inflow_Pressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineInflow];
5877  su2double *Inflow_Area_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineInflow];
5878 
5879  su2double *Inflow_MassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineInflow];
5880  su2double *Inflow_Mach_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineInflow];
5881  su2double *Inflow_Pressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineInflow];
5882  su2double *Inflow_Area_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineInflow];
5883 
5884  for (iMarker_EngineInflow = 0; iMarker_EngineInflow < nMarker_EngineInflow; iMarker_EngineInflow++) {
5885  Inflow_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow] = 0.0;
5886  Inflow_Mach_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow] = 0.0;
5887  Inflow_Pressure_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow] = 0.0;
5888  Inflow_Area_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow] = 0.0;
5889 
5890  Inflow_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] = 0.0;
5891  Inflow_Mach_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] = 0.0;
5892  Inflow_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] = 0.0;
5893  Inflow_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] = 0.0;
5894  }
5895 
5896  su2double *Bleed_MassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineBleed];
5897  su2double *Bleed_Temperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineBleed];
5898  su2double *Bleed_Pressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineBleed];
5899  su2double *Bleed_Area_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineBleed];
5900 
5901  su2double *Bleed_MassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineBleed];
5902  su2double *Bleed_Temperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineBleed];
5903  su2double *Bleed_Pressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineBleed];
5904  su2double *Bleed_Area_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineBleed];
5905 
5906  for (iMarker_EngineBleed = 0; iMarker_EngineBleed < nMarker_EngineBleed; iMarker_EngineBleed++) {
5907  Bleed_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed] = 0.0;
5908  Bleed_Temperature_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed] = 0.0;
5909  Bleed_Pressure_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed] = 0.0;
5910  Bleed_Area_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed] = 0.0;
5911 
5912  Bleed_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] = 0.0;
5913  Bleed_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] = 0.0;
5914  Bleed_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] = 0.0;
5915  Bleed_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] = 0.0;
5916  }
5917 
5918  su2double *Exhaust_MassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineExhaust];
5919  su2double *Exhaust_Temperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineExhaust];
5920  su2double *Exhaust_Pressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineExhaust];
5921  su2double *Exhaust_Area_Local = new su2double [nMarker_EngineExhaust];
5922 
5923  su2double *Exhaust_MassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineExhaust];
5924  su2double *Exhaust_Temperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineExhaust];
5925  su2double *Exhaust_Pressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineExhaust];
5926  su2double *Exhaust_Area_Total = new su2double [nMarker_EngineExhaust];
5927 
5928  for (iMarker_EngineExhaust = 0; iMarker_EngineExhaust < nMarker_EngineExhaust; iMarker_EngineExhaust++) {
5929  Exhaust_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = 0.0;
5930  Exhaust_Temperature_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = 0.0;
5931  Exhaust_Pressure_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = 0.0;
5932  Exhaust_Area_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = 0.0;
5933 
5934  Exhaust_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = 0.0;
5935  Exhaust_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = 0.0;
5936  Exhaust_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = 0.0;
5937  Exhaust_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = 0.0;
5938  }
5939 
5940  /*--- Compute the numerical fan face Mach number, mach number, temperature and the total area ---*/
5941 
5942  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
5943 
5944  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW) {
5945 
5946  for (iMarker_EngineInflow = 0; iMarker_EngineInflow < nMarker_EngineInflow; iMarker_EngineInflow++) {
5947 
5948  /*--- Add the Inflow_MassFlow, Inflow_Mach, Inflow_Pressure and Inflow_Area to the particular boundary ---*/
5949 
5950  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == config->GetMarker_EngineInflow(iMarker_EngineInflow)) {
5951  Inflow_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow] += Inflow_MassFlow[iMarker];
5952  Inflow_Mach_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow] += Inflow_Mach[iMarker];
5953  Inflow_Pressure_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow] += Inflow_Pressure[iMarker];
5954  Inflow_Area_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow] += Inflow_Area[iMarker];
5955  }
5956 
5957  }
5958 
5959  }
5960 
5961  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_BLEED) {
5962 
5963  for (iMarker_EngineBleed = 0; iMarker_EngineBleed < nMarker_EngineBleed; iMarker_EngineBleed++) {
5964 
5965  /*--- Add the Bleed_MassFlow, Bleed_Temperature, Bleed_Pressure and Bleed_Area to the particular boundary ---*/
5966 
5967  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == config->GetMarker_EngineBleed(iMarker_EngineBleed)) {
5968  Bleed_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed] += Bleed_MassFlow[iMarker];
5969  Bleed_Temperature_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed] += Bleed_Temperature[iMarker];
5970  Bleed_Pressure_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed] += Bleed_Pressure[iMarker];
5971  Bleed_Area_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed] += Bleed_Area[iMarker];
5972  }
5973 
5974  }
5975 
5976  }
5977 
5978  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_EXHAUST) {
5979 
5980  for (iMarker_EngineExhaust= 0; iMarker_EngineExhaust < nMarker_EngineExhaust; iMarker_EngineExhaust++) {
5981 
5982  /*--- Add the Exhaust_MassFlow, and Exhaust_Area to the particular boundary ---*/
5983 
5984  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == config->GetMarker_EngineExhaust(iMarker_EngineExhaust)) {
5985  Exhaust_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust] += Exhaust_MassFlow[iMarker];
5986  Exhaust_Temperature_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust] += Exhaust_Temperature[iMarker];
5987  Exhaust_Pressure_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust] += Exhaust_Pressure[iMarker];
5988  Exhaust_Area_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust] += Exhaust_Area[iMarker];
5989  }
5990 
5991  }
5992 
5993  }
5994 
5995  }
5996 
5997 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
5998 
5999  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inflow_MassFlow_Local, Inflow_MassFlow_Total, nMarker_EngineInflow, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6000  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inflow_Mach_Local, Inflow_Mach_Total, nMarker_EngineInflow, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6001  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inflow_Pressure_Local, Inflow_Pressure_Total, nMarker_EngineInflow, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6002  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inflow_Area_Local, Inflow_Area_Total, nMarker_EngineInflow, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6003 
6004  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Bleed_MassFlow_Local, Bleed_MassFlow_Total, nMarker_EngineBleed, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6005  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Bleed_Temperature_Local, Bleed_Temperature_Total, nMarker_EngineBleed, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6006  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Bleed_Pressure_Local, Bleed_Pressure_Total, nMarker_EngineBleed, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6007  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Bleed_Area_Local, Bleed_Area_Total, nMarker_EngineBleed, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6008 
6009  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Exhaust_MassFlow_Local, Exhaust_MassFlow_Total, nMarker_EngineExhaust, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6010  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Exhaust_Temperature_Local, Exhaust_Temperature_Total, nMarker_EngineExhaust, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6011  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Exhaust_Pressure_Local, Exhaust_Pressure_Total, nMarker_EngineExhaust, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6012  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Exhaust_Area_Local, Exhaust_Area_Total, nMarker_EngineExhaust, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6013 
6014 #else
6015 
6016  for (iMarker_EngineInflow = 0; iMarker_EngineInflow < nMarker_EngineInflow; iMarker_EngineInflow++) {
6017  Inflow_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] = Inflow_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow];
6018  Inflow_Mach_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] = Inflow_Mach_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow];
6019  Inflow_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] = Inflow_Pressure_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow];
6020  Inflow_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] = Inflow_Area_Local[iMarker_EngineInflow];
6021  }
6022 
6023  for (iMarker_EngineBleed = 0; iMarker_EngineBleed < nMarker_EngineBleed; iMarker_EngineBleed++) {

6025  Bleed_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] = Bleed_Temperature_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed];
6026  Bleed_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] = Bleed_Pressure_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed];
6027  Bleed_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] = Bleed_Area_Local[iMarker_EngineBleed];

6032  Exhaust_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = Exhaust_Temperature_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust];
6033  Exhaust_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = Exhaust_Pressure_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust];
6034  Exhaust_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = Exhaust_Area_Local[iMarker_EngineExhaust];
6035  }
6036 
6037 #endif
6038 
6039  /*--- Compute the value of Inflow_Area_Total, and Inflow_Pressure_Total, and
6040  set the value in the config structure for future use ---*/
6041

6043  if (Inflow_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] != 0.0) Inflow_Mach_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] /= Inflow_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow];
6044  else Inflow_Mach_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] = 0.0;
6045  if (Inflow_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] != 0.0) Inflow_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] /= Inflow_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow];
6046  else Inflow_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] = 0.0;
6047 
6048  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
6049  config->SetInflow_Mach(iMarker_EngineInflow, Inflow_Mach_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow]);
6050  config->SetInflow_Pressure(iMarker_EngineInflow, Inflow_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow]);
6051  }
6052 
6053  }
6054 
6055  /*--- Compute the value of Bleed_Area_Total, and Bleed_Pressure_Total, and
6056  set the value in the config structure for future use ---*/
6057 
6058  for (iMarker_EngineBleed = 0; iMarker_EngineBleed < nMarker_EngineBleed; iMarker_EngineBleed++) {
6059  if (Bleed_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] != 0.0) Bleed_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] /= Bleed_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed];
6060  else Bleed_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] = 0.0;
6061  if (Bleed_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] != 0.0) Bleed_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] /= Bleed_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed];
6062  else Bleed_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] = 0.0;
6063 
6064  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
6065  config->SetBleed_Temperature(iMarker_EngineBleed, Bleed_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed]);
6066  config->SetBleed_MassFlow(iMarker_EngineBleed, Bleed_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed]);
6067  config->SetBleed_Pressure(iMarker_EngineBleed, Bleed_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed]);
6068  }
6069 
6070  }
6071 
6072  /*--- Compute the value of Exhaust_Area_Total, and Exhaust_Pressure_Total, and
6073  set the value in the config structure for future use ---*/
6074 
6075  for (iMarker_EngineExhaust = 0; iMarker_EngineExhaust < nMarker_EngineExhaust; iMarker_EngineExhaust++) {
6076  if (Exhaust_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] != 0.0) Exhaust_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] /= Exhaust_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust];
6077  else Exhaust_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = 0.0;
6078  if (Exhaust_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] != 0.0) Exhaust_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] /= Exhaust_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust];
6079  else Exhaust_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] = 0.0;
6080 
6081  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
6082  config->SetExhaust_Temperature(iMarker_EngineExhaust, Exhaust_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust]);
6083  config->SetExhaust_Pressure(iMarker_EngineExhaust, Exhaust_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust]);
6084  }
6085 
6086  }
6087 
6088  bool write_heads = (((config->GetExtIter() % (config->GetWrt_Con_Freq()*40)) == 0));
6089 
6090  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (iMesh == MESH_0) && write_heads && Output) {
6091 
6092  cout.precision(4);
6093  cout.setf(ios::fixed, ios::floatfield);
6094 
6095  cout << endl << "---------------------------- Engine properties --------------------------" << endl;
6096  for (iMarker_EngineInflow = 0; iMarker_EngineInflow < nMarker_EngineInflow; iMarker_EngineInflow++) {
6097  cout << "Engine inflow ("<< config->GetMarker_EngineInflow(iMarker_EngineInflow);
6098  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << "): Mass flow (kg/s): ";
6099  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << "): Mass flow (slug/s): ";
6100  cout << Inflow_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] * config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref()
6101  << ", Mach: " << Inflow_Mach_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow];
6102  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Area (m^2): ";
6103  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Area (ft^2): ";
6104  cout << Inflow_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineInflow] <<"."<< endl;
6105  }
6106 
6107  for (iMarker_EngineBleed = 0; iMarker_EngineBleed < nMarker_EngineBleed; iMarker_EngineBleed++) {
6108  cout << "Engine bleed ("<< config->GetMarker_EngineBleed(iMarker_EngineBleed);
6109  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << "): Mass flow (kg/s): ";
6110  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << "): Mass flow (slug/s): ";
6111  cout << Bleed_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] * config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
6112  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Temp (K): ";
6113  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Temp (R): ";
6114  cout << Bleed_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] * config->GetTemperature_Ref();
6115  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Area (m^2): ";
6116  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Area (ft^2): ";
6117  cout << Bleed_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineBleed] <<"."<< endl;
6118  }
6119 
6120  for (iMarker_EngineExhaust = 0; iMarker_EngineExhaust < nMarker_EngineExhaust; iMarker_EngineExhaust++) {
6121  cout << "Engine exhaust ("<< config->GetMarker_EngineExhaust(iMarker_EngineExhaust);
6122  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << "): Mass flow (kg/s): ";
6123  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << "): Mass flow (slug/s): ";
6124  cout << Exhaust_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] * config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
6125  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Temp (K): ";
6126  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Temp (R): ";
6127  cout << Exhaust_Temperature_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] * config->GetTemperature_Ref();
6128  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Pressure (Pa): ";
6129  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Pressure (psf): ";
6130  cout << Exhaust_Pressure_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] * config->GetPressure_Ref();
6131  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Area (m^2): ";
6132  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Area (ft^2): ";
6133  cout << Exhaust_Area_Total[iMarker_EngineExhaust] <<"."<< endl;
6134  }
6135  cout << "-------------------------------------------------------------------------" << endl;
6136 
6137  }
6138 
6139  /*--- Check the flow orientation in the engine ---*/
6140 
6141  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
6142 
6143  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW) ||
6144  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_EXHAUST) ||
6145  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_BLEED)) {
6146 
6147  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
6148 
6149  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
6150 
6151  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
6152 
6153  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
6154 
6155  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
6156 
6157  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Vector[iDim] = -Vector[iDim];
6158 
6159  Area = 0.0;
6160  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6161  Area += Vector[iDim]*Vector[iDim];
6162  Area = sqrt (Area);
6163 
6164  /*--- Compute unitary vector ---*/
6165 
6166  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6167  Vector[iDim] /= Area;
6168 
6169  /*--- The flow direction is defined by the local velocity on the surface ---*/
6170 
6171  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6172  Flow_Dir[iDim] = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1) / node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0);
6173 
6174  /*--- Dot product of normal and flow direction. ---*/
6175 
6176  alpha = 0.0;
6177  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6178  alpha += Vector[iDim]*Flow_Dir[iDim];
6179 
6180  /*--- Flow in the wrong direction. ---*/
6181 
6182  if (((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_EXHAUST) ||
6183  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_BLEED)) && (alpha > 0.0)) {
6184 
6185  /*--- Copy the old solution ---*/
6186  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
6187  node[iPoint]->SetSolution(iVar, node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Old(iVar));
6188 
6189  }
6190 
6191  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW) && (alpha < 0.0)) {
6192 
6193  /*--- Copy the old solution ---*/
6194  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
6195  node[iPoint]->SetSolution(iVar, node[iPoint]->GetSolution_Old(iVar));
6196 
6197  }
6198 
6199  }
6200 
6201  }
6202 
6203  }
6204 
6205 
6206  delete [] Inflow_MassFlow_Local;
6207  delete [] Inflow_Mach_Local;
6208  delete [] Inflow_Pressure_Local;
6209  delete [] Inflow_Area_Local;
6210 
6211  delete [] Inflow_MassFlow_Total;
6212  delete [] Inflow_Mach_Total;
6213  delete [] Inflow_Pressure_Total;
6214  delete [] Inflow_Area_Total;
6215 
6216  delete [] Exhaust_MassFlow_Local;
6217  delete [] Exhaust_Temperature_Local;
6218  delete [] Exhaust_Pressure_Local;
6219  delete [] Exhaust_Area_Local;
6220 
6221  delete [] Exhaust_MassFlow_Total;
6222  delete [] Exhaust_Temperature_Total;
6223  delete [] Exhaust_Pressure_Total;
6224  delete [] Exhaust_Area_Total;
6225 
6226  delete [] Bleed_MassFlow_Local;
6227  delete [] Bleed_Temperature_Local;
6228  delete [] Bleed_Pressure_Local;
6229  delete [] Bleed_Area_Local;
6230 
6231  delete [] Bleed_MassFlow_Total;
6232  delete [] Bleed_Temperature_Total;
6233  delete [] Bleed_Pressure_Total;
6234  delete [] Bleed_Area_Total;
6235 
6236 }
6237 
6238 void CEulerSolver::GetActuatorDisk_Properties(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
6239 
6240  unsigned short iDim, iMarker;
6241  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
6242  su2double Pressure, Temperature, Velocity[3], Velocity2, MassFlow, Density, Energy, Area;
6243  unsigned short iMarker_ActDiskInlet, iMarker_ActDiskOutlet;
6244 
6245  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
6246 
6247  unsigned short nMarker_ActDiskInlet = config->GetnMarker_ActDisk_Inlet();
6248  unsigned short nMarker_ActDiskOutlet = config->GetnMarker_ActDisk_Outlet();
6249 
6250  int rank = MASTER_NODE;
6251 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6252  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
6253 #endif
6254 
6255  su2double *Inlet_MassFlow = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()];
6256  su2double *Inlet_Pressure = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()];
6257  su2double *Inlet_Temperature = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()];
6258  su2double *Inlet_Area = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()];
6259 
6260  su2double *Outlet_MassFlow = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()];
6261  su2double *Outlet_Pressure = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()];
6262  su2double *Outlet_Temperature = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()];
6263  su2double *Outlet_Area = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()];
6264 
6265  /*--- Compute the numerical fan face Mach number, and the total area of the inflow ---*/
6266 
6267  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
6268 
6269  Inlet_MassFlow[iMarker] = 0.0;
6270  Inlet_Pressure[iMarker] = 0.0;
6271  Inlet_Temperature[iMarker] = 0.0;
6272  Inlet_Area[iMarker] = 0.0;
6273 
6274  Outlet_MassFlow[iMarker] = 0.0;
6275  Outlet_Pressure[iMarker] = 0.0;
6276  Outlet_Temperature[iMarker] = 0.0;
6277  Outlet_Area[iMarker] = 0.0;
6278 
6279  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) {
6280 
6281  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
6282 
6283  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
6284 
6285  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
6286 
6287  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
6288 
6289  Density = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0);
6290  Velocity2 = 0.0; Area = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0;
6291  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6292  Area += Vector[iDim]*Vector[iDim];
6293  Velocity[iDim] = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1)/Density;
6294  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
6295  MassFlow += Vector[iDim]*node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1);
6296  }
6297 
6298  Area = sqrt (Area);
6299  Energy = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(nVar-1)/Density;
6300  Pressure = Gamma_Minus_One*Density*(Energy-0.5*Velocity2);
6301  Temperature = Pressure / (Gas_Constant * Density);
6302 
6303  /*--- Compute the Inlet_MassFlow, Inlet_Pressure, Inlet_Temperature, and Inlet_Area ---*/
6304 
6305  Inlet_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
6306  Inlet_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*Area;
6307  Inlet_Temperature[iMarker] += Temperature*Area;
6308  Inlet_Area[iMarker] += Area;
6309 
6310  }
6311  }
6312 
6313  }
6314 
6315  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET) {
6316 
6317  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
6318  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
6319 
6320  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
6321 
6322  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
6323 
6324  Density = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0);
6325  Velocity2 = 0.0; Area = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0;
6326  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6327  Area += Vector[iDim]*Vector[iDim];
6328  Velocity[iDim] = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1)/Density;
6329  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
6330  MassFlow += Vector[iDim]*node[iPoint]->GetSolution(iDim+1);
6331  }
6332 
6333  Area = sqrt (Area);
6334  Energy = node[iPoint]->GetSolution(nVar-1)/Density;
6335  Pressure = Gamma_Minus_One*Density*(Energy-0.5*Velocity2);
6336  Temperature = Pressure / (Gas_Constant * Density);
6337 
6338  /*--- Compute the mass Outlet_MassFlow ---*/
6339 
6340  Outlet_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
6341  Outlet_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*Area;
6342  Outlet_Temperature[iMarker] += Temperature*Area;
6343  Outlet_Area[iMarker] += Area;
6344 
6345  }
6346  }
6347 
6348  }
6349 
6350  }
6351 
6352  /*--- Copy to the appropriate structure ---*/
6353 
6354  su2double *Inlet_MassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6355  su2double *Inlet_Temperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6356  su2double *Inlet_Pressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6357  su2double *Inlet_Area_Local = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6358 
6359  su2double *Inlet_MassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6360  su2double *Inlet_Temperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6361  su2double *Inlet_Pressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6362  su2double *Inlet_Area_Total = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6363 
6364  for (iMarker_ActDiskInlet = 0; iMarker_ActDiskInlet < nMarker_ActDiskInlet; iMarker_ActDiskInlet++) {
6365  Inlet_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = 0.0;
6366  Inlet_Temperature_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = 0.0;
6367  Inlet_Pressure_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = 0.0;
6368  Inlet_Area_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = 0.0;
6369 
6370  Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = 0.0;
6371  Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = 0.0;
6372  Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = 0.0;
6373  Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = 0.0;
6374  }
6375 
6376  su2double *Outlet_MassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6377  su2double *Outlet_Temperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6378  su2double *Outlet_Pressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6379  su2double *Outlet_Area_Local = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6380 
6381  su2double *Outlet_MassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6382  su2double *Outlet_Temperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6383  su2double *Outlet_Pressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6384  su2double *Outlet_Area_Total = new su2double [nMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6385 
6386  for (iMarker_ActDiskOutlet = 0; iMarker_ActDiskOutlet < nMarker_ActDiskOutlet; iMarker_ActDiskOutlet++) {
6387  Outlet_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = 0.0;
6388  Outlet_Temperature_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = 0.0;
6389  Outlet_Pressure_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = 0.0;
6390  Outlet_Area_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = 0.0;
6391 
6392  Outlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = 0.0;
6393  Outlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = 0.0;
6394  Outlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = 0.0;
6395  Outlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = 0.0;
6396  }
6397 
6398  /*--- Compute the numerical fan face Mach number, mach number, temperature and the total area ---*/
6399 
6400  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
6401 
6402  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) {
6403 
6404  for (iMarker_ActDiskInlet = 0; iMarker_ActDiskInlet < nMarker_ActDiskInlet; iMarker_ActDiskInlet++) {
6405 
6406  /*--- Add the Inlet_MassFlow, Inlet_Temperature, Inlet_Pressure and Inlet_Area to the particular boundary ---*/
6407 
6408  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == config->GetMarker_ActDisk_Inlet(iMarker_ActDiskInlet)) {
6409  Inlet_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] += Inlet_MassFlow[iMarker];
6410  Inlet_Temperature_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] += Inlet_Temperature[iMarker];
6411  Inlet_Pressure_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] += Inlet_Pressure[iMarker];
6412  Inlet_Area_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] += Inlet_Area[iMarker];
6413  }
6414 
6415  }
6416 
6417  }
6418 
6419  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET) {
6420 
6421  for (iMarker_ActDiskOutlet= 0; iMarker_ActDiskOutlet < nMarker_ActDiskOutlet; iMarker_ActDiskOutlet++) {
6422 
6423  /*--- Add the Outlet_MassFlow, and Outlet_Area to the particular boundary ---*/
6424 
6425  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == config->GetMarker_ActDisk_Outlet(iMarker_ActDiskOutlet)) {
6426  Outlet_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] += Outlet_MassFlow[iMarker];
6427  Outlet_Temperature_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] += Outlet_Temperature[iMarker];
6428  Outlet_Pressure_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] += Outlet_Pressure[iMarker];
6429  Outlet_Area_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] += Outlet_Area[iMarker];
6430  }
6431 
6432  }
6433 
6434  }
6435 
6436  }
6437 
6438 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6439 
6440  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_MassFlow_Local, Inlet_MassFlow_Total, nMarker_ActDiskInlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6441  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Temperature_Local, Inlet_Temperature_Total, nMarker_ActDiskInlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6442  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Pressure_Local, Inlet_Pressure_Total, nMarker_ActDiskInlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6443  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Area_Local, Inlet_Area_Total, nMarker_ActDiskInlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6444 
6445  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_MassFlow_Local, Outlet_MassFlow_Total, nMarker_ActDiskOutlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6446  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Temperature_Local, Outlet_Temperature_Total, nMarker_ActDiskOutlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6447  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Pressure_Local, Outlet_Pressure_Total, nMarker_ActDiskOutlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6448  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Area_Local, Outlet_Area_Total, nMarker_ActDiskOutlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, MPI_COMM_WORLD);
6449 
6450 #else
6451 
6452  for (iMarker_ActDiskInlet = 0; iMarker_ActDiskInlet < nMarker_ActDiskInlet; iMarker_ActDiskInlet++) {
6453  Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = Inlet_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6454  Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = Inlet_Temperature_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6455  Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = Inlet_Pressure_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6456  Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = Inlet_Area_Local[iMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6457  }
6458 
6459  for (iMarker_ActDiskOutlet = 0; iMarker_ActDiskOutlet < nMarker_ActDiskOutlet; iMarker_ActDiskOutlet++) {
6460  Outlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = Outlet_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6461  Outlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = Outlet_Temperature_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6462  Outlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = Outlet_Pressure_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6463  Outlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = Outlet_Area_Local[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6464  }
6465 
6466 #endif
6467 
6468  /*--- Compute the value of Inlet_Area_Total, and Inlet_Pressure_Total, and
6469  set the value in the config structure for future use ---*/
6470 
6471  for (iMarker_ActDiskInlet = 0; iMarker_ActDiskInlet < nMarker_ActDiskInlet; iMarker_ActDiskInlet++) {
6472  if (Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] != 0.0) Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] /= Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6473  else Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = 0.0;
6474  if (Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] != 0.0) Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] /= Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet];
6475  else Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] = 0.0;
6476  }
6477 
6478  /*--- Compute the value of Outlet_Area_Total, and Outlet_Pressure_Total, and
6479  set the value in the config structure for future use ---*/
6480 
6481  for (iMarker_ActDiskOutlet = 0; iMarker_ActDiskOutlet < nMarker_ActDiskOutlet; iMarker_ActDiskOutlet++) {
6482  if (Outlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] != 0.0) Outlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] /= Outlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6483  else Outlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = 0.0;
6484  if (Outlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] != 0.0) Outlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] /= Outlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet];
6485  else Outlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] = 0.0;
6486  }
6487 
6488  bool write_heads = (((config->GetExtIter() % (config->GetWrt_Con_Freq()*40)) == 0));
6489 
6490  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (iMesh == MESH_0) && write_heads && Output) {
6491 
6492  cout.precision(4);
6493  cout.setf(ios::fixed, ios::floatfield);
6494 
6495  cout << endl << "------------------------ Actuator Disk properties -----------------------" << endl;
6496 
6497  for (iMarker_ActDiskInlet = 0; iMarker_ActDiskInlet < nMarker_ActDiskInlet; iMarker_ActDiskInlet++) {
6498  cout << "Actuator Disk Inlet ("<< config->GetMarker_ActDisk_Inlet(iMarker_ActDiskInlet);
6499  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << "): Mass flow (kg/s): ";
6500  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << "): Mass flow (slug/s): ";
6501  cout << -Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] * config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
6502  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Temp (K): ";
6503  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Temp (R): ";
6504  cout << Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] * config->GetTemperature_Ref();
6505  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Pressure (Pa): ";
6506  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Pressure (psf): ";
6507  cout << Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] * config->GetPressure_Ref();
6508  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Area (m^2): ";
6509  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Area (ft^2): ";
6510  cout << Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskInlet] <<"."<< endl;
6511  }
6512 
6513  for (iMarker_ActDiskOutlet = 0; iMarker_ActDiskOutlet < nMarker_ActDiskOutlet; iMarker_ActDiskOutlet++) {
6514  cout << "Actuator Disk Outlet ("<< config->GetMarker_ActDisk_Outlet(iMarker_ActDiskOutlet);
6515  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << "): Mass flow (kg/s): ";
6516  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << "): Mass flow (slug/s): ";
6517  cout << Outlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] * config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
6518  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Temp (K): ";
6519  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Temp (R): ";
6520  cout << Outlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] * config->GetTemperature_Ref();
6521  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Pressure (Pa): ";
6522  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Pressure (psf): ";
6523  cout << Outlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] * config->GetPressure_Ref();
6524  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << ", Area (m^2): ";
6525  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << ", Area (ft^2): ";
6526  cout << Outlet_Area_Total[iMarker_ActDiskOutlet] <<"."<< endl;
6527  }
6528  cout << "-------------------------------------------------------------------------" << endl;
6529 
6530  }
6531 
6532  delete [] Outlet_MassFlow_Local;
6533  delete [] Outlet_Temperature_Local;
6534  delete [] Outlet_Pressure_Local;
6535  delete [] Outlet_Area_Local;
6536 
6537  delete [] Outlet_MassFlow_Total;
6538  delete [] Outlet_Temperature_Total;
6539  delete [] Outlet_Pressure_Total;
6540  delete [] Outlet_Area_Total;
6541 
6542  delete [] Inlet_MassFlow_Local;
6543  delete [] Inlet_Temperature_Local;
6544  delete [] Inlet_Pressure_Local;
6545  delete [] Inlet_Area_Local;
6546 
6547  delete [] Inlet_MassFlow_Total;
6548  delete [] Inlet_Temperature_Total;
6549  delete [] Inlet_Pressure_Total;
6550  delete [] Inlet_Area_Total;
6551 
6552 
6553  delete [] Inlet_MassFlow;
6554  delete [] Inlet_Pressure;
6555  delete [] Inlet_Temperature;
6556  delete [] Inlet_Area;
6557 
6558  delete [] Outlet_MassFlow;
6559  delete [] Outlet_Pressure;
6560  delete [] Outlet_Temperature;
6561  delete [] Outlet_Area;
6562 
6563 }
6564 
6565 void CEulerSolver::SetFarfield_AoA(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
6566  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
6567 
6568  su2double Target_CL, AoA, Vel_Infty[3], AoA_inc, Vel_Infty_Mag;
6569  unsigned short iDim;
6570  unsigned long Iter_Fixed_CL = config->GetIter_Fixed_CL();
6571  unsigned long ExtIter = config->GetExtIter();
6572  su2double Beta = config->GetAoS()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
6573  su2double dCl_dAlpha = config->GetdCl_dAlpha()*180.0/PI_NUMBER;
6574  bool Update_AoA = false;
6575 
6576  int rank = MASTER_NODE;
6577 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6578  MPI_Comm_rank(MPI_COMM_WORLD, &rank);
6579 #endif
6580 
6581  if (ExtIter == 0) AoA_Counter = 0;
6582 
6583  /*--- Only the fine mesh level should check the convergence criteria ---*/
6584 
6585  if ((iMesh == MESH_0) && Output) {
6586 
6587  /*--- Initialize the update flag to false ---*/
6588 
6589  Update_AoA = false;
6590 
6591  /*--- Reevaluate Angle of Attack at a fix number of iterations ---*/
6592 
6593  if ((ExtIter % Iter_Fixed_CL == 0) && (ExtIter != 0)) {
6594  AoA_Counter++;
6595  if (AoA_Counter >= 2) Update_AoA = true;
6596  else Update_AoA = false;
6597  };
6598 
6599  /*--- Store the update boolean for use on other mesh levels in the MG ---*/
6600 
6601  config->SetUpdate_AoA(Update_AoA);
6602 
6603  }
6604 
6605  else {
6606  Update_AoA = config->GetUpdate_AoA();
6607  }
6608 
6609  /*--- If we are within two digits of convergence in the CL coefficient,
6610  * compute an updated value for the AoA at the farfield. We are iterating
6611  * on the AoA in order to match the specified fixed lift coefficient. ---*/
6612 
6613  if (Update_AoA && Output) {
6614 
6615  /*--- Retrieve the specified target CL value. ---*/
6616 
6617  Target_CL = config->GetTarget_CL();
6618 
6619  /*--- Retrieve the old AoA (radians) ---*/
6620 
6621  AoA_old = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
6622 
6623  /*--- Estimate the increment in AoA based on dCl_dAlpha (radians) ---*/
6624 
6625  AoA_inc = (1.0/dCl_dAlpha)*(Target_CL - Total_CLift);
6626 
6627  /*--- Compute a new value for AoA on the fine mesh only (radians)---*/
6628 
6629  if (iMesh == MESH_0) AoA = AoA_old + AoA_inc;
6630  else { AoA = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0; }
6631 
6632  /*--- Only the fine mesh stores the updated values for AoA in config ---*/
6633 
6634  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
6635  config->SetAoA(AoA*180.0/PI_NUMBER);
6636  }
6637 
6638  /*--- Update the freestream velocity vector at the farfield ---*/
6639 
6640  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6641  Vel_Infty[iDim] = GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
6642 
6643  /*--- Compute the magnitude of the free stream velocity ---*/
6644 
6645  Vel_Infty_Mag = 0;
6646  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6647  Vel_Infty_Mag += Vel_Infty[iDim]*Vel_Infty[iDim];
6648  Vel_Infty_Mag = sqrt(Vel_Infty_Mag);
6649 
6650  /*--- Compute the new freestream velocity with the updated AoA ---*/
6651 
6652  if (nDim == 2) {
6653  Vel_Infty[0] = cos(AoA)*Vel_Infty_Mag;
6654  Vel_Infty[1] = sin(AoA)*Vel_Infty_Mag;
6655  }
6656  if (nDim == 3) {
6657  Vel_Infty[0] = cos(AoA)*cos(Beta)*Vel_Infty_Mag;
6658  Vel_Infty[1] = sin(Beta)*Vel_Infty_Mag;
6659  Vel_Infty[2] = sin(AoA)*cos(Beta)*Vel_Infty_Mag;
6660  }
6661 
6662  /*--- Store the new freestream velocity vector for the next iteration ---*/
6663 
6664  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6665  Velocity_Inf[iDim] = Vel_Infty[iDim];
6666  }
6667 
6668  /*--- Only the fine mesh stores the updated values for velocity in config ---*/
6669 
6670  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
6671  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6672  config->SetVelocity_FreeStreamND(Vel_Infty[iDim], iDim);
6673  }
6674 
6675  }
6676 
6677  /*--- Output some information to the console with the headers ---*/
6678 
6679  bool write_heads = ((ExtIter % Iter_Fixed_CL == 0) && (ExtIter != 0));
6680  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (iMesh == MESH_0) && write_heads && Output) {
6681  cout.precision(7);
6682  cout.setf(ios::fixed, ios::floatfield);
6683  cout << endl << "----------------------------- Fixed CL Mode -----------------------------" << endl;
6684  cout << "Target CL: " << config->GetTarget_CL();
6685  cout << ", current CL: " << Total_CLift;
6686  cout << ", current AoA: " << config->GetAoA() << " deg." << endl;
6687  cout << "-------------------------------------------------------------------------" << endl << endl;
6688  }
6689 
6690 
6691 }
6692 
6693 void CEulerSolver::BC_Euler_Wall(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
6694  CNumerics *numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
6695 
6696  unsigned short iDim, iVar, jVar, kVar, jDim;
6697  unsigned long iPoint, iVertex;
6698  su2double Density = 0.0, Pressure = 0.0, *Normal = NULL, *GridVel = NULL, Area, UnitNormal[3], *NormalArea,
6699  ProjGridVel = 0.0, turb_ke;
6700  su2double Density_b, StaticEnergy_b, Enthalpy_b, *Velocity_b, Kappa_b, Chi_b, Energy_b, VelMagnitude2_b, Pressure_b;
6701  su2double Density_i, *Velocity_i, ProjVelocity_i = 0.0, Energy_i, VelMagnitude2_i;
6702  su2double **Jacobian_b, **DubDu;
6703 
6704  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
6705  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
6706  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
6707  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
6708  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
6709  bool tkeNeeded = (((config->GetKind_Solver() == RANS )|| (config->GetKind_Solver() == DISC_ADJ_RANS)) &&
6710  (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == SST));
6711 
6712  Normal = new su2double[nDim];
6713  NormalArea = new su2double[nDim];
6714  Velocity_b = new su2double[nDim];
6715  Velocity_i = new su2double[nDim];
6716  Jacobian_b = new su2double*[nVar];
6717  DubDu = new su2double*[nVar];
6718  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
6719  Jacobian_b[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
6720  DubDu[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
6721  }
6722 
6723  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
6724 
6725  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
6726  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
6727 
6728  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e, not a halo node) ---*/
6729 
6730  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
6731 
6732  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negative for outward convention) ---*/
6733 
6734  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
6735 
6736  Area = 0.0;
6737  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
6738  Area = sqrt (Area);
6739 
6740  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6741  NormalArea[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
6742  UnitNormal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim]/Area;
6743  }
6744 
6745  /*--- Compressible solver ---*/
6746 
6747  if (compressible) {
6748 
6749  /*--- Get the state i ---*/
6750 
6751  VelMagnitude2_i = 0.0; ProjVelocity_i = 0.0;
6752  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6753  Velocity_i[iDim] = node[iPoint]->GetVelocity(iDim);
6754  ProjVelocity_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
6755  VelMagnitude2_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*Velocity_i[iDim];
6756  }
6757  Density_i = node[iPoint]->GetDensity();
6758  Energy_i = node[iPoint]->GetEnergy();
6759 
6760  /*--- Compute the boundary state b ---*/
6761 
6762  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6763  Velocity_b[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim] - ProjVelocity_i * UnitNormal[iDim]; //Force the velocity to be tangential to the surface.
6764 
6765  if (grid_movement) {
6766  GridVel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
6767  ProjGridVel = 0.0;
6768  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) ProjGridVel += GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
6769  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Velocity_b[iDim] += GridVel[iDim] - ProjGridVel * UnitNormal[iDim];
6770  }
6771 
6772  VelMagnitude2_b = 0.0;
6773  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6774  VelMagnitude2_b += Velocity_b[iDim] * Velocity_b[iDim];
6775 
6776  /*--- Compute the residual ---*/
6777 
6778  turb_ke = 0.0;
6779  if (tkeNeeded) turb_ke = solver_container[TURB_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0);
6780 
6781  Density_b = Density_i;
6782  StaticEnergy_b = Energy_i - 0.5 * VelMagnitude2_i - turb_ke;
6783  Energy_b = StaticEnergy_b + 0.5 * VelMagnitude2_b + turb_ke;
6784 
6785  FluidModel->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_b, StaticEnergy_b);
6786  Kappa_b = FluidModel->GetdPde_rho() / Density_b;
6787  Chi_b = FluidModel->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_b * StaticEnergy_b;
6788  Pressure_b = FluidModel->GetPressure();
6789  Enthalpy_b = Energy_b + Pressure_b/Density_b;
6790 
6791  numerics->GetInviscidProjFlux(&Density_b, Velocity_b, &Pressure_b, &Enthalpy_b, NormalArea, Residual);
6792 
6793  /*--- Grid velocity correction to the energy term ---*/
6794  if (grid_movement) {
6795  GridVel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
6796  ProjGridVel = 0.0;
6797  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6798  ProjGridVel += GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
6799  Residual[nVar-1] += Pressure_b*ProjGridVel*Area;
6800  }
6801 
6802  /*--- Add the Reynolds stress tensor contribution ---*/
6803 
6804  if (tkeNeeded) {
6805  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6806  Residual[iDim+1] += (2.0/3.0)*Density_b*turb_ke*NormalArea[iDim];
6807  }
6808 
6809  }
6810 
6811  /*--- Incompressible solver ---*/
6812 
6813  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
6814 
6815  /*--- Compute the residual ---*/
6816 
6817  Pressure = node[iPoint]->GetPressureInc();
6818  Density = node[iPoint]->GetPressureInc();
6819 
6820  Residual[0] = 0.0;
6821  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6822  Residual[iDim+1] = Pressure*NormalArea[iDim];
6823  if (compressible || freesurface) {
6824  Residual[nVar-1] = 0.0;
6825  }
6826 
6827  /*--- Add the Reynolds stress tensor contribution ---*/
6828 
6829  if (tkeNeeded) {
6830  turb_ke = solver_container[TURB_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0);
6831  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6832  Residual[iDim+1] += (2.0/3.0)*Density*turb_ke*NormalArea[iDim];
6833  }
6834 
6835  /*--- Adjustment to energy equation due to grid motion ---*/
6836 
6837  if (grid_movement) {
6838  ProjGridVel = 0.0;
6839  GridVel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
6840  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6841  ProjGridVel += GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
6842  Residual[nVar-1] = Pressure*ProjGridVel*Area;
6843  }
6844 
6845  }
6846 
6847  /*--- Add value to the residual ---*/
6848 
6849  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
6850 
6851  /*--- Form Jacobians for implicit computations ---*/
6852 
6853  if (implicit) {
6854 
6855  /*--- Initialize Jacobian ---*/
6856 
6857  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
6858  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
