6859  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] = 0.0;
6860  }
6861 
6862  /*--- Compressible solver ---*/
6863 
6864  if (compressible) {
6865 
6866  /*--- Compute DubDu ---*/
6867 
6868  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
6869  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
6870  DubDu[iVar][jVar]= 0.0;
6871  DubDu[iVar][iVar]= 1.0;
6872  }
6873 
6874  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6875  for (jDim = 0; jDim<nDim; jDim++)
6876  DubDu[iDim+1][jDim+1] -= UnitNormal[iDim]*UnitNormal[jDim];
6877  DubDu[nVar-1][0] += 0.5*ProjVelocity_i*ProjVelocity_i;
6878  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6879  DubDu[nVar-1][iDim+1] -= ProjVelocity_i*UnitNormal[iDim];
6880  }
6881 
6882  /*--- Compute flux Jacobian in state b ---*/
6883 
6884  numerics->GetInviscidProjJac(Velocity_b, &Enthalpy_b, &Chi_b, &Kappa_b, NormalArea, 1, Jacobian_b);
6885 
6886  // Check for grid movement, should be already considered since Jacobian b is computed from u_b
6887  // if (grid_movement) {
6888  // Jacobian_b[nVar-1][0] += 0.5*ProjGridVel*ProjGridVel;
6889  // for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6890  // Jacobian_b[nVar-1][iDim+1] -= ProjGridVel * UnitNormal[iDim];
6891  // }
6892 
6893  /*--- Compute numerical flux Jacobian at node i ---*/
6894 
6895  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
6896  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
6897  for (kVar = 0; kVar < nVar; kVar++)
6898  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] += Jacobian_b[iVar][kVar] * DubDu[kVar][jVar];
6899 
6900  /*--- Add the Jacobian to the sparse matrix ---*/
6901 
6902  Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
6903 
6904  }
6905 
6906  /*--- Incompressible solver ---*/
6907 
6908  if (incompressible || freesurface) {
6909  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6910  Jacobian_i[iDim+1][0] = -Normal[iDim];
6911  Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
6912  }
6913 
6914  }
6915  }
6916  }
6917 
6918  delete [] Normal;
6919  delete [] NormalArea;
6920  delete [] Velocity_b;
6921  delete [] Velocity_i;
6922  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
6923  delete [] Jacobian_b[iVar];
6924  delete [] DubDu[iVar];
6925  }
6926  delete [] Jacobian_b;
6927  delete [] DubDu;
6928 
6929 }
6930 
6931 void CEulerSolver::BC_Far_Field(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics,
6932  CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
6933 
6934  unsigned short iDim;
6935  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, Point_Normal;
6936 
6937  su2double *GridVel;
6938  su2double Area, UnitNormal[3] = {0.0,0.0,0.0};
6939  su2double Density, Pressure, Energy, Velocity[3] = {0.0,0.0,0.0};
6940  su2double Density_Bound, Pressure_Bound, Vel_Bound[3] = {0.0,0.0,0.0};
6941  su2double Density_Infty, Pressure_Infty, Vel_Infty[3] = {0.0,0.0,0.0};
6942  su2double SoundSpeed, Entropy, Velocity2, Vn;
6943  su2double SoundSpeed_Bound, Entropy_Bound, Vel2_Bound, Vn_Bound;
6944  su2double SoundSpeed_Infty, Entropy_Infty, Vel2_Infty, Vn_Infty, Qn_Infty;
6945  su2double RiemannPlus, RiemannMinus;
6946  su2double *V_infty, *V_domain;
6947 
6948  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
6949 
6950  bool implicit = config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT;
6951  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
6952  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
6953  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == INCOMPRESSIBLE);
6954  bool freesurface = (config->GetKind_Regime() == FREESURFACE);
6955  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
6956  bool tkeNeeded = (((config->GetKind_Solver() == RANS ) ||
6957  (config->GetKind_Solver() == DISC_ADJ_RANS))
6958  && (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == SST));
6959 
6960  su2double *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
6961 
6962  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
6963 
6964  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
6965  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
6966 
6967  /*--- Allocate the value at the infinity ---*/
6968  V_infty = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
6969 
6970  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e, not a halo node) ---*/
6971 
6972  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
6973 
6974  /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
6975 
6976  Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
6977 
6978  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
6979 
6980  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
6981  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
6982  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
6983 
6984  /*--- Retrieve solution at the farfield boundary node ---*/
6985  V_domain = node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive();
6986 
6987  /*--- Construct solution state at infinity (far-field) ---*/
6988 
6989  if (compressible) {
6990 
6991  /*--- Construct solution state at infinity for compressible flow by
6992  using Riemann invariants, and then impose a weak boundary condition
6993  by computing the flux using this new state for U. See CFD texts by
6994  Hirsch or Blazek for more detail. Adapted from an original
6995  implementation in the Stanford University multi-block (SUmb) solver
6996  in the routine bcFarfield.f90 written by Edwin van der Weide,
6997  last modified 06-12-2005. First, compute the unit normal at the
6998  boundary nodes. ---*/
6999 
7000  Area = 0.0;
7001  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
7002  Area = sqrt(Area);
7003 
7004  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7005  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
7006 
7007  /*--- Store primitive variables (density, velocities, velocity squared,
7008  energy, pressure, and sound speed) at the boundary node, and set some
7009  other quantities for clarity. Project the current flow velocity vector
7010  at this boundary node into the local normal direction, i.e. compute
7011  v_bound.n. ---*/
7012 
7013  Density_Bound = V_domain[nDim+2];
7014  Vel2_Bound = 0.0; Vn_Bound = 0.0;
7015  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7016  Vel_Bound[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7017  Vel2_Bound += Vel_Bound[iDim]*Vel_Bound[iDim];
7018  Vn_Bound += Vel_Bound[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7019  }
7020  Pressure_Bound = node[iPoint]->GetPressure();
7021  SoundSpeed_Bound = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_Bound/Density_Bound);
7022  Entropy_Bound = pow(Density_Bound, Gamma)/Pressure_Bound;
7023 
7024  /*--- Store the primitive variable state for the freestream. Project
7025  the freestream velocity vector into the local normal direction,
7026  i.e. compute v_infty.n. ---*/
7027 
7028  Density_Infty = GetDensity_Inf();
7029  Vel2_Infty = 0.0; Vn_Infty = 0.0;
7030  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7031  Vel_Infty[iDim] = GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
7032  Vel2_Infty += Vel_Infty[iDim]*Vel_Infty[iDim];
7033  Vn_Infty += Vel_Infty[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7034  }
7035  Pressure_Infty = GetPressure_Inf();
7036  SoundSpeed_Infty = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_Infty/Density_Infty);
7037  Entropy_Infty = pow(Density_Infty, Gamma)/Pressure_Infty;
7038 
7039  /*--- Adjust the normal freestream velocity for grid movement ---*/
7040 
7041  Qn_Infty = Vn_Infty;
7042  if (grid_movement) {
7043  GridVel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
7044  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7045  Qn_Infty -= GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7046  }
7047 
7048  /*--- Compute acoustic Riemann invariants: R = u.n +/- 2c/(gamma-1).
7049  These correspond with the eigenvalues (u+c) and (u-c), respectively,
7050  which represent the acoustic waves. Positive characteristics are
7051  incoming, and a physical boundary condition is imposed (freestream
7052  state). This occurs when either (u.n+c) > 0 or (u.n-c) > 0. Negative
7053  characteristics are leaving the domain, and numerical boundary
7054  conditions are required by extrapolating from the interior state
7055  using the Riemann invariants. This occurs when (u.n+c) < 0 or
7056  (u.n-c) < 0. Note that grid movement is taken into account when
7057  checking the sign of the eigenvalue. ---*/
7058 
7059  /*--- Check whether (u.n+c) is greater or less than zero ---*/
7060 
7061  if (Qn_Infty > -SoundSpeed_Infty) {
7062  /*--- Subsonic inflow or outflow ---*/
7063  RiemannPlus = Vn_Bound + 2.0*SoundSpeed_Bound/Gamma_Minus_One;
7064  } else {
7065  /*--- Supersonic inflow ---*/
7066  RiemannPlus = Vn_Infty + 2.0*SoundSpeed_Infty/Gamma_Minus_One;
7067  }
7068 
7069  /*--- Check whether (u.n-c) is greater or less than zero ---*/
7070 
7071  if (Qn_Infty > SoundSpeed_Infty) {
7072  /*--- Supersonic outflow ---*/
7073  RiemannMinus = Vn_Bound - 2.0*SoundSpeed_Bound/Gamma_Minus_One;
7074  } else {
7075  /*--- Subsonic outflow ---*/
7076  RiemannMinus = Vn_Infty - 2.0*SoundSpeed_Infty/Gamma_Minus_One;
7077  }
7078 
7079  /*--- Compute a new value for the local normal velocity and speed of
7080  sound from the Riemann invariants. ---*/
7081 
7082  Vn = 0.5 * (RiemannPlus + RiemannMinus);
7083  SoundSpeed = 0.25 * (RiemannPlus - RiemannMinus)*Gamma_Minus_One;
7084 
7085  /*--- Construct the primitive variable state at the boundary for
7086  computing the flux for the weak boundary condition. The values
7087  that we choose to construct the solution (boundary or freestream)
7088  depend on whether we are at an inflow or outflow. At an outflow, we
7089  choose boundary information (at most one characteristic is incoming),
7090  while at an inflow, we choose infinity values (at most one
7091  characteristic is outgoing). ---*/
7092 
7093  if (Qn_Infty > 0.0) {
7094  /*--- Outflow conditions ---*/
7095  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7096  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Bound[iDim] + (Vn-Vn_Bound)*UnitNormal[iDim];
7097  Entropy = Entropy_Bound;
7098  } else {
7099  /*--- Inflow conditions ---*/
7100  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7101  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Infty[iDim] + (Vn-Vn_Infty)*UnitNormal[iDim];
7102  Entropy = Entropy_Infty;
7103  }
7104 
7105  /*--- Recompute the primitive variables. ---*/
7106 
7107  Density = pow(Entropy*SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed/Gamma,1.0/Gamma_Minus_One);
7108  Velocity2 = 0.0;
7109  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7110  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7111  }
7112  Pressure = Density*SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed/Gamma;
7113  Energy = Pressure/(Gamma_Minus_One*Density) + 0.5*Velocity2;
7114  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7115 
7116  /*--- Store new primitive state for computing the flux. ---*/
7117 
7118  V_infty[0] = Pressure/(Gas_Constant*Density);
7119  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7120  V_infty[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
7121  V_infty[nDim+1] = Pressure;
7122  V_infty[nDim+2] = Density;
7123  V_infty[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
7124 
7125  }
7126  if (incompressible) {
7127 
7128  /*--- All the values computed from the infinity ---*/
7129 
7130  V_infty[0] = GetPressure_Inf();
7131  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7132  V_infty[iDim+1] = GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
7133  V_infty[nDim+1] = GetDensity_Inf();
7134  V_infty[nDim+2] = config->GetArtComp_Factor();
7135 
7136  }
7137  if (freesurface) {
7138 
7139  /*--- All the values computed from the infinity ---*/
7140 
7141  V_infty[0] = GetPressure_Inf();
7142  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7143  V_infty[iDim+1] = GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
7144  V_infty[nDim+1] = GetDensity_Inf();
7145  V_infty[nDim+2] = config->GetArtComp_Factor();
7146 
7147  }
7148 
7149  /*--- Set various quantities in the numerics class ---*/
7150 
7151  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_infty);
7152 
7153  if (grid_movement) {
7154  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel(),
7155  geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel());
7156  }
7157 
7158  /*--- Compute the convective residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
7159 
7160  conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual, Jacobian_i, Jacobian_j, config);
7161 
7162  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
7163 
7164  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
7165 
7166  /*--- Convective Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7167 
7168  if (implicit)
7169  Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
7170 
7171  /*--- Roe Turkel preconditioning, set the value of beta ---*/
7172 
7173  if (config->GetKind_Upwind() == TURKEL)
7174  node[iPoint]->SetPreconditioner_Beta(conv_numerics->GetPrecond_Beta());
7175 
7176  /*--- Viscous residual contribution ---*/
7177 
7178  if (viscous) {
7179 
7180  /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
7181 
7182  if (compressible) {
7183  V_infty[nDim+5] = node[iPoint]->GetLaminarViscosity();
7184  V_infty[nDim+6] = node[iPoint]->GetEddyViscosity();
7185  }
7186  if (incompressible) {
7187  V_infty[nDim+3] = node[iPoint]->GetLaminarViscosityInc();
7188  V_infty[nDim+4] = node[iPoint]->GetEddyViscosityInc();
7189  }
7190 
7191  /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
7192 
7193  visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7194  visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(),
7195  geometry->node[Point_Normal]->GetCoord());
7196 
7197  /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
7198 
7199  visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_infty);
7200  visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(node[iPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive(),
7201  node[iPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive());
7202 
7203  /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
7204 
7205  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == SST)
7206  visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0),
7207  solver_container[TURB_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0));
7208 
7209  /*--- Compute and update viscous residual ---*/
7210 
7211  visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual, Jacobian_i, Jacobian_j, config);
7212  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual);
7213 
7214  /*--- Viscous Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7215 
7216  if (implicit)
7217  Jacobian.SubtractBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
7218 
7219  }
7220 
7221  }
7222  }
7223 
7224  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
7225  delete [] Normal;
7226 
7227 }
7228 
7229 void CEulerSolver::BC_Riemann(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
7230  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
7231  unsigned short iDim, iVar, jVar, kVar;
7232  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, Point_Normal;
7233  su2double P_Total, T_Total, P_static, T_static, Rho_static, *Mach, *Flow_Dir, Area, UnitNormal[3];
7234  su2double *Velocity_b, Velocity2_b, Enthalpy_b, Energy_b, StaticEnergy_b, Density_b, Kappa_b, Chi_b, Pressure_b, Temperature_b;
7235  su2double *Velocity_e, Velocity2_e, VelMag_e, Enthalpy_e, Entropy_e, Energy_e = 0.0, StaticEnthalpy_e, StaticEnergy_e, Density_e = 0.0, Pressure_e;
7236  su2double *Velocity_i, Velocity2_i, Enthalpy_i, Energy_i, StaticEnergy_i, Density_i, Kappa_i, Chi_i, Pressure_i, SoundSpeed_i;
7237  su2double ProjVelocity_i;
7238  su2double **P_Tensor, **invP_Tensor, *Lambda_i, **Jacobian_b, **DubDu, *dw, *u_e, *u_i, *u_b;
7239  su2double *gridVel;
7240  su2double *V_boundary, *V_domain, *S_boundary, *S_domain;
7241 
7242  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
7243  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
7244  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
7245  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
7246  bool gravity = (config->GetGravityForce());
7247  bool tkeNeeded = (((config->GetKind_Solver() == RANS )|| (config->GetKind_Solver() == DISC_ADJ_RANS)) &&
7248  (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == SST));
7249 
7250  su2double *Normal, *FlowDirMix, TangVelocity, NormalVelocity;
7251  Normal = new su2double[nDim];
7252  su2double ext_flow_angle;
7253 
7254  Velocity_i = new su2double[nDim];
7255  Velocity_b = new su2double[nDim];
7256  Velocity_e = new su2double[nDim];
7257  FlowDirMix = new su2double[nDim];
7258  Lambda_i = new su2double[nVar];
7259  u_i = new su2double[nVar];
7260  u_e = new su2double[nVar];
7261  u_b = new su2double[nVar];
7262  dw = new su2double[nVar];
7263 
7264  S_boundary = new su2double[8];
7265 
7266  P_Tensor = new su2double*[nVar];
7267  invP_Tensor = new su2double*[nVar];
7268  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
7269  {
7270  P_Tensor[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
7271  invP_Tensor[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
7272  }
7273 
7274  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
7275  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7276 
7277  V_boundary= GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
7278 
7279  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7280 
7281  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
7282  if (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) {
7283 
7284  /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
7285  Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
7286 
7287  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
7288  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7289  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7290  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7291 
7292  Area = 0.0;
7293  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
7294  Area = sqrt (Area);
7295 
7296  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7297  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
7298 
7299  /*--- Retrieve solution at this boundary node ---*/
7300  V_domain = node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive();
7301 
7302  /* --- Compute the internal state u_i --- */
7303  Velocity2_i = 0;
7304  for (iDim=0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7305  {
7306  Velocity_i[iDim] = node[iPoint]->GetVelocity(iDim);
7307  Velocity2_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*Velocity_i[iDim];
7308  }
7309 
7310 
7311  Density_i = node[iPoint]->GetDensity();
7312 
7313  Energy_i = node[iPoint]->GetEnergy();
7314  StaticEnergy_i = Energy_i - 0.5*Velocity2_i;
7315 
7316  FluidModel->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_i, StaticEnergy_i);
7317 
7318  Pressure_i = FluidModel->GetPressure();
7319  Enthalpy_i = Energy_i + Pressure_i/Density_i;
7320 
7321  SoundSpeed_i = FluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
7322 
7323  Kappa_i = FluidModel->GetdPde_rho() / Density_i;
7324  Chi_i = FluidModel->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_i * StaticEnergy_i;
7325 
7326  ProjVelocity_i = 0.0;
7327  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7328  ProjVelocity_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7329 
7330  /*--- Build the external state u_e from boundary data and internal node ---*/
7331 
7332  switch(config->GetKind_Data_Riemann(Marker_Tag))
7333  {
7334  //TODO(turbo), generilize for 3D case
7335  //TODO(turbo), generilize for Inlet and Outlet in for backflow treatment
7336  //TODO(turbo), implement not uniform inlet and radial equilibrium for the outlet
7337  case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT:
7338 
7339  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
7340  if (gravity) P_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(nDim-1)*STANDART_GRAVITY;
7341  else P_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
7342  T_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
7343  Flow_Dir = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
7344 
7345  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
7346  P_Total /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
7347  T_Total /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
7348 
7349  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
7350  FluidModel->SetTDState_PT(P_Total, T_Total);
7351  Enthalpy_e = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy()+ FluidModel->GetPressure()/FluidModel->GetDensity();
7352  Entropy_e = FluidModel->GetEntropy();
7353 
7354  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
7355  Velocity2_e = Velocity2_i;
7356  if (nDim == 2){
7357  NormalVelocity= -sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[0];
7358  TangVelocity= -sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[1];
7359  Velocity_e[0]= UnitNormal[0]*NormalVelocity - UnitNormal[1]*TangVelocity;
7360  Velocity_e[1]= UnitNormal[1]*NormalVelocity + UnitNormal[0]*TangVelocity;
7361  }else{
7362  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7363  Velocity_e[iDim] = sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[iDim];
7364  }
7365  StaticEnthalpy_e = Enthalpy_e - 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
7366  FluidModel->SetTDState_hs(StaticEnthalpy_e, Entropy_e);
7367  Density_e = FluidModel->GetDensity();
7368  StaticEnergy_e = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy();
7369  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
7370  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
7371  break;
7372 
7373  case STATIC_SUPERSONIC_INFLOW_PT:
7374 
7375  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
7376  if (gravity) P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(nDim-1)*STANDART_GRAVITY;
7377  else P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
7378  T_static = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
7379  Mach = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
7380 
7381  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
7382  P_static /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
7383  T_static /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
7384 
7385  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
7386  FluidModel->SetTDState_PT(P_static, T_static);
7387 
7388  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
7389  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
7390  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7391  Velocity_e[iDim] = Mach[iDim]*FluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
7392  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
7393  }
7394  Density_e = FluidModel->GetDensity();
7395  StaticEnergy_e = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy();
7396  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
7397  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
7398  break;
7399 
7400  case STATIC_SUPERSONIC_INFLOW_PD:
7401 
7402  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
7403 
7404  if (gravity) P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(nDim-1)*STANDART_GRAVITY;
7405  else P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
7406  Rho_static = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
7407  Mach = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
7408 
7409  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
7410  P_static /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
7411  Rho_static /= config->GetDensity_Ref();
7412 
7413  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
7414  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(P_static, Rho_static);
7415 
7416  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
7417  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
7418  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7419  Velocity_e[iDim] = Mach[iDim]*FluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
7420  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
7421  }
7422  Density_e = FluidModel->GetDensity();
7423  StaticEnergy_e = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy();
7424  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
7425  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
7426  break;
7427 
7428  case MIXING_IN:
7429 
7430  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
7431  P_Total = ExtAveragedTotPressure[val_marker];
7432  T_Total = ExtAveragedTotTemperature[val_marker];
7433  ext_flow_angle = atan(ExtAveragedTangVelocity[val_marker]/ExtAveragedNormalVelocity[val_marker]);
7434  FlowDirMix[0] = cos(ext_flow_angle);
7435  FlowDirMix[1] = sin(ext_flow_angle);
7436 
7437  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
7438  FluidModel->SetTDState_PT(P_Total, T_Total);
7439  Enthalpy_e = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy()+ FluidModel->GetPressure()/FluidModel->GetDensity();
7440  Entropy_e = FluidModel->GetEntropy();
7441 
7442  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
7443  Velocity2_e = Velocity2_i;
7444  if (nDim == 2){
7445  NormalVelocity= -sqrt(Velocity2_e)*FlowDirMix[0];
7446  TangVelocity= -sqrt(Velocity2_e)*FlowDirMix[1];
7447  Velocity_e[0]= UnitNormal[0]*NormalVelocity - UnitNormal[1]*TangVelocity;
7448  Velocity_e[1]= UnitNormal[1]*NormalVelocity + UnitNormal[0]*TangVelocity;
7449  }else{
7450  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7451  Velocity_e[iDim] = sqrt(Velocity2_e)*FlowDirMix[iDim];
7452  }
7453  StaticEnthalpy_e = Enthalpy_e - 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
7454  FluidModel->SetTDState_hs(StaticEnthalpy_e, Entropy_e);
7455  Density_e = FluidModel->GetDensity();
7456  StaticEnergy_e = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy();
7457  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
7458  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
7459  break;
7460 
7461  case DENSITY_VELOCITY:
7462 
7463  /*--- Retrieve the specified density and velocity magnitude ---*/
7464  Density_e = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
7465  VelMag_e = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
7466  Flow_Dir = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
7467 
7468  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
7469  Density_e /= config->GetDensity_Ref();
7470  VelMag_e /= config->GetVelocity_Ref();
7471 
7472  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7473  Velocity_e[iDim] = VelMag_e*Flow_Dir[iDim];
7474  Energy_e = Energy_i;
7475  break;
7476 
7477  case MIXING_OUT:
7478 
7479  /*--- Retrieve the staic pressure for this boundary. ---*/
7480  Pressure_e = ExtAveragedPressure[val_marker];
7481  Density_e = Density_i;
7482 
7483  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
7484  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_e, Density_e);
7485  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
7486  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7487  Velocity_e[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
7488  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
7489  }
7490  Energy_e = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_e;
7491  break;
7492 
7493  case STATIC_PRESSURE:
7494 
7495  /*--- Retrieve the staic pressure for this boundary. ---*/
7496  Pressure_e = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
7497  Pressure_e /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
7498  Density_e = Density_i;
7499 
7500  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
7501  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_e, Density_e);
7502  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
7503  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7504  Velocity_e[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
7505  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
7506  }
7507  Energy_e = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_e;
7508  break;
7509 
7510  default:
7511  cout << "Warning! Invalid Riemann input!" << endl;
7512  exit(EXIT_FAILURE);
7513  break;
7514 
7515  }
7516 
7517  /*--- Compute P (matrix of right eigenvectors) ---*/
7518  conv_numerics->GetPMatrix(&Density_i, Velocity_i, &SoundSpeed_i, &Enthalpy_i, &Chi_i, &Kappa_i, UnitNormal, P_Tensor);
7519 
7520  /*--- Compute inverse P (matrix of left eigenvectors)---*/
7521  conv_numerics->GetPMatrix_inv(invP_Tensor, &Density_i, Velocity_i, &SoundSpeed_i, &Chi_i, &Kappa_i, UnitNormal);
7522 
7523  /*--- eigenvalues contribution due to grid motion ---*/
7524  if (grid_movement){
7525  gridVel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
7526 
7527  su2double ProjGridVel = 0.0;
7528  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7529  ProjGridVel += gridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7530  ProjVelocity_i -= ProjGridVel;
7531  }
7532 
7533  /*--- Flow eigenvalues ---*/
7534  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7535  Lambda_i[iDim] = ProjVelocity_i;
7536  Lambda_i[nVar-2] = ProjVelocity_i + SoundSpeed_i;
7537  Lambda_i[nVar-1] = ProjVelocity_i - SoundSpeed_i;
7538 
7539  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
7540  u_e[0] = Density_e;
7541  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7542  u_e[iDim+1] = Velocity_e[iDim]*Density_e;
7543  u_e[nVar-1] = Energy_e*Density_e;
7544 
7545  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_i --- */
7546  u_i[0] = Density_i;
7547  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7548  u_i[iDim+1] = Velocity_i[iDim]*Density_i;
7549  u_i[nVar-1] = Energy_i*Density_i;
7550 
7551  /*--- Compute the characteristic jumps ---*/
7552  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
7553  {
7554  dw[iVar] = 0;
7555  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
7556  dw[iVar] += invP_Tensor[iVar][jVar] * (u_e[jVar] - u_i[jVar]);
7557 
7558  }
7559 
7560  /*--- Compute the boundary state u_b using characteristics ---*/
7561  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
7562  {
7563  u_b[iVar] = u_i[iVar];
7564 
7565  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
7566  {
7567  if (Lambda_i[jVar] < 0)
7568  {
7569  u_b[iVar] += P_Tensor[iVar][jVar]*dw[jVar];
7570 
7571  }
7572  }
7573  }
7574 
7575 
7576  /*--- Compute the thermodynamic state in u_b ---*/
7577  Density_b = u_b[0];
7578  Velocity2_b = 0;
7579  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7580  {
7581  Velocity_b[iDim] = u_b[iDim+1]/Density_b;
7582  Velocity2_b += Velocity_b[iDim]*Velocity_b[iDim];
7583  }
7584  Energy_b = u_b[nVar-1]/Density_b;
7585  StaticEnergy_b = Energy_b - 0.5*Velocity2_b;
7586  FluidModel->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_b, StaticEnergy_b);
7587  Pressure_b = FluidModel->GetPressure();
7588  Temperature_b = FluidModel->GetTemperature();
7589  Enthalpy_b = Energy_b + Pressure_b/Density_b;
7590  Kappa_b = FluidModel->GetdPde_rho() / Density_b;
7591  Chi_b = FluidModel->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_b * StaticEnergy_b;
7592 
7593  /*--- Compute the residuals ---*/
7594  conv_numerics->GetInviscidProjFlux(&Density_b, Velocity_b, &Pressure_b, &Enthalpy_b, Normal, Residual);
7595 
7596  /*--- Residual contribution due to grid motion ---*/
7597  if (grid_movement) {
7598  gridVel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
7599  su2double projVelocity = 0.0;
7600 
7601  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7602  projVelocity += gridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
7603  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
7604  Residual[iVar] -= projVelocity *(u_b[iVar]);
7605  }
7606 
7607  if (implicit) {
7608 
7609  Jacobian_b = new su2double*[nVar];
7610  DubDu = new su2double*[nVar];
7611  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
7612  {
7613  Jacobian_b[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
7614  DubDu[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
7615  }
7616 
7617  /*--- Initialize DubDu to unit matrix---*/
7618 
7619  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
7620  {
7621  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
7622  DubDu[iVar][jVar]= 0;
7623 
7624  DubDu[iVar][iVar]= 1;
7625  }
7626 
7627  /*--- Compute DubDu -= RNL---*/
7628  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++)
7629  {
7630  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++)
7631  {
7632  for (kVar=0; kVar<nVar; kVar++)
7633  {
7634  if (Lambda_i[kVar]<0)
7635  DubDu[iVar][jVar] -= P_Tensor[iVar][kVar] * invP_Tensor[kVar][jVar];
7636  }
7637  }
7638  }
7639 
7640  /*--- Compute flux Jacobian in state b ---*/
7641  conv_numerics->GetInviscidProjJac(Velocity_b, &Enthalpy_b, &Chi_b, &Kappa_b, Normal, 1.0, Jacobian_b);
7642 
7643  /*--- Jacobian contribution due to grid motion ---*/
7644  if (grid_movement)
7645  {
7646  gridVel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
7647  su2double projVelocity = 0.0;
7648  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7649  projVelocity += gridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
7650  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++){
7651  Residual[iVar] -= projVelocity *(u_b[iVar]);
7652  Jacobian_b[iVar][iVar] -= projVelocity;
7653  }
7654 
7655  }
7656 
7657  /*--- initiate Jacobian_i to zero matrix ---*/
7658  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++)
7659  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++)
7660  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] = 0.0;
7661 
7662  /*--- Compute numerical flux Jacobian at node i ---*/
7663  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++) {
7664  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++) {
7665  for (kVar=0; kVar<nVar; kVar++) {
7666  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] += Jacobian_b[iVar][kVar] * DubDu[kVar][jVar];
7667  }
7668  }
7669  }
7670 
7671  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
7672  delete [] Jacobian_b[iVar];
7673  delete [] DubDu[iVar];
7674  }
7675  delete [] Jacobian_b;
7676  delete [] DubDu;
7677  }
7678 
7679  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
7680  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
7681 
7682  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7683  if (implicit)
7684  Jacobian.AddBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
7685 
7686  /*--- Roe Turkel preconditioning, set the value of beta ---*/
7687  if (config->GetKind_Upwind() == TURKEL)
7688  node[iPoint]->SetPreconditioner_Beta(conv_numerics->GetPrecond_Beta());
7689 
7690  /*--- Viscous contribution ---*/
7691  if (viscous) {
7692 
7693  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7694  V_boundary[0] = Temperature_b;
7695  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7696  V_boundary[iDim+1] = Velocity_b[iDim];
7697  V_boundary[nDim+1] = Pressure_b;
7698  V_boundary[nDim+2] = Density_b;
7699  V_boundary[nDim+3] = Enthalpy_b;
7700 
7701  /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
7702  V_boundary[nDim+5] = FluidModel->GetLaminarViscosity();
7703  V_boundary[nDim+6] = node[iPoint]->GetEddyViscosity();
7704  V_boundary[nDim+7] = FluidModel->GetThermalConductivity();
7705  V_boundary[nDim+8] = FluidModel->GetCp();
7706 
7707  /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
7708  visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7709  visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->node[iPoint]->GetCoord(), geometry->node[Point_Normal]->GetCoord());
7710 
7711  /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
7712  visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_boundary);
7713  visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(node[iPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive(), node[iPoint]->GetGradient_Primitive());
7714 
7715  /*--- Secondary variables ---*/
7716  S_domain = node[iPoint]->GetSecondary();
7717 
7718  /*--- Compute secondary thermodynamic properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
7719 
7720  S_boundary[0]= FluidModel->GetdPdrho_e();
7721  S_boundary[1]= FluidModel->GetdPde_rho();
7722 
7723  S_boundary[2]= FluidModel->GetdTdrho_e();
7724  S_boundary[3]= FluidModel->GetdTde_rho();
7725 
7726  /*--- Compute secondary thermo-physical properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
7727 
7728  S_boundary[4]= FluidModel->Getdmudrho_T();
7729  S_boundary[5]= FluidModel->GetdmudT_rho();
7730 
7731  S_boundary[6]= FluidModel->Getdktdrho_T();
7732  S_boundary[7]= FluidModel->GetdktdT_rho();
7733 
7734  visc_numerics->SetSecondary(S_domain, S_boundary);
7735 
7736  /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
7737  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == SST)
7738  visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0), solver_container[TURB_SOL]->node[iPoint]->GetSolution(0));
7739 
7740  /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
7741  visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(Residual, Jacobian_i, Jacobian_j, config);
7742  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, Residual);
7743 
7744  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7745  if (implicit)
7746  Jacobian.SubtractBlock(iPoint, iPoint, Jacobian_i);
7747 
7748  }
7749 
7750  }
7751  }
7752 
7753  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
7754  delete [] Normal;
7755  delete [] Velocity_e;
7756  delete [] Velocity_b;
7757  delete [] Velocity_i;
7758  delete [] FlowDirMix;
7759 
7760  delete [] S_boundary;
7761  delete [] Lambda_i;
7762  delete [] u_i;
7763  delete [] u_e;
7764  delete [] u_b;
7765  delete [] dw;
7766 
7767 
7768  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
7769  {
7770  delete [] P_Tensor[iVar];
7771  delete [] invP_Tensor[iVar];
7772  }
7773  delete [] P_Tensor;
7774  delete [] invP_Tensor;
7775 
7776 }
7777 
7778 
7779 void CEulerSolver::Mixing_Process(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_Marker) {
7780 
7781  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, nVert;
7782  unsigned short iDim, iVar;
7783  unsigned short mixing_process = config->GetKind_MixingProcess();
7784  su2double Pressure = 0.0, Density = 0.0, Enthalpy = 0.0, *Velocity = NULL, *Normal, *gridVel,
7785  Area, TotalArea, TotalAreaPressure, TotalAreaDensity, *TotalAreaVelocity, UnitNormal[3];
7786  string Marker_Tag, Monitoring_Tag;
7787  su2double val_init_pressure;
7788  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == COMPRESSIBLE);
7789  bool grid_movement = config->GetGrid_Movement();
7790  su2double TotalDensity, TotalPressure, *TotalVelocity, TotalNormal, avgVel2, avgTotalEnthaply;
7791 
7792  /*-- Variables declaration and allocation ---*/
7793  Velocity = new su2double[nDim];
7794  Normal = new su2double[nDim];
7795  TotalVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
7796  TotalAreaVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
7797 
7798  for (iDim=0; iDim<nDim; iDim++) {
7799  TotalVelocity[iDim]=0;
7800  TotalAreaVelocity[iDim]=0;
7801  }
7802 
7803  TotalDensity = 0.0;
7804  TotalPressure = 0.0;
7805  TotalAreaPressure=0.0;
7806  TotalAreaDensity=0.0;
7807  TotalArea = 0.0;
7808  TotalNormal=0.0;
7809 
7810  /*--- Forces initialization for Marker vector ---*/
7811  AveragedPressure[val_Marker] = 0.0;
7812  AveragedEnthalpy[val_Marker] = 0.0;
7813  AveragedDensity[val_Marker] = 0.0;
7814  AveragedSoundSpeed[val_Marker] = 0.0;
7815 
7816  for (iDim=0;iDim < nDim;iDim++){
7817  AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][iDim] = 0.0;
7818  AveragedNormal[val_Marker][iDim] = 0.0;
7819  AveragedGridVel[val_Marker][iDim] = 0.0;
7820  }
7821 
7822  for (iVar=0;iVar<nVar;iVar++)
7823  TotalFlux[val_Marker][iVar]= 0.0;
7824 
7825  /*--- Loop over the vertices to compute the averaged quantities ---*/
7826  nVert = 0;
7827  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(val_Marker); iVertex++) {
7828 
7829  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_Marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7830 
7831  /*--- Compute the integral fluxes for the boundaries ---*/
7832  if (compressible) {
7833  Pressure = node[iPoint]->GetPressure();
7834  Density = node[iPoint]->GetDensity();
7835  Enthalpy = node[iPoint]->GetEnthalpy();
7836  }
7837  else {
7838  cout << "!!! Mixing process for incompressible and freesurface does not available yet !!! " << endl;
7839  cout << "Press any key to exit..." << endl;
7840  cin.get();
7841  exit(1);
7842  }
7843 
7844  /*--- Note that the fluxes from halo cells are discarded ---*/
7845  if ( (geometry->node[iPoint]->GetDomain()) ) {
7846  nVert++;
7847 
7848  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
7849  geometry->vertex[val_Marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7850  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7851  Area = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim]; Area = sqrt(Area);
7852  su2double VelNormal = 0.0, VelSq = 0.0;
7853  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7854  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
7855  Velocity[iDim] = node[iPoint]->GetPrimitive(iDim+1);
7856  VelNormal += UnitNormal[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7857  VelSq += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7858  }
7859 
7860 
7861  /*--- Compute the integral fluxes for the boundary of interest ---*/
7862 
7863  if ((mixing_process == AREA_AVERAGE) || (mixing_process == MIXEDOUT_AVERAGE)){
7864 
7865  TotalFlux[val_Marker][0] += Area*(Density*VelNormal );
7866  for (iDim = 1; iDim < nDim+1; iDim++)
7867  TotalFlux[val_Marker][iDim] += Area*(Density*VelNormal*Velocity[iDim -1] + Pressure*UnitNormal[iDim -1] );
7868  TotalFlux[val_Marker][nDim+1] += Area*(Density*VelNormal*Enthalpy );
7869 
7870  TotalArea += Area;
7871  TotalAreaPressure += Area*Pressure;
7872  TotalAreaDensity += Area*Density;
7873  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7874  TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] += Area*Velocity[iDim];
7875 
7876  }else{
7877 
7878  TotalDensity += Density;
7879  TotalPressure += Pressure;
7880  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7881  TotalVelocity[iDim] += Velocity[iDim];
7882 
7883 
7884  }
7885  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) AveragedNormal[val_Marker][iDim] +=Normal[iDim];
7886  if (grid_movement){
7887  gridVel = geometry->node[iPoint]->GetGridVel();
7888  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7889  AveragedGridVel[val_Marker][iDim] +=gridVel[iDim];
7890  }
7891  }
7892  }
7893 
7894  /*--- Compute the averaged value for the boundary of interest ---*/
7895  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
7896  AveragedNormal[val_Marker][iDim] /=nVert;
7897  TotalNormal+= AveragedNormal[val_Marker][iDim]*AveragedNormal[val_Marker][iDim];
7898  }
7899  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) AveragedNormal[val_Marker][iDim] /=sqrt(TotalNormal);
7900  if (grid_movement){
7901  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7902  AveragedGridVel[val_Marker][iDim] /=nVert;
7903  }
7904 
7905  switch(mixing_process){
7906 
7907 
7908  case ALGEBRAIC_AVERAGE:
7909  AveragedDensity[val_Marker] = TotalDensity / nVert;
7910  AveragedPressure[val_Marker] = TotalPressure / nVert;
7911  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7912  AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][iDim] = TotalVelocity[iDim] / nVert;
7913  break;
7914 
7915  case AREA_AVERAGE:
7916  AveragedDensity[val_Marker] = TotalAreaDensity / TotalArea;
7917  AveragedPressure[val_Marker] = TotalAreaPressure / TotalArea;
7918  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7919  AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][iDim] = TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] / TotalArea;
7920  break;
7921 
7922  case MIXEDOUT_AVERAGE:
7923  for (iVar = 0; iVar<nVar; iVar++){
7924  AveragedFlux[val_Marker][iVar] = TotalFlux[val_Marker][iVar]/TotalArea;
7925  }
7926  val_init_pressure = TotalAreaPressure/TotalArea;
7927 
7928  if (abs(AveragedFlux[val_Marker][0])<(10.0e-9)*TotalAreaDensity) {
7929  cout << "Mass flux is 0.0 so a Area Averaged algorithm is used for the Mixing Procees" << endl;
7930  AveragedDensity[val_Marker] = TotalAreaDensity / TotalArea;
7931  AveragedPressure[val_Marker] = TotalAreaPressure / TotalArea;
7932  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7933  AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][iDim] = TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] / TotalArea;
7934 
7935  }else {
7936  MixedOut_Average (val_init_pressure, AveragedFlux[val_Marker], AveragedNormal[val_Marker], &AveragedPressure[val_Marker], &AveragedDensity[val_Marker]);
7937  for (iDim = 1; iDim < nDim +1;iDim++)
7938  AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][iDim-1]= ( AveragedFlux[val_Marker][iDim] - AveragedPressure[val_Marker]*AveragedNormal[val_Marker][iDim-1] ) / AveragedFlux[val_Marker][0];
7939  }
7940  break;
7941 
7942 
7943  default:
7944  cout << "Warning! Invalid MIXING_PROCESS input!" << endl;
7945  exit(EXIT_FAILURE);
7946  break;
7947  }
7948 
7949  /* --- compute static averaged quantities ---*/
7950  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(AveragedPressure[val_Marker], AveragedDensity[val_Marker]);
7951  AveragedEnthalpy[val_Marker] = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + AveragedPressure[val_Marker]/AveragedDensity[val_Marker];
7952  AveragedSoundSpeed[val_Marker] = FluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
7953  AveragedEntropy[val_Marker] = FluidModel->GetEntropy();
7954  AveragedNormalVelocity[val_Marker]= AveragedNormal[val_Marker][0]*AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][0] + AveragedNormal[val_Marker][1]*AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][1];
7955  AveragedTangVelocity[val_Marker]= AveragedNormal[val_Marker][0]*AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][1] - AveragedNormal[val_Marker][1]*AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][0];
7956  MassFlow[val_Marker]= AveragedDensity[val_Marker]*AveragedNormalVelocity[val_Marker]*TotalArea;
7957  FlowAngle[val_Marker]= atan(AveragedTangVelocity[val_Marker]/AveragedNormalVelocity[val_Marker]);
7958 
7959  /* --- compute total averaged quantities ---*/
7960  avgVel2 = 0.0;
7961  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgVel2 += AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][iDim]*AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][iDim];
7962 
7963  avgTotalEnthaply = AveragedEnthalpy[val_Marker] + 0.5*avgVel2;
7964  FluidModel->SetTDState_hs(avgTotalEnthaply,AveragedEntropy[val_Marker]);
7965  AveragedTotTemperature[val_Marker] = FluidModel->GetTemperature();
7966  AveragedTotPressure[val_Marker] = FluidModel->GetPressure();
7967 
7968  if(grid_movement){
7969  AveragedTangGridVelocity[val_Marker] = AveragedNormal[val_Marker][0]*AveragedGridVel[val_Marker][1]-AveragedNormal[val_Marker][1]*AveragedGridVel[val_Marker][0];
7970  AveragedMach[val_Marker] = sqrt(AveragedNormalVelocity[val_Marker]*AveragedNormalVelocity[val_Marker] + (AveragedTangVelocity[val_Marker] - AveragedTangGridVelocity[val_Marker])*(AveragedTangVelocity[val_Marker] - AveragedTangGridVelocity[val_Marker]));
7971  AveragedMach[val_Marker] /= AveragedSoundSpeed[val_Marker];
7972  AveragedTangMach[val_Marker] = (AveragedTangVelocity[val_Marker] - AveragedTangGridVelocity[val_Marker])/AveragedSoundSpeed[val_Marker];
7973  FlowAngle[val_Marker]= atan((AveragedTangVelocity[val_Marker] - AveragedTangGridVelocity[val_Marker])/AveragedNormalVelocity[val_Marker]);
7974 
7975  }else{
7976  AveragedMach[val_Marker] = 0.0;
7977  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7978  AveragedMach[val_Marker] += AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][iDim]*AveragedVelocity[val_Marker][iDim];
7979  }
7980  AveragedMach[val_Marker] = sqrt(AveragedMach[val_Marker])/AveragedSoundSpeed[val_Marker];
7981  AveragedTangMach[val_Marker] = AveragedTangVelocity[val_Marker]/AveragedSoundSpeed[val_Marker];
7982 
7983  }
7984 
7985  AveragedNormalMach[val_Marker] = AveragedNormalVelocity[val_Marker]/AveragedSoundSpeed[val_Marker];
7986 
7987 
7988  if ((AveragedDensity[val_Marker]!= AveragedDensity[val_Marker]) || (AveragedEnthalpy[val_Marker]!=AveragedEnthalpy[val_Marker]))
7989  cout<<"nan in mixing process in boundary "<<config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_Marker)<< endl;
7990 
7991  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
7992  delete [] Velocity;
7993  delete [] Normal;
7994  delete [] TotalVelocity;
7995  delete [] TotalAreaVelocity;
7996 }
7997 
7998 void CEulerSolver::MixedOut_Average (su2double val_init_pressure, su2double *val_Averaged_Flux, su2double *val_normal,
7999  su2double *pressure_mix, su2double *density_mix) {
8000 
8001  unsigned short maxiter = 10;
8002  unsigned short iter = 0;
8003  su2double toll = 1.0e-07;
8004  su2double resdl = 0.0;
8005 
8006  su2double *val_func = new su2double, *val_right_func = new su2double, *val_left_func = new su2double;
8007  su2double deltaP, *p_mix = new su2double, *p_mix_right = new su2double, *p_mix_left = new su2double;
8008  su2double epsilon = 1.0e-04;
8009  su2double relax_factor = 1;
8010 
8011  *pressure_mix = val_init_pressure;
8012 
8013  /*--- Newton-Raphson's method with central difference formula ---*/
8014 
8015  while ( iter <= maxiter ) {
8016  deltaP = 2*epsilon*(*pressure_mix);
8017  *p_mix_right = *pressure_mix+deltaP/2;
8018  *p_mix_left = *pressure_mix-deltaP/2;
8019  *p_mix = *pressure_mix;
8020  MixedOut_Root_Function(p_mix_right,val_Averaged_Flux,val_normal,val_right_func,density_mix);
8021  MixedOut_Root_Function(p_mix_left,val_Averaged_Flux,val_normal,val_left_func,density_mix);
8022  MixedOut_Root_Function(p_mix,val_Averaged_Flux,val_normal,val_func,density_mix);
8023  su2double der_func = (*val_right_func-*val_left_func) / deltaP;
8024  deltaP = -*val_func/der_func;
8025  resdl = deltaP/val_init_pressure;
8026  *pressure_mix += relax_factor*(deltaP);
8027 
8028  iter += 1;
8029  if ( abs(resdl) <= toll ) {
8030  break;
8031  }
8032 
8033  }
8034 
8035  MixedOut_Root_Function(pressure_mix,val_Averaged_Flux,val_normal,val_func,density_mix);
8036 
8037  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
8038  delete val_func;
8039  delete val_right_func;
8040  delete val_left_func;
8041  delete p_mix;
8042  delete p_mix_right;
8043  delete p_mix_left;
8044 
8045 }
8046 
8047 void CEulerSolver::MixedOut_Root_Function(su2double *pressure, su2double *val_Averaged_Flux, su2double *val_normal, su2double *valfunc, su2double *density) {
8048 
8049  su2double velnormal, velsq;
8050 
8051  su2double *vel;
8052  vel = new su2double[nDim];
8053 
8054 
8055  *valfunc = 0.0;
8056  *density = 0.0;
8057 
8058  velnormal = 0.0;
8059  velsq = 0.0;
8060 
8061  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8062  vel[iDim] = (val_Averaged_Flux[iDim+1] - (*pressure)*val_normal[iDim]) / val_Averaged_Flux[0];
8063  velnormal += val_normal[iDim]*vel[iDim];
8064  velsq += vel[iDim]*vel[iDim];
8065  }
8066  *density = val_Averaged_Flux[0] / velnormal;
8067  if (*density <= 0) cout << " desnity in mixedout routine negative : " << endl;
8068  FluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(*pressure, *density);
8069  su2double enthalpy = FluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + (*pressure)/(*density);
8070  *valfunc = val_Averaged_Flux[nDim+1]/val_Averaged_Flux[0] - enthalpy - velsq/2;
8071  if (*valfunc!=*valfunc) cout << " mixedout root func gives nan: " << endl;
8072 
8073 
8074  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
8075  delete [] vel;
8076 
8077 }
